182/**
183 * This class is the entry point for source completions.
184 * It contains two public APIs used to call CodeAssist on a given source with
185 * a given environment, assisting position and storage (and possibly options).
186 */
187public final class CompletionEngine
188        extends Engine
189        implements ISearchRequestor, TypeConstants , TerminalTokens , RelevanceConstants, SuffixConstants {
190 
191        public class CompletionProblemFactory extends DefaultProblemFactory {
192                private int lastErrorStart;
193 
194                private boolean checkProblems = false;
195                public boolean hasForbiddenProblems = false;
196                public boolean hasAllowedProblems = false;
197 
198                public CompletionProblemFactory(Locale loc) {
199                        super(loc);
200                }
201 
202                public CategorizedProblem createProblem(
203                        char[] originatingFileName,
204                        int problemId,
205                        String[] problemArguments,
206                        String[] messageArguments,
207                        int severity,
208                        int start,
209                        int end,
210                        int lineNumber,
211                        int columnNumber) {
212 
213                        CategorizedProblem pb = super.createProblem(
214                                originatingFileName,
215                                problemId,
216                                problemArguments,
217                                messageArguments,
218                                severity,
219                                start,
220                                end,
221                                lineNumber,
222                                columnNumber);
223                        int id = pb.getID();
224                        if (CompletionEngine.this.actualCompletionPosition > start
225                                && this.lastErrorStart < start
226                                && pb.isError()
227                                && (id & IProblem.Syntax) == 0
228                                && (CompletionEngine.this.fileName == null || CharOperation.equals(CompletionEngine.this.fileName, originatingFileName))) {
229 
230                                CompletionEngine.this.problem = pb;
231                                this.lastErrorStart = start;
232                        }
233                        if (this.checkProblems && !this.hasForbiddenProblems) {
234                                switch (id) {
235                                        case IProblem.UsingDeprecatedType:
236                                                this.hasForbiddenProblems =
237                                                        CompletionEngine.this.options.checkDeprecation;
238                                                break;
239                                        case IProblem.NotVisibleType:
240                                                this.hasForbiddenProblems =
241                                                        CompletionEngine.this.options.checkVisibility;
242                                                break;
243                                        case IProblem.ForbiddenReference:
244                                                this.hasForbiddenProblems =
245                                                        CompletionEngine.this.options.checkForbiddenReference;
246                                                break;
247                                        case IProblem.DiscouragedReference:
248                                                this.hasForbiddenProblems =
249                                                        CompletionEngine.this.options.checkDiscouragedReference;
250                                                break;
251                                        default:
252                                                if ((severity & ProblemSeverities.Optional) != 0) {
253                                                        this.hasAllowedProblems = true;
254                                                } else {
255                                                        this.hasForbiddenProblems = true;
256                                                }
257 
258                                                break;
259                                }
260                        }
261 
262                        return pb;
263                }
264 
265                public void startCheckingProblems() {
266                        this.checkProblems = true;
267                        this.hasForbiddenProblems = false;
268                        this.hasAllowedProblems = false;
269                }
270 
271                public void stopCheckingProblems() {
272                        this.checkProblems = false;
273                }
274        }
275 
276        private static class AcceptedBinding {
277                public AcceptedBinding(
278                        char[] packageName,
279                        char[] simpleTypeName,
280                        char[][] enclosingTypeNames,
281                        int modifiers,
282                        int accessibility) {
283                        this.packageName = packageName;
284                        this.simpleTypeName = simpleTypeName;
285                        this.enclosingTypeNames = enclosingTypeNames;
286                        this.modifiers = modifiers;
287                        this.accessibility = accessibility;
288                    this.bindingType=Binding.TYPE;
289                }
290                public AcceptedBinding(
291                                int bindingType,
292                                char[] packageName,
293                                char[] simpleTypeName,
294                                int modifiers,
295                                int accessibility) {
296                            this.bindingType=bindingType;
297                                this.packageName = packageName;
298                                this.simpleTypeName = simpleTypeName;
299                                this.modifiers = modifiers;
300                                this.accessibility = accessibility;
301                        }
302                public char[] packageName;

314                        StringBuffer buffer = new StringBuffer();

320                        buffer.append(CharOperation.concatWith(enclosingTypeNames, '.'));
321                        buffer.append('}');
322                        return buffer.toString();
323                }

476        /**
477         * The CompletionEngine is responsible for computing source completions.
478         *
479         * It requires a searchable name environment, which supports some
480         * specific search APIs, and a requestor to feed back the results to a UI.
481         *
482         *  @param nameEnvironment org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.internal.codeassist.ISearchableNameEnvironment
483         *      used to resolve type/package references and search for types/packages
484         *      based on partial names.
485         *
486         *  @param requestor org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.internal.codeassist.ICompletionRequestor
487         *      since the engine might produce answers of various forms, the engine
488         *      is associated with a requestor able to accept all possible completions.
489         *
490         *  @param settings java.util.Map
491         *                set of options used to configure the code assist engine.
492         */
493        public CompletionEngine(
494                        SearchableEnvironment nameEnvironment,
495                        CompletionRequestor requestor,
496                        Map settings,
497                        IJavaScriptProject javaProject) {
498                super(settings);
499                this.javaProject = javaProject;
500                this.requestor = requestor;
501                this.nameEnvironment = nameEnvironment;
502                this.typeCache = new HashtableOfObject(5);
503 
504                this.problemFactory = new CompletionProblemFactory(Locale.getDefault());
505                this.problemReporter = new ProblemReporter(
506                                DefaultErrorHandlingPolicies.proceedWithAllProblems(),
507                                this.compilerOptions,
508                                problemFactory);
509                this.lookupEnvironment =
510                        new LookupEnvironment(this, this.compilerOptions, this.problemReporter, nameEnvironment);
511                this.parser =
512                        new CompletionParser(this.problemReporter);
513                this.nameScanner =
514                        new Scanner(
515                                false /*comment*/,
516                                false /*whitespace*/,
517                                false /*nls*/,
518                                this.compilerOptions.sourceLevel,
519                                null /*taskTags*/,
520                                null/*taskPriorities*/,
521                                true/*taskCaseSensitive*/);
522        }
523 
524        /**
525         * One result of the search consists of a new type.
526         *
527         * NOTE - All package and type names are presented in their readable form:
528         *    Package names are in the form "a.b.c".
529         *    Nested type names are in the qualified form "A.I".
530         *    The default package is represented by an empty array.
531         */
532        public void acceptType(
533                char[] packageName,
534                char[] fileName,
535                char[] simpleTypeName,
536                char[][] enclosingTypeNames,
537                int modifiers,
538                AccessRestriction accessRestriction) {
539 
540                if (this.options.checkDeprecation && (modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccDeprecated) != 0) return;
541 
542                if (this.options.checkVisibility) {
543                        if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccPublic) == 0) {
544                                if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccPrivate) != 0)
545                                        return;
546 
547                                //char[] currentPackage = CharOperation.concatWith(this.unitScope.getDefaultPackage().compoundName, '.');
548                                //if(!CharOperation.equals(packageName, currentPackage)) return;
549                        }
550                }
551 
552                int accessibility = IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE;
553                if(accessRestriction != null) {
554                        switch (accessRestriction.getProblemId()) {
555                                case IProblem.ForbiddenReference:
556                                        if (this.options.checkForbiddenReference) {
557                                                return;
558                                        }
559                                        accessibility = IAccessRule.K_NON_ACCESSIBLE;
560                                        break;
561                                case IProblem.DiscouragedReference:
562                                        if (this.options.checkDiscouragedReference) {
563                                                return;
564                                        }
565                                        accessibility = IAccessRule.K_DISCOURAGED;
566                                        break;
567                        }
568                }
569 
570                if(acceptedTypes == null) {
571                        acceptedTypes = new ObjectVector();
572                }
573                acceptedTypes.add(new AcceptedBinding(packageName, simpleTypeName, enclosingTypeNames, modifiers, accessibility));
574        }

576        public void acceptBinding(
577                        char[] packageName,
578                        char[] fileName,
579                        char[] simpleTypeName,
580                        int bindingType,
581                        int modifiers,
582                        AccessRestriction accessRestriction) {
583 
584//                  char [][]pkgName=new char[][]{packageName};
585//                  PackageBinding packageBinding = (PackageBinding) this.unitScope.getBinding(name, mask, invocationSite, needResolve)getPackage(pkgName);
586//                  Binding binding = packageBinding.getBinding(simpleTypeName, bindingType);
587                        if (this.options.checkDeprecation && (modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccDeprecated) != 0) return;
588 
589                        if (this.options.checkVisibility) {
590                                if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccPublic) == 0) {
591                                        if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccPrivate) != 0) return;
592 
593                                        char[] currentPackage = CharOperation.concatWith(this.unitScope.getDefaultPackage().compoundName, '.');
594                                        if(!CharOperation.equals(packageName, currentPackage)) return;
595                                }
596                        }
597 
598                        int accessibility = IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE;
599                        if(accessRestriction != null) {
600                                switch (accessRestriction.getProblemId()) {
601                                        case IProblem.ForbiddenReference:
602                                                if (this.options.checkForbiddenReference) {
603                                                        return;
604                                                }
605                                                accessibility = IAccessRule.K_NON_ACCESSIBLE;
606                                                break;
607                                        case IProblem.DiscouragedReference:
608                                                if (this.options.checkDiscouragedReference) {
609                                                        return;
610                                                }
611                                                accessibility = IAccessRule.K_DISCOURAGED;
612                                                break;
613                                }
614                        }
615 
616                        if(acceptedTypes == null) {
617                                acceptedTypes = new ObjectVector();
618                        }
619                        acceptedTypes.add(new AcceptedBinding(bindingType,packageName, simpleTypeName, modifiers, accessibility));
620                }

624        private void acceptTypes(Scope scope) {
625                if(this.acceptedTypes == null) return;
626 
627                int length = this.acceptedTypes.size();
628 
629                if(length == 0) return;
630 
631                HashtableOfObject onDemandFound = new HashtableOfObject();
632 
633                next : for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
634                        AcceptedBinding acceptedType = (AcceptedBinding)this.acceptedTypes.elementAt(i);
635                        if (acceptedType.bindingType!=Binding.TYPE)
636                                continue;
637                        char[] packageName = acceptedType.packageName;
638                        char[] simpleTypeName = acceptedType.simpleTypeName;
639                        char[][] enclosingTypeNames = acceptedType.enclosingTypeNames;
640                        int modifiers = acceptedType.modifiers;
641                        int accessibility = acceptedType.accessibility;
642 
643                        char[] typeName;
644                        char[] flatEnclosingTypeNames;
645                        if(enclosingTypeNames == null || enclosingTypeNames.length == 0) {
646                                flatEnclosingTypeNames = null;
647                                typeName = simpleTypeName;
648                        } else {
649                                flatEnclosingTypeNames = CharOperation.concatWith(acceptedType.enclosingTypeNames, '.');
650                                typeName = CharOperation.concat(flatEnclosingTypeNames, simpleTypeName, '.');
651                        }
652                        char[] fullyQualifiedName = CharOperation.concat(packageName, typeName, '.');
653 
654                        if (this.knownTypes.containsKey(fullyQualifiedName)) continue next;
655 
656                        this.knownTypes.put(fullyQualifiedName, this);
657 
658                        if (this.resolvingImports) {
659                                char[] completionName = CharOperation.concat(fullyQualifiedName, new char[] { ';' });
660                                
661                                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
662                                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
663                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
664                                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(accessibility);
665                                if(insideQualifiedReference) {
666                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(this.completionToken, fullyQualifiedName);
667                                } else {
668                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(this.completionToken, simpleTypeName);
669                                }
670 
671                                this.noProposal = false;
672                                if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
673                                        createTypeProposal(packageName, typeName, modifiers, accessibility, completionName, relevance);
674                                }
675                        } else {
676                                if(!this.importCachesInitialized) {
677                                        this.initializeImportCaches();
678                                }
679 
680                                for (int j = 0; j < this.importCacheCount; j++) {
681                                        char[][] importName = this.importsCache[j];
682                                        if(CharOperation.equals(typeName, importName[0])) {
683                                                proposeType(
684                                                                packageName,
685                                                                simpleTypeName,
686                                                                modifiers,
687                                                                accessibility,
688                                                                typeName,
689                                                                fullyQualifiedName,
690                                                                !CharOperation.equals(fullyQualifiedName, importName[1]),
691                                                                scope);
692                                                continue next;
693                                        }
694                                }
695 
696 
697                                //if ((enclosingTypeNames == null || enclosingTypeNames.length == 0 ) && CharOperation.equals(this.currentPackageName, packageName)) {
698                                        proposeType(
699                                                        packageName,
700                                                        simpleTypeName,
701                                                        modifiers,
702                                                        accessibility,
703                                                        typeName,
704                                                        fullyQualifiedName,
705                                                        true,scope);
706                                        continue next;
707 
708//                                } else {
709//                                        char[] fullyQualifiedEnclosingTypeOrPackageName = null;
710//
711//                                        AcceptedBinding foundType = null;
712//                                        if((foundType = (AcceptedBinding)onDemandFound.get(simpleTypeName)) == null) {
713//                                                for (int j = 0; j < this.onDemandImportCacheCount; j++) {
714//                                                        ImportBinding importBinding = this.onDemandImportsCache[j];
715//
716//                                                        char[][] importName = importBinding.compoundName;
717//                                                        char[] importFlatName = CharOperation.concatWith(importName, '.');
718//
719//                                                        if(fullyQualifiedEnclosingTypeOrPackageName == null) {
720//                                                                if(enclosingTypeNames != null && enclosingTypeNames.length != 0) {
721//                                                                        fullyQualifiedEnclosingTypeOrPackageName =
722//                                                                                CharOperation.concat(
723//                                                                                                packageName,
724//                                                                                                flatEnclosingTypeNames,
725//                                                                                                '.');
726//                                                                } else {
727//                                                                        fullyQualifiedEnclosingTypeOrPackageName =
728//                                                                                packageName;
729//                                                                }
730//                                                        }
731//                                                        if(CharOperation.equals(fullyQualifiedEnclosingTypeOrPackageName, importFlatName)) {
732//                                                                if(importBinding.isStatic()) {
733//                                                                        if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccStatic) != 0) {
734//                                                                                acceptedType.qualifiedTypeName = typeName;
735//                                                                                acceptedType.fullyQualifiedName = fullyQualifiedName;
736//                                                                                onDemandFound.put(
737//                                                                                                simpleTypeName,
738//                                                                                                acceptedType);
739//                                                                                continue next;
740//                                                                        }
741//                                                                } else {
742//                                                                        acceptedType.qualifiedTypeName = typeName;
743//                                                                        acceptedType.fullyQualifiedName = fullyQualifiedName;
744//                                                                        onDemandFound.put(
745//                                                                                        simpleTypeName,
746//                                                                                        acceptedType);
747//                                                                        continue next;
748//                                                                }
749//                                                        }
750//                                                }
751//                                        } else if(!foundType.mustBeQualified){
752//                                                done : for (int j = 0; j < this.onDemandImportCacheCount; j++) {
753//                                                        ImportBinding importBinding = this.onDemandImportsCache[j];
754//
755//                                                        char[][] importName = importBinding.compoundName;
756//                                                        char[] importFlatName = CharOperation.concatWith(importName, '.');
757//
758//                                                        if(fullyQualifiedEnclosingTypeOrPackageName == null) {
759//                                                                if(enclosingTypeNames != null && enclosingTypeNames.length != 0) {
760//                                                                        fullyQualifiedEnclosingTypeOrPackageName =
761//                                                                                CharOperation.concat(
762//                                                                                                packageName,
763//                                                                                                flatEnclosingTypeNames,
764//                                                                                                '.');
765//                                                                } else {
766//                                                                        fullyQualifiedEnclosingTypeOrPackageName =
767//                                                                                packageName;
768//                                                                }
769//                                                        }
770//                                                        if(CharOperation.equals(fullyQualifiedEnclosingTypeOrPackageName, importFlatName)) {
771//                                                                if(importBinding.isStatic()) {
772//                                                                        if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccStatic) != 0) {
773//                                                                                foundType.mustBeQualified = true;
774//                                                                                break done;
775//                                                                        }
776//                                                                } else {
777//                                                                        foundType.mustBeQualified = true;
778//                                                                        break done;
779//                                                                }
780//                                                        }
781//                                                }
782//                                        }
783//                                        proposeType(
784//                                                        packageName,
785//                                                        simpleTypeName,
786//                                                        modifiers,
787//                                                        accessibility,
788//                                                        typeName,
789//                                                        fullyQualifiedName,
790//                                                        true);
791//                                }
792                        }
793                }
794                char[][] keys = onDemandFound.keyTable;
795                Object[] values = onDemandFound.valueTable;
796                int max = keys.length;
797                for (int i = 0; i < max; i++) {
798                        if(keys[i] != null) {
799                                AcceptedBinding value = (AcceptedBinding) values[i];
800                                if(value != null) {
801                                        proposeType(
802                                                        value.packageName,
803                                                        value.simpleTypeName,
804                                                        value.modifiers,
805                                                        value.accessibility,
806                                                        value.qualifiedTypeName,
807                                                        value.fullyQualifiedName,
808                                                        value.mustBeQualified, scope);
809                                }
810                        }
811                }
812                this.acceptedTypes = null; // reset
813        }
814 
815        public void acceptUnresolvedName(char[] name) {
816                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
817                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution(false);
818                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
819                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(completionToken, name);
820                relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(false);
821                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for local variable
822                CompletionEngine.this.noProposal = false;
823                if(!CompletionEngine.this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.LOCAL_VARIABLE_REF)) {
824                        CompletionProposal proposal = CompletionEngine.this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.LOCAL_VARIABLE_REF, CompletionEngine.this.actualCompletionPosition);
825                        proposal.setSignature(JAVA_LANG_OBJECT_SIGNATURE);
826                        proposal.setPackageName(JAVA_LANG_NAME);
827                        proposal.setTypeName(OBJECT);
828                        proposal.setName(name);
829                        proposal.setCompletion(name);
830                        proposal.setFlags(Flags.AccDefault);
831                        proposal.setReplaceRange(CompletionEngine.this.startPosition - CompletionEngine.this.offset, CompletionEngine.this.endPosition - CompletionEngine.this.offset);
832                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
833                        CompletionEngine.this.requestor.accept(proposal);
834                        if(DEBUG) {
835                                CompletionEngine.this.printDebug(proposal);
836                        }
837                }
838        }

841        private void acceptBindings(char[] name,boolean exactMatch, boolean prefixRequired) {
842                if(this.acceptedTypes == null) return;
843 
844                int length = this.acceptedTypes.size();
845 
846                if(length == 0) return;
847 
848 
849                 for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
850                        AcceptedBinding acceptedType = (AcceptedBinding)this.acceptedTypes.elementAt(i);
851                        char[] packageName = acceptedType.packageName;

1129        // this code is derived from FunctionBinding#areParametersCompatibleWith(TypeBinding[])
1130        private final boolean areParametersCompatibleWith(TypeBinding[] parameters, TypeBinding[] arguments, boolean isVarargs) {
1131                int paramLength = parameters.length;
1132                int argLength = arguments.length;
1133                int lastIndex = argLength;
1134                if (isVarargs) {
1135                        lastIndex = paramLength - 1;
1136                        if (paramLength == argLength) { // accept X[] but not X or X[][]
1137                                TypeBinding varArgType = parameters[lastIndex]; // is an ArrayBinding by definition
1138                                TypeBinding lastArgument = arguments[lastIndex];
1139                                if (varArgType != lastArgument && !lastArgument.isCompatibleWith(varArgType))
1140                                        return false;
1141                        } else if (paramLength < argLength) { // all remainig argument types must be compatible with the elementsType of varArgType
1142                                TypeBinding varArgType = ((ArrayBinding) parameters[lastIndex]).elementsType();
1143                                for (int i = lastIndex; i < argLength; i++)
1144                                        if (varArgType != arguments[i] && !arguments[i].isCompatibleWith(varArgType))
1145                                                return false;
1146                        } else if (lastIndex != argLength) { // can call foo(int i, X ... x) with foo(1) but NOT foo();
1147                                return false;
1148                        }
1149                        // now compare standard arguments from 0 to lastIndex
1150                } else {
1151                        if(paramLength != argLength)
1152                                return false;
1153                }
1154                for (int i = 0; i < lastIndex; i++)
1155                        if (parameters[i] != arguments[i] && !arguments[i].isCompatibleWith(parameters[i]))
1156                                return false;
1157                return true;
1158        }
1159 
1160        private void proposeType(char[] packageName, char[] simpleTypeName, int modifiers, int accessibility, char[] typeName, char[] fullyQualifiedName, boolean isQualified, Scope scope) {
1161                char[] completionName = fullyQualifiedName;
1162                if(isQualified) {
1163                        if (packageName == null || packageName.length == 0)
1164                                if (this.unitScope != null && this.unitScope.getDefaultPackage().compoundName != CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR)
1165                                        return; // ignore types from the default package from outside it
1166                } else {
1167                        completionName = simpleTypeName;
1168                }
1169                TypeBinding guessedType = null;
1170                if ((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccAnnotation) != 0 &&
1171                                this.assistNodeIsAnnotation &&
1172                                (this.targetedElement & TagBits.AnnotationTargetMASK) != 0) {
1173                        char[][] cn = CharOperation.splitOn('.', fullyQualifiedName);
1174 
1175                        TypeReference ref;
1176                        if (cn.length == 1) {
1177                                ref = new SingleTypeReference(simpleTypeName, 0);
1178                        } else {
1179                                ref = new QualifiedTypeReference(cn,new long[cn.length]);
1180                        }
1181 
1182                        switch (scope.kind) {
1183                                case Scope.METHOD_SCOPE :
1184                                case Scope.BLOCK_SCOPE :
1185                                        guessedType = ref.resolveType((BlockScope)scope);
1186                                        break;
1187                                case Scope.CLASS_SCOPE :
1188                                        guessedType = ref.resolveType((ClassScope)scope);
1189                                        break;
1190                        }
1191 
1192                        if (!guessedType.isValidBinding()) return;
1193 
1194                        if (!hasPossibleAnnotationTarget(guessedType, scope)) return;
1195                }
1196 
1197 
1198                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
1199                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
1200                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
1201                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(accessibility);
1202                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(this.completionToken, simpleTypeName);
1203                relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(packageName, simpleTypeName);
1204                relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(isQualified);
1205 
1206                int kind = modifiers & (ClassFileConstants.AccInterface | ClassFileConstants.AccEnum | ClassFileConstants.AccAnnotation);
1207                switch (kind) {
1208                        case ClassFileConstants.AccAnnotation:
1209                        case ClassFileConstants.AccAnnotation | ClassFileConstants.AccInterface:
1210                                relevance += computeRelevanceForAnnotation();
1211                                if (guessedType != null) relevance += computeRelevanceForAnnotationTarget(guessedType);
1212                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterface();
1213                                break;
1214                        case ClassFileConstants.AccEnum:
1215                                relevance += computeRelevanceForEnum();
1216                                break;
1217                        case ClassFileConstants.AccInterface:
1218                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterface();
1219                                break;
1220                        default:
1221                                relevance += computeRelevanceForClass();
1222                                relevance += computeRelevanceForException(simpleTypeName);
1223                                break;
1224                }
1225 
1226                this.noProposal = false;
1227                if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
1228                        createTypeProposal(packageName, typeName, modifiers, accessibility, completionName, relevance);
1229                }
1230        }
1231 
1232        /**
1233         * One result of the search consists of a new package.
1234         *
1235         * NOTE - All package names are presented in their readable form:
1236         *    Package names are in the form "a.b.c".
1237         *    The default package is represented by an empty array.
1238         */
1239        public void acceptPackage(char[] packageName) {
1240 
1241                if (this.knownPkgs.containsKey(packageName)) return;
1242 
1243                this.knownPkgs.put(packageName, this);
1244 
1245//                char[] completion;
1246//                if(this.resolvingImports) {
1247//                        if(this.resolvingStaticImports) {
1248//                                completion = CharOperation.concat(packageName, new char[] { '.' });
1249//                        } else {
1250//                                completion = CharOperation.concat(packageName, new char[] { '.', '*', ';' });
1251//                        }
1252//                } else {
1253//                        completion = packageName;
1254//                }
1255 
1256                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
1257                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
1258                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
1259                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(this.qualifiedCompletionToken == null ? this.completionToken : this.qualifiedCompletionToken, packageName);
1260                if(!this.resolvingImports) {
1261                        relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(true);
1262                }
1263                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE);
1264 
1265                this.noProposal = false;
1266//                if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.PACKAGE_REF)) {
1267//                        CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.PACKAGE_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
1268//                        proposal.setDeclarationSignature(packageName);
1269//                        proposal.setPackageName(packageName);
1270//                        proposal.setCompletion(completion);
1271//                        proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
1272//                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
1273//                        this.requestor.accept(proposal);
1274//                        if(DEBUG) {
1275//                                this.printDebug(proposal);
1276//                        }
1277//                }
1278        }
1279 
1280        private void buildContext(
1281                        ASTNode astNode,
1282                        ASTNode astNodeParent,
1283                        Binding qualifiedBinding,
1284                        Scope scope) {
1285                CompletionContext context = new CompletionContext();
1286 
1287                // build expected types context
1288                if (this.expectedTypesPtr > -1) {
1289                        int length = this.expectedTypesPtr + 1;
1290                        char[][] expTypes = new char[length][];
1291                        char[][] expKeys = new char[length][];
1292                        for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
1293                                expTypes[i] = getSignature(this.expectedTypes[i]);
1294                                expKeys[i] = this.expectedTypes[i].computeUniqueKey();
1295                        }
1296                        context.setExpectedTypesSignatures(expTypes);
1297                        context.setExpectedTypesKeys(expKeys);
1298                }
1299 
1300                context.setOffset(this.actualCompletionPosition + 1 - this.offset);
1301 
1302                // Set javadoc info
1303                if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnJavadoc) {
1304                        this.assistNodeInJavadoc = ((CompletionOnJavadoc)astNode).getCompletionFlags();
1305                        context.setJavadoc(this.assistNodeInJavadoc);
1306                }
1307 
1308                if (!(astNode instanceof CompletionOnJavadoc)) {
1309                        CompletionScanner scanner = (CompletionScanner)this.parser.scanner;
1310                        context.setToken(scanner.completionIdentifier);
1311                        context.setTokenRange(
1312                                        scanner.completedIdentifierStart - this.offset,
1313                                        scanner.completedIdentifierEnd - this.offset,
1314                                        scanner.endOfEmptyToken - this.offset);
1315                } else if(astNode instanceof CompletionOnJavadocTag) {
1316                        CompletionOnJavadocTag javadocTag = (CompletionOnJavadocTag) astNode;
1317                        context.setToken(CharOperation.concat(new char[]{'@'}, javadocTag.token));
1318                        context.setTokenRange(
1319                                        javadocTag.tagSourceStart - this.offset,
1320                                        javadocTag.tagSourceEnd - this.offset,
1321                                        ((CompletionScanner)this.parser.javadocParser.scanner).endOfEmptyToken - this.offset);
1322                } else {
1323                        CompletionScanner scanner = (CompletionScanner)this.parser.javadocParser.scanner;
1324                        context.setToken(scanner.completionIdentifier);
1325                        context.setTokenRange(
1326                                        scanner.completedIdentifierStart - this.offset,
1327                                        scanner.completedIdentifierEnd - this.offset,
1328                                        scanner.endOfEmptyToken - this.offset);
1329                }
1330 
1331                if(astNode instanceof CompletionOnStringLiteral) {
1332                        context.setTokenKind(CompletionContext.TOKEN_KIND_STRING_LITERAL);
1333                } else {
1334                        context.setTokenKind(CompletionContext.TOKEN_KIND_NAME);
1335                }
1336 
1337                if(DEBUG) {
1338                        System.out.println(context.toString());
1339                }
1340                this.requestor.acceptContext(context);
1341        }
1342 
1343        private boolean complete(ASTNode astNode, ASTNode astNodeParent, Binding qualifiedBinding, Scope scope, boolean insideTypeAnnotation) {
1344 
1345                setSourceRange(astNode.sourceStart, astNode.sourceEnd);
1346 
1347                scope = computeForbiddenBindings(astNode, astNodeParent, scope);
1348                computeUninterestingBindings(astNodeParent, scope);
1349                if(astNodeParent != null) {
1350                        if(!isValidParent(astNodeParent, astNode, scope)) return false;
1351                        computeExpectedTypes(astNodeParent, astNode, scope);
1352                }
1353 
1354                buildContext(astNode, astNodeParent, qualifiedBinding, scope);
1355 
1356                if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnFieldType) {
1357 
1358                        CompletionOnFieldType field = (CompletionOnFieldType) astNode;
1359                        CompletionOnSingleTypeReference type = (CompletionOnSingleTypeReference) field.type;
1360                        this.completionToken = type.token;
1361                        setSourceRange(type.sourceStart, type.sourceEnd);
1362 
1363                        findTypesAndPackages(this.completionToken, scope, new ObjectVector());
1364                        if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD)) {
1365                                findKeywordsForMember(this.completionToken, field.modifiers);
1366                        }
1367 
1368                        if (!field.isLocalVariable && field.modifiers == ClassFileConstants.AccDefault) {
1369                                SourceTypeBinding enclosingType = scope.enclosingSourceType();
1370                                if (!enclosingType.isAnnotationType()) {
1371                                        if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.METHOD_DECLARATION)) {
1372                                                findMethods(this.completionToken,null,null,enclosingType,scope,new ObjectVector(),false,false,true,null,null,false,false,true,null, null, null, false);
1373                                        }
1374                                        if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.POTENTIAL_METHOD_DECLARATION)) {
1375                                                proposeNewMethod(this.completionToken, enclosingType);
1376                                        }
1377                                }
1378                        }
1379                } else if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnMethodReturnType) {
1380 
1381                        CompletionOnMethodReturnType method = (CompletionOnMethodReturnType) astNode;
1382                        SingleTypeReference type = (CompletionOnSingleTypeReference) method.returnType;
1383                        this.completionToken = type.token;
1384                        setSourceRange(type.sourceStart, type.sourceEnd);
1385                        findTypesAndPackages(this.completionToken, scope.parent, new ObjectVector());
1386                        if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD)) {
1387                                findKeywordsForMember(this.completionToken, method.modifiers);
1388                        }
1389 
1390                        if (method.modifiers == ClassFileConstants.AccDefault) {
1391                                SourceTypeBinding enclosingType = scope.enclosingSourceType();
1392                                if (!enclosingType.isAnnotationType()) {
1393                                        if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.METHOD_DECLARATION)) {
1394                                                findMethods(this.completionToken,null,null,scope.enclosingSourceType(),scope,new ObjectVector(),false,false,true,null,null,false,false,true,null, null, null, false);
1395                                        }
1396                                        if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.POTENTIAL_METHOD_DECLARATION)) {
1397                                                proposeNewMethod(this.completionToken, scope.enclosingSourceType());
1398                                        }
1399                                }
1400                        }
1401                } else if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnSingleNameReference) {
1402 
1403                        CompletionOnSingleNameReference singleNameReference = (CompletionOnSingleNameReference) astNode;
1404                        this.completionToken = singleNameReference.token;
1405                        SwitchStatement switchStatement = astNodeParent instanceof SwitchStatement ? (SwitchStatement) astNodeParent : null;
1406                        if (switchStatement != null
1407                                        && switchStatement.expression.resolvedType != null
1408                                        && switchStatement.expression.resolvedType.isEnum()) {
1409                                if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF)) {
1410                                        this.assistNodeIsEnum = true;
1411                                }
1412                        } else if (this.expectedTypesPtr > -1 && this.expectedTypes[0].isAnnotationType()) {
1413                                findTypesAndPackages(this.completionToken, scope, new ObjectVector());
1414                        } else {
1415                                if (scope instanceof BlockScope && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.LOCAL_VARIABLE_REF)) {
1416                                        char[][] alreadyDefinedName = computeAlreadyDefinedName((BlockScope)scope, singleNameReference);
1417 
1418                                        findUnresolvedReference(
1419                                                        singleNameReference.sourceStart,
1420                                                        singleNameReference.sourceEnd,
1421                                                        (BlockScope)scope,
1422                                                        alreadyDefinedName);
1423                                }
1424                                findVariablesAndMethods(
1425                                        this.completionToken,
1426                                        scope,
1427                                        singleNameReference,
1428                                        scope,
1429                                        insideTypeAnnotation,
1430                                        singleNameReference.isInsideAnnotationAttribute);
1431                                // can be the start of a qualified type name
1432                                findTypesAndPackages(this.completionToken, scope, new ObjectVector());
1433                                if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD)) {
1434                                        if (this.completionToken != null && this.completionToken.length != 0) {
1435                                                findKeywords(this.completionToken, singleNameReference.possibleKeywords, false, false);
1436                                        } else {
1437                                                findTrueOrFalseKeywords(singleNameReference.possibleKeywords);
1438                                        }
1439                                }
1440                                if (singleNameReference.canBeExplicitConstructor && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF)){
1441                                        if (CharOperation.prefixEquals(this.completionToken, Keywords.THIS, false)) {
1442                                                ReferenceBinding ref = scope.enclosingSourceType();
1443                                                findExplicitConstructors(Keywords.THIS, ref, (MethodScope)scope, singleNameReference);
1444                                        } else if (CharOperation.prefixEquals(this.completionToken, Keywords.SUPER, false)) {
1445                                                ReferenceBinding ref = scope.enclosingSourceType();
1446                                                findExplicitConstructors(Keywords.SUPER, ref.superclass(), (MethodScope)scope, singleNameReference);
1447                                        }
1448                                }
1449                        }
1450 
1451                } else if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnSingleTypeReference) {
1452 
1453                        CompletionOnSingleTypeReference singleRef = (CompletionOnSingleTypeReference) astNode;
1454 
1455                        this.completionToken = singleRef.token;
1456 
1457                        this.assistNodeIsClass = singleRef.isClass();
1458                        this.assistNodeIsException = singleRef.isException();
1459                        this.assistNodeIsInterface = singleRef.isInterface();
1460                        this.assistNodeIsConstructor = singleRef.isConstructorType;
1461                        this.assistNodeIsSuperType = singleRef.isSuperType();
1462 
1463 
1464                        // can be the start of a qualified type name
1465                        if (qualifiedBinding == null) {
1466                                if (this.completionToken.length == 0 &&
1467                                                (astNodeParent instanceof ParameterizedSingleTypeReference ||
1468                                                                astNodeParent instanceof ParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference)) {
1469                                        this.setSourceRange(astNode.sourceStart, astNode.sourceStart - 1, false);
1470 
1471                                        findParameterizedType((TypeReference)astNodeParent, scope);
1472                                } else {
1473                                        ObjectVector typesFound = new ObjectVector();
1474                                        if (this.assistNodeIsException && astNodeParent instanceof TryStatement) {
1475                                                findExceptionFromTryStatement(
1476                                                                this.completionToken,
1477                                                                null,
1478                                                                scope.enclosingSourceType(),
1479                                                                (BlockScope)scope,
1480                                                                typesFound);
1481                                        }
1482                                        findTypesAndPackages(this.completionToken, scope, typesFound);
1483                                }
1484                        } else if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
1485                                findMemberTypes(
1486                                        this.completionToken,
1487                                        (ReferenceBinding) qualifiedBinding,
1488                                        scope,
1489                                        scope.enclosingSourceType(),
1490                                        false,
1491                                        false,
1492                                        false,
1493                                        false,
1494                                        !this.assistNodeIsConstructor,
1495                                        null,
1496                                        new ObjectVector());
1497                        }
1498                } else if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnSingleTypeName) {
1499 
1500                        CompletionOnSingleTypeName singleRef = (CompletionOnSingleTypeName) astNode;
1501                        this.completionToken = singleRef.token;
1502 
1503                        this.assistNodeIsClass = true;
1504                        this.assistNodeIsConstructor = true;
1505 
1506                        // can be the start of a qualified type name
1507                        if (qualifiedBinding == null) {
1508                                        ObjectVector typesFound = new ObjectVector();
1509                                        findTypesAndPackages(this.completionToken, scope, typesFound);
1510                        } else if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
1511                                findMemberTypes(
1512                                        this.completionToken,
1513                                        (ReferenceBinding) qualifiedBinding,
1514                                        scope,
1515                                        scope.enclosingSourceType(),
1516                                        false,
1517                                        false,
1518                                        false,
1519                                        false,
1520                                        !this.assistNodeIsConstructor,
1521                                        null,
1522                                        new ObjectVector());
1523                        }
1524                }
1525                else if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnQualifiedNameReference) {
1526 
1527                        this.insideQualifiedReference = true;
1528                        CompletionOnQualifiedNameReference ref =
1529                                (CompletionOnQualifiedNameReference) astNode;
1530                        this.completionToken = ref.completionIdentifier;
1531                        long completionPosition = ref.sourcePositions[ref.sourcePositions.length - 1];
1532 
1533                        if (qualifiedBinding.problemId() == ProblemReasons.NotFound) {
1534                                setSourceRange((int) (completionPosition >>> 32), (int) completionPosition);
1535                                // complete field members with missing fields type
1536                                // class X {
1537                                //   Missing f;
1538                                //   void foo() {
1539                                //     f.|
1540                                //   }
1541                                // }
1542                                if (this.assistNodeInJavadoc == 0 &&
1543                                                (this.requestor.isAllowingRequiredProposals(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF, CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF) ||
1544                                                                this.requestor.isAllowingRequiredProposals(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF, CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF))) {
1545                                        if(ref.tokens.length == 1) {
1546                                                findFieldsAndMethodsFromMissingFieldType(ref.tokens[0], scope, ref, insideTypeAnnotation);
1547                                        }
1548                                }
1549                        } else if (qualifiedBinding instanceof VariableBinding) {
1550                                setSourceRange((int) (completionPosition >>> 32), (int) completionPosition);
1551                                TypeBinding receiverType = ((VariableBinding) qualifiedBinding).type;
1552                                if (receiverType != null) {
1553                                        findFieldsAndMethods(this.completionToken, receiverType.capture(scope, ref.sourceEnd), scope, ref, scope,false,false,false, null, null, null, false);
1554                                } else if (this.assistNodeInJavadoc == 0 &&
1555                                                (this.requestor.isAllowingRequiredProposals(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF, CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF) ||
1556                                                                this.requestor.isAllowingRequiredProposals(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF, CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF))) {
1557                                        boolean proposeField = !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF);
1558                                        boolean proposeMethod = !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF);
1559                                        if (proposeField || proposeMethod) {
1560                                                if (qualifiedBinding instanceof LocalVariableBinding) {
1561                                                        // complete local variable members with missing variables type
1562                                                        // class X {
1563                                                        //   void foo() {
1564                                                        //     Missing f;
1565                                                        //     f.|
1566                                                        //   }
1567                                                        // }
1568                                                        LocalVariableBinding localVariableBinding = (LocalVariableBinding) qualifiedBinding;
1569 
1570                                                        findFieldsAndMethodsFromMissingType(
1571                                                                        this.completionToken,
1572                                                                        localVariableBinding.declaration.type,
1573                                                                        localVariableBinding.declaringScope,
1574                                                                        ref,
1575                                                                        scope);
1576                                                }
1577                                        }
1578                                }
1579 
1580                        } else if (qualifiedBinding instanceof ReferenceBinding && !(qualifiedBinding instanceof TypeVariableBinding)) {
1581                                boolean isInsideAnnotationAttribute = ref.isInsideAnnotationAttribute;
1582                                ReferenceBinding receiverType = (ReferenceBinding) qualifiedBinding;
1583                                setSourceRange((int) (completionPosition >>> 32), (int) completionPosition);
1584 
1585                                if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
1586                                        findMemberTypes(
1587                                                        this.completionToken,
1588                                                        receiverType,
1589                                                        scope,
1590                                                        scope.enclosingSourceType(),
1591                                                        false,
1592                                                        true,
1593                                                        new ObjectVector());
1594                                }
1595                                if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF)) {
1596                                        findClassField(this.completionToken, (TypeBinding) qualifiedBinding, scope);
1597                                }
1598 
1599                                MethodScope methodScope = null;
1600                                if (!isInsideAnnotationAttribute &&
1601                                                !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD) &&
1602                                                ((scope instanceof MethodScope && !((MethodScope)scope).isStatic)
1603                                                || ((methodScope = scope.enclosingMethodScope()) != null && !methodScope.isStatic))) {
1604                                        if (this.completionToken.length > 0) {
1605                                                findKeywords(this.completionToken, new char[][]{Keywords.THIS}, false, true);
1606                                        } else {
1607                                                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
1608                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
1609                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
1610                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(this.completionToken, Keywords.THIS);
1611                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for keywords
1612                                                relevance += R_NON_INHERITED;
1613 
1614                                                this.noProposal = false;
1615                                                if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD)) {
1616                                                        CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD, this.actualCompletionPosition);
1617                                                        proposal.setName(Keywords.THIS);
1618                                                        proposal.setCompletion(Keywords.THIS);
1619                                                        proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
1620                                                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
1621                                                        this.requestor.accept(proposal);
1622                                                        if (DEBUG) {
1623                                                                this.printDebug(proposal);
1624                                                        }
1625                                                }
1626                                        }
1627                                }
1628 
1629                                if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF)) {
1630                                        findFields(
1631                                                this.completionToken,
1632                                                receiverType,
1633                                                scope,
1634                                                new ObjectVector(),
1635                                                new ObjectVector(),
1636                                                true,
1637                                                ref,
1638                                                scope,
1639                                                false,
1640                                                false,
1641                                                null,
1642                                                null,
1643                                                null,
1644                                                false);
1645                                }
1646 
1647                                if (!isInsideAnnotationAttribute && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF)) {
1648                                        findMethods(
1649                                                this.completionToken,
1650                                                null,
1651                                                null,
1652                                                receiverType,
1653                                                scope,
1654                                                new ObjectVector(),
1655                                                true,
1656                                                false,
1657                                                false,
1658                                                ref,
1659                                                scope,
1660                                                false,
1661                                                false,
1662                                                false,
1663                                                null,
1664                                                null,
1665                                                null,
1666                                                false);
1667                                }
1668 
1669                        } else if (qualifiedBinding instanceof PackageBinding) {
1670 
1671                                setSourceRange(astNode.sourceStart, (int) completionPosition);
1672                                // replace to the end of the completion identifier
1673                                findTypesAndSubpackages(this.completionToken, (PackageBinding) qualifiedBinding, scope);
1674                        }
1675                } else if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnQualifiedTypeReference) {
1676 
1677                        this.insideQualifiedReference = true;
1678 
1679                        CompletionOnQualifiedTypeReference ref =
1680                                (CompletionOnQualifiedTypeReference) astNode;
1681 
1682                        this.assistNodeIsClass = ref.isClass();

2326        public void complete(IType type, char[] snippet, int position, char[][] localVariableTypeNames, char[][] localVariableNames, int[] localVariableModifiers, boolean isStatic){
2327                if(this.requestor != null){
2328                        this.requestor.beginReporting();
2329                }
2330                boolean contextAccepted = false;
2331                IType topLevelType = type;
2332                while(topLevelType.getDeclaringType() != null) {
2333                        topLevelType = topLevelType.getDeclaringType();
2334                }
2335 
2336                this.fileName = topLevelType.getParent().getElementName().toCharArray();
2337                CompilationResult compilationResult = new CompilationResult(this.fileName, this.packageName, 1, 1, this.compilerOptions.maxProblemsPerUnit);
2338 
2339                CompilationUnitDeclaration compilationUnit = null;
2340 
2341                try {
2342                        // TypeConverter is used instead of SourceTypeConverter because the type
2343                        // to convert can be a binary type or a source type
2344                        TypeDeclaration typeDeclaration = null;
2345                        if (type instanceof SourceType) {
2346                                SourceType sourceType = (SourceType) type;
2347                                ISourceType info = (ISourceType) sourceType.getElementInfo();
2348                                compilationUnit = SourceTypeConverter.buildCompilationUnit(
2349                                        new ISourceType[] {info},//sourceTypes[0] is always toplevel here
2350                                        SourceTypeConverter.FIELD_AND_METHOD // need field and methods
2351                                        | SourceTypeConverter.MEMBER_TYPE, // need member types
2352                                        // no need for field initialization
2353                                        this.problemReporter,
2354                                        compilationResult);
2355                                if (compilationUnit.types != null)
2356                                        typeDeclaration = compilationUnit.types[0];
2357                        } else {
2358                                compilationUnit = new CompilationUnitDeclaration(this.problemReporter, compilationResult, 0);
2359                                typeDeclaration = BinaryTypeConverter.buildTypeDeclaration(type, compilationUnit, compilationResult);
2360                        }
2361 
2362                        if(typeDeclaration != null) {
2363                                // build AST from snippet
2364                                Initializer fakeInitializer = parseSnippeInitializer(snippet, position, localVariableTypeNames, localVariableNames, localVariableModifiers, isStatic);
2365 
2366                                // merge AST
2367                                FieldDeclaration[] oldFields = typeDeclaration.fields;
2368                                FieldDeclaration[] newFields = null;
2369                                if (oldFields != null) {
2370                                        newFields = new FieldDeclaration[oldFields.length + 1];
2371                                        System.arraycopy(oldFields, 0, newFields, 0, oldFields.length);
2372                                        newFields[oldFields.length] = fakeInitializer;
2373                                } else {
2374                                        newFields = new FieldDeclaration[] {fakeInitializer};
2375                                }
2376                                typeDeclaration.fields = newFields;
2377 
2378                                if(DEBUG) {
2379                                        System.out.println("SNIPPET COMPLETION AST :"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2380                                        System.out.println(compilationUnit.toString());
2381                                }
2382 
2383                                if (compilationUnit.types != null) {
2384                                        try {
2385                                                this.lookupEnvironment.buildTypeBindings(compilationUnit, null /*no access restriction*/);
2386 
2387                                                if ((this.unitScope = compilationUnit.scope) != null) {
2388                                                        this.lookupEnvironment.completeTypeBindings(compilationUnit, true);
2389                                                        compilationUnit.scope.faultInTypes();
2390                                                        compilationUnit.resolve();
2391                                                }
2392                                        } catch (CompletionNodeFound e) {
2393                                                //                                        completionNodeFound = true;
2394                                                if (e.astNode != null) {
2395                                                        // if null then we found a problem in the completion node
2396                                                        contextAccepted = complete(e.astNode, this.parser.assistNodeParent, e.qualifiedBinding, e.scope, e.insideTypeAnnotation);
2397                                                }
2398                                        }
2399                                }
2400                                if(this.noProposal && this.problem != null) {
2401                                        if(!contextAccepted) {
2402                                                contextAccepted = true;
2403                                                this.requestor.acceptContext(new CompletionContext());
2404                                        }
2405                                        this.requestor.completionFailure(this.problem);
2406                                        if(DEBUG) {
2407                                                this.printDebug(this.problem);
2408                                        }
2409                                }
2410                        }
2411                }  catch (IndexOutOfBoundsException e) { // work-around internal failure - 1GEMF6D (added with fix of 99629)
2412                        if(DEBUG) {
2413                                System.out.println("Exception caught by CompletionEngine:"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2414                                e.printStackTrace(System.out);
2415                        }
2416                } catch (InvalidCursorLocation e) { // may eventually report a usefull error (added to fix 99629)
2417                        if(DEBUG) {
2418                                System.out.println("Exception caught by CompletionEngine:"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2419                                e.printStackTrace(System.out);
2420                        }
2421                } catch (AbortCompilation e) { // ignore this exception for now since it typically means we cannot find java.lang.Object (added with fix of 99629)
2422                        if(DEBUG) {
2423                                System.out.println("Exception caught by CompletionEngine:"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2424                                e.printStackTrace(System.out);
2425                        }
2426                } catch (CompletionNodeFound e){ // internal failure - bugs 5618 (added with fix of 99629)
2427                        if(DEBUG) {
2428                                System.out.println("Exception caught by CompletionEngine:"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2429                                e.printStackTrace(System.out);
2430                        }
2431                } catch(JavaScriptModelException e) {
2432                        // Do nothing
2433                }
2434                if(!contextAccepted) {
2435                        contextAccepted = true;
2436                        this.requestor.acceptContext(new CompletionContext());
2437                }
2438                if(this.requestor != null){
2439                        this.requestor.endReporting();
2440                }
2441        }
