2443        private Initializer parseSnippeInitializer(char[] snippet, int position, char[][] localVariableTypeNames, char[][] localVariableNames, int[] localVariableModifiers, boolean isStatic){
2444                StringBuffer prefix = new StringBuffer();
2445                prefix.append("public class FakeType {\n "); //$NON-NLS-1$
2446                if(isStatic) {
2447                        prefix.append("static "); //$NON-NLS-1$
2448                }
2449                prefix.append("{\n"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2450                for (int i = 0; i < localVariableTypeNames.length; i++) {
2451                        ASTNode.printModifiers(localVariableModifiers[i], prefix);
2452                        prefix.append(' ');
2453                        prefix.append(localVariableTypeNames[i]);
2454                        prefix.append(' ');
2455                        prefix.append(localVariableNames[i]);
2456                        prefix.append(';');
2457                }
2458 
2459                char[] fakeSource = CharOperation.concat(prefix.toString().toCharArray(), snippet, "}}".toCharArray());//$NON-NLS-1$
2460                this.offset = prefix.length();
2461 
2462                String encoding = this.compilerOptions.defaultEncoding;
2463                BasicCompilationUnit fakeUnit = new BasicCompilationUnit(
2464                        fakeSource,
2465                        null,
2466                        "FakeType.java", //$NON-NLS-1$
2467                        encoding);
2468 
2469                this.actualCompletionPosition = prefix.length() + position - 1;
2470 
2471                CompilationResult fakeResult = new CompilationResult(fakeUnit, 1, 1, this.compilerOptions.maxProblemsPerUnit);
2472                CompilationUnitDeclaration fakeAST = this.parser.dietParse(fakeUnit, fakeResult, this.actualCompletionPosition);
2473 
2474                parseBlockStatements(fakeAST, this.actualCompletionPosition);
2475 
2476                return (Initializer)fakeAST.types[0].fields[0];
2477        }

2479        /**
2480         * Ask the engine to compute a completion at the specified position
2481         * of the given compilation unit.
2482         *
2483         *  No return
2484         *      completion results are answered through a requestor.
2485         *
2486         *  @param sourceUnit org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.internal.compiler.env.ICompilationUnit
2487         *      the source of the current compilation unit.
2488         *
2489         *  @param completionPosition int
2490         *      a position in the source where the completion is taking place.
2491         *      This position is relative to the source provided.
2492         */
2493        public void complete(ICompilationUnit sourceUnit, int completionPosition, int pos) {
2494 
2495                if(DEBUG) {
2496                        System.out.print("COMPLETION IN "); //$NON-NLS-1$
2497                        System.out.print(sourceUnit.getFileName());
2498                        System.out.print(" AT POSITION "); //$NON-NLS-1$
2499                        System.out.println(completionPosition);
2500                        System.out.println("COMPLETION - Source :"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2501                        System.out.println(sourceUnit.getContents());
2502                }
2503                this.requestor.beginReporting();
2504                boolean contextAccepted = false;
2505                try {
2506                        this.fileName = sourceUnit.getFileName();
2507                        this.packageName=sourceUnit.getPackageName();
2508                        this.actualCompletionPosition = completionPosition - 1;
2509                        this.offset = pos;
2510                        // for now until we can change the UI.
2511                        CompilationResult result = new CompilationResult(sourceUnit, 1, 1, this.compilerOptions.maxProblemsPerUnit);
2512                        CompilationUnitDeclaration parsedUnit = this.parser.dietParse(sourceUnit, result, this.actualCompletionPosition);
2513                        //                boolean completionNodeFound = false;
2514                        if (parsedUnit != null) {
2515                                if(DEBUG) {
2516                                        System.out.println("COMPLETION - Diet AST :"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2517                                        System.out.println(parsedUnit.toString());
2518                                }
2519 
2520                                this.parser.inferTypes(parsedUnit, this.compilerOptions);
2521                                // scan the package & import statements first
2522                                if (parsedUnit.currentPackage instanceof CompletionOnPackageReference) {
2523                                        contextAccepted = true;
2524                                        this.buildContext(parsedUnit.currentPackage, null, null, null);
2525//                                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.PACKAGE_REF)) {
2526//                                                findPackages((CompletionOnPackageReference) parsedUnit.currentPackage);
2527//                                        }
2528                                        if(this.noProposal && this.problem != null) {
2529                                                this.requestor.completionFailure(this.problem);
2530                                                if(DEBUG) {
2531                                                        this.printDebug(this.problem);
2532                                                }
2533                                        }
2534                                        return;
2535                                }
2536 
2537                                ImportReference[] imports = parsedUnit.imports;
2538                                if (imports != null) {
2539                                        for (int i = 0, length = imports.length; i < length; i++) {
2540                                                ImportReference importReference = imports[i];
2541                                                if (importReference instanceof CompletionOnImportReference) {
2542                                                        this.lookupEnvironment.buildTypeBindings(parsedUnit, null /*no access restriction*/);
2543                                                        if ((this.unitScope = parsedUnit.scope) != null) {
2544                                                                contextAccepted = true;
2545                                                                this.buildContext(importReference, null, null, null);
2546 
2547                                                                setSourceRange(
2548                                                                        importReference.sourceStart,
2549                                                                        importReference.declarationSourceEnd);
2550 
2551                                                                char[][] oldTokens = importReference.tokens;
2552                                                                int tokenCount = oldTokens.length;
2553                                                                if (tokenCount == 1) {
2554                                                                        findImports((CompletionOnImportReference)importReference, true);
2555                                                                } else if(tokenCount > 1){
2556                                                                        this.insideQualifiedReference = true;
2557 
2558                                                                        char[] lastToken = oldTokens[tokenCount - 1];
2559                                                                        char[][] qualifierTokens = CharOperation.subarray(oldTokens, 0, tokenCount - 1);
2560 
2561                                                                        Binding binding = this.unitScope.getTypeOrPackage(qualifierTokens);
2562                                                                        if(binding != null) {
2563                                                                                if(binding instanceof PackageBinding) {
2564                                                                                        findImports((CompletionOnImportReference)importReference, false);
2565                                                                                } else {
2566                                                                                        ReferenceBinding ref = (ReferenceBinding) binding;
2567                                                                                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
2568                                                                                                this.findImportsOfMemberTypes(lastToken, ref);
2569                                                                                        }
2570                                                                                }
2571                                                                        }
2572                                                                }
2573 
2574                                                                if(this.noProposal && this.problem != null) {
2575                                                                        this.requestor.completionFailure(this.problem);
2576                                                                        if(DEBUG) {
2577                                                                                this.printDebug(this.problem);
2578                                                                        }
2579                                                                }
2580                                                        }
2581                                                        return;
2582                                                } else if(importReference instanceof CompletionOnKeyword) {
2583                                                        contextAccepted = true;
2584                                                        this.buildContext(importReference, null, null, null);
2585                                                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD)) {
2586                                                                setSourceRange(importReference.sourceStart, importReference.sourceEnd);
2587                                                                CompletionOnKeyword keyword = (CompletionOnKeyword)importReference;
2588                                                                findKeywords(keyword.getToken(), keyword.getPossibleKeywords(), false, false);
2589                                                        }
2590                                                        if(this.noProposal && this.problem != null) {
2591                                                                this.requestor.completionFailure(this.problem);
2592                                                                if(DEBUG) {
2593                                                                        this.printDebug(this.problem);
2594                                                                }
2595                                                        }
2596                                                        return;
2597                                                }
2598                                        }
2599                                }
2600 
2601                                if (parsedUnit.statements  != null) {
2602                                        try {
2603                                                this.lookupEnvironment.buildTypeBindings(parsedUnit, null /*no access restriction*/);
2604 
2605                                                if ((this.unitScope = parsedUnit.scope) != null) {
2606                                                        this.source = sourceUnit.getContents();
2607                                                        this.lookupEnvironment.completeTypeBindings(parsedUnit, true);
2608                                                        parsedUnit.scope.faultInTypes();
2609                                                        if (Parser.DO_DIET_PARSE)
2610                                                        parseBlockStatements(parsedUnit, this.actualCompletionPosition);
2611                                                        if(DEBUG) {
2612                                                                System.out.println("COMPLETION - AST :"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2613                                                                System.out.println(parsedUnit.toString());
2614                                                        }
2615                                                        parsedUnit.resolve();
2616                                                }
2617                                        } catch (CompletionNodeFound e) {
2618                                                //                                        completionNodeFound = true;
2619                                                if (e.astNode != null) {
2620                                                        if(DEBUG) {
2621                                                                System.out.print("COMPLETION - Completion node : "); //$NON-NLS-1$
2622                                                                System.out.println(e.astNode.toString());
2623                                                                if(this.parser.assistNodeParent != null) {
2624                                                                        System.out.print("COMPLETION - Parent Node : ");  //$NON-NLS-1$
2625                                                                        System.out.println(this.parser.assistNodeParent);
2626                                                                }
2627                                                        }
2628                                                        // if null then we found a problem in the completion node
2629                                                        contextAccepted = complete(e.astNode, this.parser.assistNodeParent, e.qualifiedBinding, e.scope, e.insideTypeAnnotation);
2630                                                }
2631                                        }
2632                                }
2633                                parsedUnit.cleanUp();
2634                        }
2635 
2636                        if(this.noProposal && this.problem != null) {
2637                                if(!contextAccepted) {
2638                                        contextAccepted = true;
2639                                        CompletionContext context = new CompletionContext();
2640                                        context.setOffset(completionPosition - this.offset);
2641                                        context.setTokenKind(CompletionContext.TOKEN_KIND_UNKNOWN);
2642                                        this.requestor.acceptContext(context);
2643                                }
2644                                this.requestor.completionFailure(this.problem);
2645                                if(DEBUG) {
2646                                        this.printDebug(this.problem);
2647                                }
2648                        }
2649                        /* Ignore package, import, class & interface keywords for now...
2650                                        if (!completionNodeFound) {
2651                                                if (parsedUnit == null || parsedUnit.types == null) {
2652                                                        // this is not good enough... can still be trying to define a second type
2653                                                        CompletionScanner scanner = (CompletionScanner) this.parser.scanner;
2654                                                        setSourceRange(scanner.completedIdentifierStart, scanner.completedIdentifierEnd);
2655                                                        findKeywords(scanner.completionIdentifier, mainDeclarations, null);
2656                                                }
2657                                                // currently have no way to know if extends/implements are possible keywords
2658                                        }
2659                        */
2660                } catch (IndexOutOfBoundsException e) { // work-around internal failure - 1GEMF6D
2661                        if(DEBUG) {
2662                                System.out.println("Exception caught by CompletionEngine:"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2663                                e.printStackTrace(System.out);
2664                        }
2665                } catch (InvalidCursorLocation e) { // may eventually report a usefull error
2666                        if(DEBUG) {
2667                                System.out.println("Exception caught by CompletionEngine:"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2668                                e.printStackTrace(System.out);
2669                        }
2670                } catch (AbortCompilation e) { // ignore this exception for now since it typically means we cannot find java.lang.Object
2671                        if(DEBUG) {
2672                                System.out.println("Exception caught by CompletionEngine:"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2673                                e.printStackTrace(System.out);
2674                        }
2675                } catch (CompletionNodeFound e){ // internal failure - bugs 5618
2676                        if(DEBUG) {
2677                                System.out.println("Exception caught by CompletionEngine:"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2678                                e.printStackTrace(System.out);
2679                        }
2680                } finally {
2681                        this.parser=null;
2682                        reset();
2683                        if(!contextAccepted) {
2684                                contextAccepted = true;
2685                                CompletionContext context = new CompletionContext();
2686                                context.setTokenKind(CompletionContext.TOKEN_KIND_UNKNOWN);
2687                                context.setOffset(completionPosition - this.offset);
2688                                this.requestor.acceptContext(context);
2689                        }
2690                        this.requestor.endReporting();
2691                }
2692        }
2693        private long computeTargetedElement(CompletionOnAnnotationOfType fakeNode) {
2694                ASTNode annotatedElement = fakeNode.potentialAnnotatedNode;
2695 
2696                if (annotatedElement instanceof TypeDeclaration) {
2697                        TypeDeclaration annotatedTypeDeclaration = (TypeDeclaration) annotatedElement;
2698                        if (TypeDeclaration.kind(annotatedTypeDeclaration.modifiers) == TypeDeclaration.ANNOTATION_TYPE_DECL) {
2699                                return TagBits.AnnotationForAnnotationType | TagBits.AnnotationForType;
2700                        }
2701                        return TagBits.AnnotationForType;
2702                } else if (annotatedElement instanceof FieldDeclaration) {
2703                        if (fakeNode.isParameter) {
2704                                return TagBits.AnnotationForParameter;
2705                        }
2706                        return TagBits.AnnotationForField;
2707                } else if (annotatedElement instanceof MethodDeclaration) {
2708                        return TagBits.AnnotationForMethod;
2709                } else if (annotatedElement instanceof Argument) {
2710                        return TagBits.AnnotationForParameter;
2711                } else if (annotatedElement instanceof ConstructorDeclaration) {
2712                        return TagBits.AnnotationForConstructor;
2713                } else if (annotatedElement instanceof LocalDeclaration) {
2714                        return TagBits.AnnotationForLocalVariable;
2715                } else if (annotatedElement instanceof ImportReference) {
2716                        return TagBits.AnnotationForPackage;
2717                }
2718                return 0;
2719        }

2721        private TypeBinding[] computeTypes(Expression[] arguments) {
2722                if (arguments == null) return null;
2723                int argsLength = arguments.length;
2724                TypeBinding[] argTypes = new TypeBinding[argsLength];
2725                for (int a = argsLength; --a >= 0;) {
2726                        argTypes[a] = arguments[a].resolvedType;
2727                }
2728                return argTypes;
2729        }
2730 
2731        private TypeBinding[] computeTypesIfCorrect(Expression[] arguments) {
2732                if (arguments == null) return null;
2733                int argsLength = arguments.length;
2734                TypeBinding[] argTypes = new TypeBinding[argsLength];
2735                for (int a = argsLength; --a >= 0;) {
2736                        TypeBinding typeBinding = arguments[a].resolvedType;
2737                        if(typeBinding == null || !typeBinding.isValidBinding()) return null;
2738                        argTypes[a] = typeBinding;
2739                }
2740                return argTypes;
2741        }

2743        private void findAnonymousType(
2744                ReferenceBinding currentType,
2745                TypeBinding[] argTypes,
2746                Scope scope,
2747                InvocationSite invocationSite) {
2748 
2749                if (currentType.isInterface()) {
2750                        char[] completion = CharOperation.NO_CHAR;
2751                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
2752                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
2753                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
2754                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE);
2755 
2756                        this.noProposal = false;
2757                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.ANONYMOUS_CLASS_DECLARATION)) {
2758                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.ANONYMOUS_CLASS_DECLARATION, this.actualCompletionPosition);
2759                                proposal.setDeclarationSignature(getSignature(currentType));
2760                                proposal.setDeclarationKey(currentType.computeUniqueKey());
2761                                proposal.setSignature(
2762                                                createMethodSignature(
2763                                                                CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR,
2764                                                                CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR,
2765                                                                CharOperation.NO_CHAR,
2766                                                                CharOperation.NO_CHAR));
2767                                //proposal.setOriginalSignature(null);
2768                                //proposal.setUniqueKey(null);
2769                                proposal.setDeclarationPackageName(currentType.qualifiedPackageName());
2770                                proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(currentType.qualifiedSourceName());
2771                                //proposal.setParameterPackageNames(null);
2772                                //proposal.setParameterTypeNames(null);
2773                                //proposal.setPackageName(null);
2774                                //proposal.setTypeName(null);
2775                                proposal.setCompletion(completion);
2776                                proposal.setFlags(Flags.AccPublic);
2777                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.endPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
2778                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
2779                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
2780                                if(DEBUG) {
2781                                        this.printDebug(proposal);
2782                                }
2783                        }
2784                } else {
2785                        findConstructors(
2786                                currentType,
2787                                argTypes,
2788                                scope,
2789                                invocationSite,
2790                                true);
2791                }

2794        private void findClassField(char[] token, TypeBinding receiverType, Scope scope) {
2795 
2796                if (token == null) return;
2797 
2798                if (token.length <= classField.length
2799                        && CharOperation.prefixEquals(token, classField, false /* ignore case */
2800                )) {
2801                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
2802                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
2803                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
2804                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(token, classField);
2805                        relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(scope.getJavaLangClass());
2806                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); //no access restriction for class field
2807                        relevance += R_NON_INHERITED;
2808 
2809                        this.noProposal = false;
2810                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF)) {
2811                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
2812                                //proposal.setDeclarationSignature(null);
2813                                char[] signature =
2814                                        createNonGenericTypeSignature(
2815                                                CharOperation.concatWith(JAVA_LANG, '.'),
2816                                                CLASS);
2817                                if (this.compilerOptions.sourceLevel > ClassFileConstants.JDK1_4) {
2818                                        // add type argument
2819                                        char[] typeArgument = getTypeSignature(receiverType);
2820                                        int oldLength = signature.length;
2821                                        int argumentLength = typeArgument.length;
2822                                        int newLength = oldLength + argumentLength + 2;
2823                                        System.arraycopy(signature, 0, signature = new char[newLength], 0, oldLength - 1);
2824                                        signature[oldLength - 1] = '<';
2825                                        System.arraycopy(typeArgument, 0, signature, oldLength , argumentLength);
2826                                        signature[newLength - 2] = '>';
2827                                        signature[newLength - 1] = ';';
2828                                }
2829                                proposal.setSignature(signature);
2830                                //proposal.setDeclarationPackageName(null);
2831                                //proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(null);
2832                                proposal.setPackageName(CharOperation.concatWith(JAVA_LANG, '.'));
2833                                proposal.setTypeName(CLASS);
2834                                proposal.setName(classField);
2835                                proposal.setCompletion(classField);
2836                                proposal.setFlags(Flags.AccStatic | Flags.AccPublic);
2837                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
2838                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
2839                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
2840                                if(DEBUG) {
2841                                        this.printDebug(proposal);
2842                                }
2843                        }
2844                }
2845        }

2847        private void findExceptionFromTryStatement(
2848                        char[] typeName,
2849                        ReferenceBinding exceptionType,
2850                        ReferenceBinding receiverType,
2851                        SourceTypeBinding invocationType,
2852                        BlockScope scope,
2853                        ObjectVector typesFound,
2854                        boolean searchSuperClasses) {
2855 
2856 
2857                if (searchSuperClasses) {
2858                        ReferenceBinding javaLangThrowable = scope.getJavaLangThrowable();
2859                        if (exceptionType != javaLangThrowable) {
2860                                ReferenceBinding superClass = exceptionType.superclass();
2861                                while(superClass != null && superClass != javaLangThrowable) {
2862                                        findExceptionFromTryStatement(typeName, superClass, receiverType, invocationType, scope, typesFound, false);
2863                                        superClass = superClass.superclass();
2864                                }
2865                        }
2866                }
2867 
2868                if (typeName.length > exceptionType.sourceName.length)
2869                        return;
2870 
2871                if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(typeName, exceptionType.sourceName, false/* ignore case */)
2872                                && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(typeName, exceptionType.sourceName)))
2873                        return;
2874 
2875                if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
2876                                exceptionType.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
2877                                !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(exceptionType))
2878                        return;
2879 
2880                if (this.options.checkVisibility) {
2881                        if (invocationType != null) {
2882                                if (receiverType != null) {
2883                                        if (!exceptionType.canBeSeenBy(receiverType, invocationType)) return;
2884                                } else {
2885                                        if (!exceptionType.canBeSeenBy(exceptionType, invocationType)) return;
2886                                }
2887                        } else if(!exceptionType.canBeSeenBy(this.unitScope.getDefaultPackage())) {
2888                                return;
2889                        }
2890                }
2891 
2892                for (int j = typesFound.size; --j >= 0;) {
2893                        ReferenceBinding otherType = (ReferenceBinding) typesFound.elementAt(j);
2894 
2895                        if (exceptionType == otherType)
2896                                return;
2897 
2898                        if (CharOperation.equals(exceptionType.sourceName, otherType.sourceName, true)) {
2899 
2900                                if (exceptionType.enclosingType().isSuperclassOf(otherType.enclosingType()))
2901                                        return;
2902 
2903                                if (otherType.enclosingType().isInterface())
2904                                        if (exceptionType.enclosingType()
2905                                                .implementsInterface(otherType.enclosingType(), true))
2906                                                return;
2907 
2908                                if (exceptionType.enclosingType().isInterface())
2909                                        if (otherType.enclosingType()
2910                                                .implementsInterface(exceptionType.enclosingType(), true))
2911                                                return;
2912                        }
2913                }
2914 
2915                typesFound.add(exceptionType);
2916 
2917                char[] completionName = exceptionType.sourceName();
2918 
2919                boolean isQualified = false;
2920 
2921                if(!this.insideQualifiedReference) {
2922                        isQualified = true;
2923 
2924                        char[] memberPackageName = exceptionType.qualifiedPackageName();
2925                        char[] memberTypeName = exceptionType.sourceName();
2926                        char[] memberEnclosingTypeNames = null;
2927 
2928                        ReferenceBinding enclosingType = exceptionType.enclosingType();
2929                        if (enclosingType != null) {
2930                                memberEnclosingTypeNames = exceptionType.enclosingType().qualifiedSourceName();
2931                        }
2932 
2933                        Scope currentScope = scope;
2934                        done : while (currentScope != null) { // done when a COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE is found
2935 
2936                                switch (currentScope.kind) {
2937 
2938                                        case Scope.METHOD_SCOPE :
2939                                        case Scope.BLOCK_SCOPE :
2940                                                BlockScope blockScope = (BlockScope) currentScope;
2941 
2942                                                for (int j = 0, length = blockScope.subscopeCount; j < length; j++) {
2943 
2944                                                        if (blockScope.subscopes[j] instanceof ClassScope) {
2945                                                                SourceTypeBinding localType =
2946                                                                        ((ClassScope) blockScope.subscopes[j]).referenceContext.binding;
2947 
2948                                                                if (localType == exceptionType) {
2949                                                                        isQualified = false;
2950                                                                        break done;
2951                                                                }
2952                                                        }
2953                                                }
2954                                                break;
2955 
2956                                        case Scope.CLASS_SCOPE :
2957                                                SourceTypeBinding type = ((ClassScope)currentScope).referenceContext.binding;
2958                                                ReferenceBinding[] memberTypes = type.memberTypes();
2959                                                if (memberTypes != null) {
2960                                                        for (int j = 0; j < memberTypes.length; j++) {
2961                                                                if (memberTypes[j] == exceptionType) {
2962                                                                        isQualified = false;
2963                                                                        break done;
2964                                                                }
2965                                                        }
2966                                                }
2967 
2968 
2969                                                break;
2970 
2971                                        case Scope.COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE :
2972                                                SourceTypeBinding[] types = ((CompilationUnitScope)currentScope).topLevelTypes;
2973                                                if (types != null) {
2974                                                        for (int j = 0; j < types.length; j++) {
2975                                                                if (types[j] == exceptionType) {
2976                                                                        isQualified = false;
2977                                                                        break done;
2978                                                                }
2979                                                        }
2980                                                }
2981                                                break done;
2982                                }
2983                                currentScope = currentScope.parent;
2984                        }
2985 
2986                        if (isQualified && mustQualifyType(memberPackageName, memberTypeName, memberEnclosingTypeNames, exceptionType.modifiers)) {
2987                                if (memberPackageName == null || memberPackageName.length == 0)
2988                                        if (this.unitScope != null && this.unitScope.getDefaultPackage().compoundName != CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR)
2989                                                return; // ignore types from the default package from outside it
2990                        } else {
2991                                isQualified = false;
2992                        }
2993 
2994                        if (isQualified) {
2995                                completionName =
2996                                        CharOperation.concat(
2997                                                        memberPackageName,
2998                                                        CharOperation.concat(
2999                                                                        memberEnclosingTypeNames,
3000                                                                        memberTypeName,
3001                                                                        '.'),
3002                                                        '.');
3003                        }
3004                }
3005 
3006                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
3007                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
3008                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
3009                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(typeName, exceptionType.sourceName);
3010                relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(exceptionType);
3011                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE);
3012                if(!insideQualifiedReference) {
3013                        relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(isQualified);
3014                }

3016                relevance += computeRelevanceForException();

3327        private char[][] findEnclosingTypeNames(Scope scope){
3328                char[][] excludedNames = new char[10][];
3329                int excludedNameCount = 0;
3330 
3331                Scope currentScope = scope;
3332                while(currentScope != null) {
3333                        switch (currentScope.kind) {
3334                                case Scope.CLASS_SCOPE :
3335                                        ClassScope classScope = (ClassScope) currentScope;
3336 
3337                                        TypeDeclaration typeDeclaration = classScope.referenceContext;
3338 
3339                                        if(excludedNameCount == excludedNames.length) {
3340                                                System.arraycopy(excludedNames, 0, excludedNames = new char[excludedNameCount * 2][], 0, excludedNameCount);
3341                                        }
3342                                        excludedNames[excludedNameCount++] = typeDeclaration.name;
3343 
3344                                        TypeParameter[] classTypeParameters = typeDeclaration.typeParameters;
3345                                        if(classTypeParameters != null) {
3346                                                for (int i = 0; i < classTypeParameters.length; i++) {
3347                                                        TypeParameter typeParameter = classTypeParameters[i];
3348                                                        if(excludedNameCount == excludedNames.length) {
3349                                                                System.arraycopy(excludedNames, 0, excludedNames = new char[excludedNameCount * 2][], 0, excludedNameCount);
3350                                                        }
3351                                                        excludedNames[excludedNameCount++] = typeParameter.name;
3352                                                }
3353                                        }
3354                                        break;
3355                                case Scope.METHOD_SCOPE :
3356                                        MethodScope methodScope = (MethodScope) currentScope;
3357                                        if(methodScope.referenceContext instanceof AbstractMethodDeclaration) {
3358                                                TypeParameter[] methodTypeParameters = ((AbstractMethodDeclaration)methodScope.referenceContext).typeParameters();
3359                                                if(methodTypeParameters != null) {
3360                                                        for (int i = 0; i < methodTypeParameters.length; i++) {
3361                                                                TypeParameter typeParameter = methodTypeParameters[i];
3362                                                                if(excludedNameCount == excludedNames.length) {
3363                                                                        System.arraycopy(excludedNames, 0, excludedNames = new char[excludedNameCount * 2][], 0, excludedNameCount);
3364                                                                }
3365                                                                excludedNames[excludedNameCount++] = typeParameter.name;
3366                                                        }
3367                                                }
3368                                        }
3369                                        break;
3370                        }
3371 
3372                        currentScope = currentScope.parent;
3373                }
3374 
3375                if(excludedNameCount == 0) {
3376                        return CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR;
3377                }
3378                System.arraycopy(excludedNames, 0, excludedNames = new char[excludedNameCount][], 0, excludedNameCount);
3379                return excludedNames;
3380        }

3399 
3400                ObjectVector newFieldsFound = new ObjectVector();
3401                // Inherited fields which are hidden by subclasses are filtered out
3402                // No visibility checks can be performed without the scope & invocationSite
3403 
3404                int fieldLength = fieldName.length;
3405                next : for (int f = fields.length; --f >= 0;) {
3406                        FieldBinding field = fields[f];
3407 
3408                        if (field.isSynthetic())        continue next;
3409 
3410                        if (onlyStaticFields && !field.isStatic()) continue next;
3411 
3412                        if (fieldLength > field.name.length) continue next;
3413 
3414                        if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(fieldName, field.name, false /* ignore case */)
3415                                        && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(fieldName, field.name)))        continue next;
3416 
3417                        if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
3418                                        field.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
3419                                        !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(field.declaringClass))
3420                                continue next;
3421 
3422                        if (this.options.checkVisibility
3423                                && !field.canBeSeenBy(receiverType, invocationSite, scope))        continue next;
3424 
3425                        boolean prefixRequired = false;
3426 
3427                        for (int i = fieldsFound.size; --i >= 0;) {
3428                                Object[] other = (Object[])fieldsFound.elementAt(i);
3429                                FieldBinding otherField = (FieldBinding) other[0];
3430                                ReferenceBinding otherReceiverType = (ReferenceBinding) other[1];
3431                                if (field == otherField && receiverType == otherReceiverType)
3432                                        continue next;
3433                                if (CharOperation.equals(field.name, otherField.name, true)) {
3434                                        if (field.declaringClass.isSuperclassOf(otherField.declaringClass))
3435                                                continue next;
3436                                        if (otherField.declaringClass.isInterface()) {
3437                                                if (field.declaringClass == scope.getJavaLangObject())
3438                                                        continue next;
3439                                                if (field.declaringClass.implementsInterface(otherField.declaringClass, true))
3440                                                        continue next;
3441                                        }
3442                                        if (field.declaringClass.isInterface())
3443                                                if (otherField.declaringClass.implementsInterface(field.declaringClass, true))
3444                                                        continue next;
3445                                        if(canBePrefixed) {
3446                                                prefixRequired = true;
3447                                        } else {
3448                                                continue next;
3449                                        }
3450                                }
3451                        }
3452 
3453                        for (int l = localsFound.size; --l >= 0;) {
3454                                LocalVariableBinding local = (LocalVariableBinding) localsFound.elementAt(l);
3455 
3456                                if (CharOperation.equals(field.name, local.name, true)) {
3457                                        SourceTypeBinding declarationType = scope.enclosingSourceType();
3458                                        if (declarationType.isAnonymousType() && declarationType != invocationScope.enclosingSourceType()) {
3459                                                continue next;
3460                                        }
3461                                        if(canBePrefixed) {
3462                                                prefixRequired = true;
3463                                        } else {
3464                                                continue next;
3465                                        }
3466                                        break;
3467                                }
3468                        }
3469 
3470                        newFieldsFound.add(new Object[]{field, receiverType});
3471 
3472                        char[] completion = field.name;
3473 
3474                        if(prefixRequired || this.options.forceImplicitQualification){
3475                                char[] prefix = computePrefix(scope.enclosingSourceType(), invocationScope.enclosingSourceType(), field.isStatic());
3476                                completion = CharOperation.concat(prefix,completion,'.');
3477                        }
3478 
3479                        // Special case for javadoc completion
3480                        if (this.assistNodeInJavadoc > 0) {
3481                                if (invocationSite instanceof CompletionOnJavadocFieldReference) {
3482                                        CompletionOnJavadocFieldReference fieldRef = (CompletionOnJavadocFieldReference) invocationSite;
3483                                        if (fieldRef.receiver.isThis()) {
3484                                                if (fieldRef.completeInText()) {
3485                                                        completion = CharOperation.concat(new char[] { '#' }, field.name);
3486                                                }
3487                                        } else if (fieldRef.completeInText()) {
3488                                                if (fieldRef.receiver instanceof JavadocSingleTypeReference) {
3489                                                        JavadocSingleTypeReference typeRef = (JavadocSingleTypeReference) fieldRef.receiver;
3490                                                        completion = CharOperation.concat(typeRef.token, field.name, '#');
3491                                                } else if (fieldRef.receiver instanceof JavadocQualifiedTypeReference) {
3492                                                        JavadocQualifiedTypeReference typeRef = (JavadocQualifiedTypeReference) fieldRef.receiver;
3493                                                        completion = CharOperation.concat(CharOperation.concatWith(typeRef.tokens, '.'), field.name, '#');
3494                                                }
3495                                        }
3496                                }
3497                        }
3498 
3499                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
3500                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
3501                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal(field);
3502                        if (fieldName != null) relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(fieldName, field.name);
3503                        relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(field.type);
3504                        relevance += computeRelevanceForStatic(onlyStaticFields, field.isStatic());
3505                        relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(prefixRequired);
3506                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE);
3507                        if (onlyStaticFields && this.insideQualifiedReference) {
3508                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInheritance(receiverType, field.declaringClass);
3509                        }
3510                        if (missingElements != null) {
3511                                relevance += computeRelevanceForMissingElements(missingElementsHaveProblems);
3512                        }
3513 
3514                        this.noProposal = false;
3515                        // Standard proposal
3516                        if (!this.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF, missingElements != null) && (this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.ONLY_INLINE_TAG) == 0) {
3517                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
3518                                proposal.setDeclarationSignature(getSignature(field.declaringClass));
3519                                proposal.setSignature(getSignature(field.type));
3520                                proposal.setDeclarationPackageName(field.declaringClass.qualifiedPackageName());
3521                                proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(field.declaringClass.qualifiedSourceName());
3522                                proposal.setPackageName(field.type.qualifiedPackageName());
3523                                proposal.setTypeName(field.type.qualifiedSourceName());
3524                                proposal.setName(field.name);
3525                                if (missingElements != null) {
3526                                        CompletionProposal[] subProposals = new CompletionProposal[missingElements.length];
3527                                        for (int i = 0; i < missingElements.length; i++) {
3528                                                subProposals[i] =
3529                                                        createRequiredTypeProposal(
3530                                                                        missingElements[i],
3531                                                                        missingElementsStarts[i],
3532                                                                        missingElementsEnds[i],
3533                                                                        relevance);
3534                                        }
3535                                        proposal.setRequiredProposals(subProposals);
3536                                }
3537                                proposal.setCompletion(completion);
3538                                proposal.setFlags(field.modifiers);
3539                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
3540                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
3541                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
3542                                if(DEBUG) {
3543                                        this.printDebug(proposal);
3544                                }
3545                        }
3546 
3547                        // Javadoc completions
3548                        if ((this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.TEXT) != 0 && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_FIELD_REF)) {
3549                                char[] javadocCompletion = inlineTagCompletion(completion, JavadocTagConstants.TAG_LINK);
3550                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_FIELD_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
3551                                proposal.setDeclarationSignature(getSignature(field.declaringClass));
3552                                proposal.setSignature(getSignature(field.type));
3553                                proposal.setDeclarationPackageName(field.declaringClass.qualifiedPackageName());
3554                                proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(field.declaringClass.qualifiedSourceName());
3555                                proposal.setPackageName(field.type.qualifiedPackageName());
3556                                proposal.setTypeName(field.type.qualifiedSourceName());
3557                                proposal.setName(field.name);
3558                                proposal.setCompletion(javadocCompletion);
3559                                proposal.setFlags(field.modifiers);
3560                                int start = (this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.REPLACE_TAG) != 0 ? this.javadocTagPosition : this.startPosition;
3561                                proposal.setReplaceRange(start - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
3562                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance+R_INLINE_TAG);
3563                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
3564                                if(DEBUG) {
3565                                        this.printDebug(proposal);
3566                                }
3567                                // Javadoc value completion for static fields
3568                                if (field.isStatic() && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_VALUE_REF)) {
3569                                        javadocCompletion = inlineTagCompletion(completion, JavadocTagConstants.TAG_VALUE);
3570                                        CompletionProposal valueProposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_VALUE_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
3571                                        valueProposal.setDeclarationSignature(getSignature(field.declaringClass));
3572                                        valueProposal.setSignature(getSignature(field.type));
3573                                        valueProposal.setDeclarationPackageName(field.declaringClass.qualifiedPackageName());
3574                                        valueProposal.setDeclarationTypeName(field.declaringClass.qualifiedSourceName());
3575                                        valueProposal.setPackageName(field.type.qualifiedPackageName());
3576                                        valueProposal.setTypeName(field.type.qualifiedSourceName());
3577                                        valueProposal.setName(field.name);
3578                                        valueProposal.setCompletion(javadocCompletion);
3579                                        valueProposal.setFlags(field.modifiers);
3580                                        valueProposal.setReplaceRange(start - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
3581                                        valueProposal.setRelevance(relevance+R_VALUE_TAG);
3582                                        this.requestor.accept(valueProposal);
3583                                        if(DEBUG) {
3584                                                this.printDebug(valueProposal);
3585                                        }
3586                                }
3587                        }
3588                }
3589 
3590                fieldsFound.addAll(newFieldsFound);
3591        }

3593        private void findFields(
3594                char[] fieldName,
3595                ReferenceBinding receiverType,
3596                Scope scope,
3597                ObjectVector fieldsFound,
3598                ObjectVector localsFound,
3599                boolean onlyStaticFields,
3600                InvocationSite invocationSite,
3601                Scope invocationScope,
3602                boolean implicitCall,
3603                boolean canBePrefixed,
3604                Binding[] missingElements,
3605                int[] missingElementsStarts,
3606                int[] missingElementsEnds,
3607                boolean missingElementsHaveProblems) {
3608 
3609                boolean notInJavadoc = this.assistNodeInJavadoc == 0;
3610                if (fieldName == null && notInJavadoc)
3611                        return;
3612 
3613                ReferenceBinding currentType = receiverType;
3614                ReferenceBinding[] interfacesToVisit = null;
3615                int nextPosition = 0;
3616                do {
3617                        ReferenceBinding[] itsInterfaces = currentType.superInterfaces();
3618                        if (notInJavadoc && itsInterfaces != Binding.NO_SUPERINTERFACES) {
3619                                if (interfacesToVisit == null) {
3620                                        interfacesToVisit = itsInterfaces;
3621                                        nextPosition = interfacesToVisit.length;
3622                                } else {
3623                                        int itsLength = itsInterfaces.length;
3624                                        if (nextPosition + itsLength >= interfacesToVisit.length)
3625                                                System.arraycopy(interfacesToVisit, 0, interfacesToVisit = new ReferenceBinding[nextPosition + itsLength + 5], 0, nextPosition);
3626                                        nextInterface : for (int a = 0; a < itsLength; a++) {
3627                                                ReferenceBinding next = itsInterfaces[a];
3628                                                for (int b = 0; b < nextPosition; b++)
3629                                                        if (next == interfacesToVisit[b]) continue nextInterface;
3630                                                interfacesToVisit[nextPosition++] = next;
3631                                        }
3632                                }
3633                        }
3634 
3635                        FieldBinding[] fields = currentType.availableFields();
3636                        if(fields != null && fields.length > 0) {
3637                                findFields(
3638                                        fieldName,
3639                                        fields,
3640                                        scope,
3641                                        fieldsFound,
3642                                        localsFound,
3643                                        onlyStaticFields,
3644                                        receiverType,
3645                                        invocationSite,
3646                                        invocationScope,
3647                                        implicitCall,
3648                                        canBePrefixed,
3649                                        missingElements,
3650                                        missingElementsStarts,
3651                                        missingElementsEnds,
3652                                        missingElementsHaveProblems);
3653                        }
3654                        
3655                        if (currentType instanceof SourceTypeBinding) {
3656                                SourceTypeBinding sourceType = (SourceTypeBinding) currentType;
3657                                for (int i = 0; i < sourceType.mixins.length; i++) {
3658                                        fields  = sourceType.mixins[i].availableFields();
3659                                        findFields(
3660                                                        fieldName,
3661                                                        fields,
3662                                                        scope,
3663                                                        fieldsFound,
3664                                                        localsFound,
3665                                                        onlyStaticFields,
3666                                                        receiverType,
3667                                                        invocationSite,
3668                                                        invocationScope,
3669                                                        implicitCall,
3670                                                        canBePrefixed,
3671                                                        missingElements,
3672                                                        missingElementsStarts,
3673                                                        missingElementsEnds,
3674                                                        missingElementsHaveProblems);
3675                                }
3676                        }
3677                        
3678                        currentType = currentType.superclass();
3679                } while (notInJavadoc && currentType != null);
3680 
3681                if (notInJavadoc && interfacesToVisit != null) {
3682                        for (int i = 0; i < nextPosition; i++) {
3683                                ReferenceBinding anInterface = interfacesToVisit[i];
3684                                FieldBinding[] fields = anInterface.availableFields();
3685                                if(fields !=  null) {
3686                                        findFields(
3687                                                fieldName,
3688                                                fields,
3689                                                scope,
3690                                                fieldsFound,
3691                                                localsFound,
3692                                                onlyStaticFields,
3693                                                receiverType,
3694                                                invocationSite,
3695                                                invocationScope,
3696                                                implicitCall,
3697                                                canBePrefixed,
3698                                                missingElements,
3699                                                missingElementsStarts,
3700                                                missingElementsEnds,
3701                                                missingElementsHaveProblems);
3702                                }
3703 
3704                                ReferenceBinding[] itsInterfaces = anInterface.superInterfaces();
3705                                if (itsInterfaces != Binding.NO_SUPERINTERFACES) {
3706                                        int itsLength = itsInterfaces.length;
3707                                        if (nextPosition + itsLength >= interfacesToVisit.length)
3708                                                System.arraycopy(interfacesToVisit, 0, interfacesToVisit = new ReferenceBinding[nextPosition + itsLength + 5], 0, nextPosition);
3709                                        nextInterface : for (int a = 0; a < itsLength; a++) {
3710                                                ReferenceBinding next = itsInterfaces[a];
3711                                                for (int b = 0; b < nextPosition; b++)
3712                                                        if (next == interfacesToVisit[b]) continue nextInterface;
3713                                                interfacesToVisit[nextPosition++] = next;
3714                                        }
3715                                }
3716                        }
3717                }
3718        }

3908        private void findFieldsAndMethodsFromFavorites(
3909                        char[] token,
3910                        Scope scope,
3911                        InvocationSite invocationSite,
3912                        Scope invocationScope,
3913                        ObjectVector localsFound,
3914                        ObjectVector fieldsFound,
3915                        ObjectVector methodsFound) {
3916 
3917                ImportBinding[] favoriteBindings = getFavoriteReferenceBindings(invocationScope);
3918 
3919                if (favoriteBindings != null && favoriteBindings.length > 0) {
3920                        for (int i = 0; i < favoriteBindings.length; i++) {
3921                                ImportBinding favoriteBinding = favoriteBindings[i];
3922                                switch (favoriteBinding.resolvedImport.kind()) {
3923                                        case Binding.FIELD:
3924                                                FieldBinding fieldBinding = (FieldBinding) favoriteBinding.resolvedImport;
3925                                                findFieldsFromFavorites(
3926                                                                token,
3927                                                                new FieldBinding[]{fieldBinding},
3928                                                                scope,
3929                                                                fieldsFound,
3930                                                                localsFound,
3931                                                                fieldBinding.declaringClass,
3932                                                                invocationSite,
3933                                                                invocationScope);
3934                                                break;
3935                                        case Binding.METHOD:
3936                                                MethodBinding methodBinding = (MethodBinding) favoriteBinding.resolvedImport;
3937                                                MethodBinding[] methods = methodBinding.declaringClass.availableMethods();
3938                                                long range;
3939                                                if ((range = ReferenceBinding.binarySearch(methodBinding.selector, methods)) >= 0) {
3940                                                        int start = (int) range, end = (int) (range >> 32);
3941                                                        int length = end - start + 1;
3942                                                        System.arraycopy(methods, start, methods = new MethodBinding[length], 0, length);
3943                                                } else {
3944                                                        methods = Binding.NO_METHODS;
3945                                                }
3946                                                findLocalMethodsFromFavorites(
3947                                                                token,
3948                                                                methods,
3949                                                                scope,
3950                                                                methodsFound,
3951                                                                methodBinding.declaringClass,
3952                                                                invocationSite,
3953                                                                invocationScope);
3954                                                break;
3955                                        case Binding.TYPE:
3956                                                ReferenceBinding referenceBinding = (ReferenceBinding) favoriteBinding.resolvedImport;
3957                                                if(favoriteBinding.onDemand) {
3958                                                        findFieldsFromFavorites(
3959                                                                        token,
3960                                                                        referenceBinding.availableFields(),
3961                                                                        scope,
3962                                                                        fieldsFound,
3963                                                                        localsFound,
3964                                                                        referenceBinding,
3965                                                                        invocationSite,
3966                                                                        invocationScope);
3967 
3968                                                        findLocalMethodsFromFavorites(
3969                                                                        token,
3970                                                                        referenceBinding.availableMethods(),
3971                                                                        scope,
3972                                                                        methodsFound,
3973                                                                        referenceBinding,
3974                                                                        invocationSite,
3975                                                                        invocationScope);
3976                                                }
3977                                                break;
3978                                }
3979                        }
3980                }
3981        }

4151        private void findFieldsFromFavorites(
4152                        char[] fieldName,
4153                        FieldBinding[] fields,
4154                        Scope scope,
4155                        ObjectVector fieldsFound,
4156                        ObjectVector localsFound,
4157                        ReferenceBinding receiverType,
4158                        InvocationSite invocationSite,
4159                        Scope invocationScope) {
4160 
4161                char[] typeName = CharOperation.concatWith(receiverType.compoundName, '.');
4162 
4163                int fieldLength = fieldName.length;
4164                next : for (int f = fields.length; --f >= 0;) {
4165                        FieldBinding field = fields[f];
4166 
4167                        if (field.isSynthetic())        continue next;
4168 
4169                        // only static fields must be proposed
4170                        if (!field.isStatic()) continue next;
4171 
4172                        if (fieldLength > field.name.length) continue next;
4173 
4174                        if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(fieldName, field.name, false /* ignore case */)
4175                                        && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(fieldName, field.name)))        continue next;
4176 
4177                        if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
4178                                        field.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
4179                                        !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(field.declaringClass))
4180                                continue next;
4181 
4182                        if (this.options.checkVisibility
4183                                && !field.canBeSeenBy(receiverType, invocationSite, scope))        continue next;
4184 
4185                        for (int i = fieldsFound.size; --i >= 0;) {
4186                                Object[] other = (Object[])fieldsFound.elementAt(i);
4187                                FieldBinding otherField = (FieldBinding) other[0];
4188 
4189                                if (field == otherField) continue next;
4190                        }
4191 
4192                        fieldsFound.add(new Object[]{field, receiverType});
4193 
4194                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();

4196                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal(field);

4199                        relevance += computeRelevanceForStatic(true, true);
4200                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE);

4324                ReferenceBinding[] memberTypes = ref.memberTypes();
4325

4329                        //                if (!wantClasses && memberType.isClass()) continue next;
4330                        //                if (!wantInterfaces && memberType.isInterface()) continue next;
4331

4333                                continue next;

4428        private void findImportsOfStaticMethods(char[] methodName, ReferenceBinding ref) {

4432                next : for (int m = methods.length; --m >= 0;) {
4433                        MethodBinding method = methods[m];
4434 
4435                        if (method.isSynthetic()) continue next;
4436 
4437                        if (method.isDefaultAbstract())        continue next;
4438 
4439                        if (method.isConstructor()) continue next;

4518

4528                                proposal.setCompletion(completion);
4529                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
4530                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
4531                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);

4578        private void findKeywords(char[] keyword, char[][] choices, boolean canCompleteEmptyToken, boolean staticFieldsAndMethodOnly) {
4579                if(choices == null || choices.length == 0) return;
4580 
4581                int length = keyword.length;
4582                if (canCompleteEmptyToken || length > 0)
4583                        for (int i = 0; i < choices.length; i++)
4584                                if (length <= choices[i].length
4585                                        && CharOperation.prefixEquals(keyword, choices[i], false /* ignore case */
4586                                )){
4587                                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
4588                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
4589                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
4590                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(keyword, choices[i]);
4591                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for keywors
4592                                        if (staticFieldsAndMethodOnly && this.insideQualifiedReference) relevance += R_NON_INHERITED;
4593 
4594                                        if(CharOperation.equals(choices[i], Keywords.TRUE) || CharOperation.equals(choices[i], Keywords.FALSE)) {
4595                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(TypeBinding.BOOLEAN);
4596                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(false);
4597                                        }
4598                                        this.noProposal = false;
4599                                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD)) {
4600                                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD, this.actualCompletionPosition);
4601                                                proposal.setName(choices[i]);
4602                                                proposal.setCompletion(choices[i]);
4603                                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
4604                                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
4605                                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
4606                                                if(DEBUG) {
4607                                                        this.printDebug(proposal);

4612        private void findTrueOrFalseKeywords(char[][] choices) {
