4646        private void findKeywordsForMember(char[] token, int modifiers) {
4647                char[][] keywords = new char[Keywords.COUNT][];
4648                int count = 0;
4649 
4650                // visibility
4651                if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccPrivate) == 0
4652                        && (modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccProtected) == 0
4653                        && (modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccPublic) == 0) {
4654                        keywords[count++] = Keywords.PROTECTED;
4655                        keywords[count++] = Keywords.PUBLIC;
4656                        if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccAbstract) == 0) {
4657                                keywords[count++] = Keywords.PRIVATE;
4658                        }
4659                }
4660 
4661                if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccAbstract) == 0) {
4662                        // abtract
4663                        if((modifiers & ~(ExtraCompilerModifiers.AccVisibilityMASK | ClassFileConstants.AccStatic)) == 0) {
4664                                keywords[count++] = Keywords.ABSTRACT;
4665                        }
4666 
4667                        // final
4668                        if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccFinal) == 0) {
4669                                keywords[count++] = Keywords.FINAL;
4670                        }
4671 
4672                        // static
4673                        if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccStatic) == 0) {
4674                                keywords[count++] = Keywords.STATIC;
4675                        }
4676 
4677                        boolean canBeField = true;
4678                        boolean canBeMethod = true;
4679                        boolean canBeType = true;
4680                        if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccNative) != 0
4681                                || (modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccStrictfp) != 0
4682                                || (modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccSynchronized) != 0) {
4683                                canBeField = false;
4684                                canBeType = false;
4685                        }
4686 
4687                        if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccTransient) != 0
4688                                || (modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccVolatile) != 0) {
4689                                canBeMethod = false;
4690                                canBeType = false;
4691                        }
4692 
4693                        if(canBeField) {
4694                                // transient
4695                                if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccTransient) == 0) {
4696                                        keywords[count++] = Keywords.TRANSIENT;
4697                                }
4698 
4699                                // volatile
4700                                if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccVolatile) == 0) {
4701                                        keywords[count++] = Keywords.VOLATILE;
4702                                }
4703                        }
4704 
4705                        if(canBeMethod) {
4706                                // native
4707                                if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccNative) == 0) {
4708                                        keywords[count++] = Keywords.NATIVE;
4709                                }
4710 
4711                                // strictfp
4712                                if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccStrictfp) == 0) {
4713                                        keywords[count++] = Keywords.STRICTFP;
4714                                }
4715 
4716                                // synchronized
4717                                if((modifiers & ClassFileConstants.AccSynchronized) == 0) {
4718                                        keywords[count++] = Keywords.SYNCHRONIZED;
4719                                }
4720                        }
4721 
4722                        if(canBeType) {
4723                                keywords[count++] = Keywords.CLASS;
4724                                keywords[count++] = Keywords.INTERFACE;
4725                        }
4726                } else {
4727                        // class
4728                        keywords[count++] = Keywords.CLASS;
4729                        keywords[count++] = Keywords.INTERFACE;
4730                }
4731                System.arraycopy(keywords, 0, keywords = new char[count][], 0, count);
4732 
4733                findKeywords(token, keywords, false, false);
4734        }
4735 
4736        // Helper method for findMemberTypes(char[], ReferenceBinding, Scope)
4737        private void findMemberTypes(
4738                char[] typeName,
4739                ReferenceBinding[] memberTypes,
4740                ObjectVector typesFound,
4741                ReferenceBinding receiverType,
4742                SourceTypeBinding invocationType,
4743                boolean staticOnly,
4744                boolean staticFieldsAndMethodOnly,
4745                boolean fromStaticImport,
4746                boolean checkQualification,
4747                Scope scope) {
4748 
4749                // Inherited member types which are hidden by subclasses are filtered out
4750                // No visibility checks can be performed without the scope & invocationSite
4751                int typeLength = typeName.length;
4752                next : for (int m = memberTypes.length; --m >= 0;) {
4753                        ReferenceBinding memberType = memberTypes[m];
4754                        //                if (!wantClasses && memberType.isClass()) continue next;
4755                        //                if (!wantInterfaces && memberType.isInterface()) continue next;
4756 
4757                        if (staticOnly && !memberType.isStatic()) continue next;
4758 
4759                        if (isForbidden(memberType)) continue next;
4760 
4761                        if (typeLength > memberType.sourceName.length)
4762                                continue next;
4763 
4764                        if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(typeName, memberType.sourceName, false/* ignore case */)
4765                                        && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(typeName, memberType.sourceName)))
4766                                continue next;
4767 
4768                        if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
4769                                        memberType.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
4770                                        !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(memberType))
4771                                continue next;
4772 
4773                        if (this.options.checkVisibility) {
4774                                if (invocationType != null && !memberType.canBeSeenBy(receiverType, invocationType)) {
4775                                        continue next;
4776                                } else if(invocationType == null && !memberType.canBeSeenBy(this.unitScope.getDefaultPackage())) {
4777                                        continue next;
4778                                }
4779                        }
4780 
4781                        for (int i = typesFound.size; --i >= 0;) {
4782                                ReferenceBinding otherType = (ReferenceBinding) typesFound.elementAt(i);
4783 
4784                                if (memberType == otherType)
4785                                        continue next;
4786 
4787                                if (CharOperation.equals(memberType.sourceName, otherType.sourceName, true)) {
4788 
4789                                        if (memberType.enclosingType().isSuperclassOf(otherType.enclosingType()))
4790                                                continue next;
4791 
4792                                        if (otherType.enclosingType().isInterface())
4793                                                if (memberType.enclosingType()
4794                                                        .implementsInterface(otherType.enclosingType(), true))
4795                                                        continue next;
4796 
4797                                        if (memberType.enclosingType().isInterface())
4798                                                if (otherType.enclosingType()
4799                                                        .implementsInterface(memberType.enclosingType(), true))
4800                                                        continue next;
4801                                }
4802                        }
4803 
4804                        typesFound.add(memberType);
4805 
4806                        if(!this.insideQualifiedReference) {
4807                                if(this.assistNodeIsClass) {
4808                                        if(!memberType.isClass()) continue next;
4809                                } else if(this.assistNodeIsInterface) {
4810                                        if(!memberType.isInterface() && !memberType.isAnnotationType()) continue next;
4811                                } else if (this.assistNodeIsAnnotation) {
4812                                        if(!memberType.isAnnotationType()) continue next;
4813                                }
4814                        }
4815 
4816                        char[] completionName = memberType.sourceName();
4817 
4818                        boolean isQualified = false;
4819                        if(checkQualification && !fromStaticImport) {
4820                                char[] memberPackageName = memberType.qualifiedPackageName();
4821                                char[] memberTypeName = memberType.sourceName();
4822                                char[] memberEnclosingTypeNames = memberType.enclosingType().qualifiedSourceName();
4823                                if (mustQualifyType(memberPackageName, memberTypeName, memberEnclosingTypeNames, memberType.modifiers)) {
4824                                        if (memberPackageName == null || memberPackageName.length == 0)
4825                                                if (this.unitScope != null && this.unitScope.getDefaultPackage().compoundName != CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR)
4826                                                        break next; // ignore types from the default package from outside it
4827                                        isQualified = true;
4828                                        completionName =
4829                                                CharOperation.concat(
4830                                                                memberPackageName,
4831                                                                CharOperation.concat(
4832                                                                                memberEnclosingTypeNames,
4833                                                                                memberTypeName,
4834                                                                                '.'),
4835                                                                '.');
4836                                }
4837                        }
4838 
4839                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
4840                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
4841                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
4842                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(typeName, memberType.sourceName);
4843                        relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(memberType);
4844                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE);
4845                        if(!insideQualifiedReference) {
4846                                relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(isQualified);
4847                        }
4848                        if (staticFieldsAndMethodOnly && this.insideQualifiedReference) relevance += R_NON_INHERITED; // This criterion doesn't concern types and is added to be balanced with field and method relevance.
4849 
4850                        if (memberType.isAnnotationType()) {
4851                                relevance += computeRelevanceForAnnotation();
4852                                relevance += computeRelevanceForAnnotationTarget(memberType);
4853                        } else if (memberType.isClass()) {
4854                                relevance += computeRelevanceForClass();
4855                                relevance += computeRelevanceForException(memberType.sourceName);
4856                        } else if(memberType.isEnum()) {
4857                                relevance += computeRelevanceForEnum();
4858                        } else if(memberType.isInterface()) {
4859                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterface();
4860                        }
4861 
4862                        this.noProposal = false;
4863                        createTypeProposal(memberType, memberType.qualifiedSourceName(), IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE, completionName, relevance);
4864                }
4865        }

4879                                typeInvocation,
4880                                staticOnly,
4881                                staticFieldsAndMethodOnly,

4885                                null,

4888        private void findMemberTypes(
4889                char[] typeName,
4890                ReferenceBinding receiverType,
4891                Scope scope,
4892                SourceTypeBinding typeInvocation,
4893                boolean staticOnly,
4894                boolean staticFieldsAndMethodOnly,
4895                boolean fromStaticImport,
4896                boolean checkQualification,
4897                boolean proposeAllMemberTypes,
4898                SourceTypeBinding typeToIgnore,
4899                ObjectVector typesFound) {
4900 
4901                ReferenceBinding currentType = receiverType;
4902                if (typeName == null)
4903                        return;
4904 
4905                if (this.assistNodeIsSuperType && !this.insideQualifiedReference) return; // we're trying to find a supertype
4906 
4907                if (currentType.superInterfaces() == null)
4908                        return; // we're trying to find a supertype
4909 
4910 
4911                if (this.insideQualifiedReference
4912                        || typeName.length == 0) { // do not search up the hierarchy
4913 
4914                        findMemberTypes(
4915                                typeName,
4916                                currentType.memberTypes(),
4917                                typesFound,
4918                                receiverType,
4919                                typeInvocation,
4920                                staticOnly,
4921                                staticFieldsAndMethodOnly,
4922                                fromStaticImport,
4923                                checkQualification,
4924                                scope);
4925                        return;
4926                }
4927 
4928                ReferenceBinding[] interfacesToVisit = null;
4929                int nextPosition = 0;
4930 
4931                do {
4932                        ReferenceBinding[] itsInterfaces = currentType.superInterfaces();
4933                        if (itsInterfaces != Binding.NO_SUPERINTERFACES) {
4934                                if (interfacesToVisit == null) {
4935                                        interfacesToVisit = itsInterfaces;
4936                                        nextPosition = interfacesToVisit.length;
4937                                } else {
4938                                        int itsLength = itsInterfaces.length;
4939                                        if (nextPosition + itsLength >= interfacesToVisit.length)
4940                                                System.arraycopy(interfacesToVisit, 0, interfacesToVisit = new ReferenceBinding[nextPosition + itsLength + 5], 0, nextPosition);
4941                                        nextInterface : for (int a = 0; a < itsLength; a++) {
4942                                                ReferenceBinding next = itsInterfaces[a];
4943                                                for (int b = 0; b < nextPosition; b++)
4944                                                        if (next == interfacesToVisit[b]) continue nextInterface;
4945                                                interfacesToVisit[nextPosition++] = next;
4946                                        }
4947                                }
4948                        }
4949 
4950                        findMemberTypes(
4951                                typeName,
4952                                currentType.memberTypes(),
4953                                typesFound,
4954                                receiverType,
4955                                typeInvocation,
4956                                staticOnly,
4957                                staticFieldsAndMethodOnly,
4958                                fromStaticImport,
4959                                checkQualification,
4960                                scope);
4961 
4962                        currentType = currentType.superclass();
4963                } while (currentType != null);
4964 
4965                if(proposeAllMemberTypes) {
4966                        ReferenceBinding[] memberTypes = receiverType.memberTypes();
4967                        for (int i = 0; i < memberTypes.length; i++) {
4968                                if(memberTypes[i] != typeToIgnore) {
4969                                        findSubMemberTypes(
4970                                                typeName,
4971                                                memberTypes[i],
4972                                                scope,
4973                                                typeInvocation,
4974                                                staticOnly,
4975                                                staticFieldsAndMethodOnly,
4976                                                fromStaticImport,
4977                                                typesFound);
4978                                }
4979                        }
4980                }
4981 
4982                if (interfacesToVisit != null) {
4983                        for (int i = 0; i < nextPosition; i++) {
4984                                ReferenceBinding anInterface = interfacesToVisit[i];
4985                                findMemberTypes(
4986                                        typeName,
4987                                        anInterface.memberTypes(),
4988                                        typesFound,
4989                                        receiverType,
4990                                        typeInvocation,
4991                                        staticOnly,
4992                                        staticFieldsAndMethodOnly,
4993                                        fromStaticImport,
4994                                        checkQualification,
4995                                        scope);
4996 
4997                                ReferenceBinding[] itsInterfaces = anInterface.superInterfaces();
4998                                if (itsInterfaces != Binding.NO_SUPERINTERFACES) {
4999                                        int itsLength = itsInterfaces.length;
5000                                        if (nextPosition + itsLength >= interfacesToVisit.length)
5001                                                System.arraycopy(interfacesToVisit, 0, interfacesToVisit = new ReferenceBinding[nextPosition + itsLength + 5], 0, nextPosition);
5002                                        nextInterface : for (int a = 0; a < itsLength; a++) {
5003                                                ReferenceBinding next = itsInterfaces[a];
5004                                                for (int b = 0; b < nextPosition; b++)
5005                                                        if (next == interfacesToVisit[b]) continue nextInterface;
5006                                                interfacesToVisit[nextPosition++] = next;
5007                                        }
5008                                }
5009                        }
5010                }

5013        /*
5014         * Find javadoc parameter names.
5015         */
5016        private void findJavadocParamNames(char[] token, char[][] missingParams, boolean isTypeParam) {
5017 
5018                if (missingParams == null) return;
5019 
5020                // Get relevance
5021                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
5022                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
5023                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for param name
5024                if (!isTypeParam) relevance += R_INTERESTING;
5025 
5026                // Propose missing param
5027                int length = missingParams.length;
5028                relevance += length;
5029                for (int i=0; i<length; i++) {
5030                        char[] argName = missingParams[i];
5031                        if (token == null || CharOperation.prefixEquals(token, argName)) {
5032 
5033                                this.noProposal = false;
5034                                if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_PARAM_REF)) {
5035                                        CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_PARAM_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
5036                                        proposal.setName(argName);
5037                                        char[] completion = isTypeParam ? CharOperation.concat('<', argName, '>') : argName;
5038                                        proposal.setCompletion(completion);
5039                                        proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
5040                                        proposal.setRelevance(--relevance);
5041                                        this.requestor.accept(proposal);
5042                                        if (DEBUG) {
5043                                                this.printDebug(proposal);
5044                                        }
5045                                }
5046                        }
5047                }
5048        }

5100        private void findInterfacesMethods(

5179        private void findImplicitMessageSends(
5180                char[] token,
5181                TypeBinding[] argTypes,
5182                Scope scope,
5183                InvocationSite invocationSite,
5184                Scope invocationScope) {
5185 
5186                if (token == null)
5187                        return;
5188 
5189                boolean staticsOnly = false;
5190                // need to know if we're in a static context (or inside a constructor)
5191                ObjectVector methodsFound = new ObjectVector();
5192 
5193                done : while (true) { // done when a COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE is found
5194 
5195                        switch (scope.kind) {
5196 
5197                                case Scope.METHOD_SCOPE :
5198                                        // handle the error case inside an explicit constructor call (see MethodScope>>findField)
5199                                        MethodScope methodScope = (MethodScope) scope;
5200                                        staticsOnly |= methodScope.isStatic | methodScope.isConstructorCall;
5201                                        break;
5202 
5203                                case Scope.CLASS_SCOPE :
5204                                        ClassScope classScope = (ClassScope) scope;
5205                                        SourceTypeBinding enclosingType = classScope.getReferenceBinding();

5210                                                enclosingType,

5215                                                false,

5217                                                invocationScope,
5218                                                true,
5219                                                false,
5220                                                true,
5221                                                null,
5222                                                null,
5223                                                null,
5224                                                false);
5225                                        staticsOnly |= enclosingType.isStatic();
5226                                        break;
5227 
5228                                case Scope.COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE :

5243                                                true,
5244                                                false,
5245                                                true,
5246                                                null,
5247                                                null,

5249                                                false);
5250                                        break done;
5251                        }

5253                }

5256        // Helper method for findMethods(char[], TypeBinding[], ReferenceBinding, Scope, ObjectVector, boolean, boolean, boolean)
5257        private void findLocalMethods(
5258                char[] methodName,
5259                TypeBinding[] typeArgTypes,
5260                TypeBinding[] argTypes,

5264                ObjectVector methodsFound,

5290

5292 
5293                        if (method.isConstructor()) continue next;
5294 
5295                        if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&

5301                        //if (expectedTypesPtr > -1 && method.returnType == BaseTypes.VoidBinding) continue next;

5306                                && !method.canBeSeenBy(receiverType, invocationSite, scope)) continue next;
5307

5309                                methodsFound.add(new Object[]{method, receiverType});
5310                                continue next;
5311                        }
5312 
5313                        if (exactMatch) {
5314                                if (!CharOperation.equals(methodName, method.selector, false /* ignore case */)) {
5315                                        continue next;
5316                                }
5317                        } else {

5320                                                && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(methodName, method.selector))) {
5321                                        continue next;
5322                                }
5323                        }
5324 
5325                        if (minTypeArgLength != 0 && minTypeArgLength != method.typeVariables.length)
5326                                continue next;
5327

5329                                method = scope.environment().createParameterizedGenericMethod(method, typeArgTypes);
5330                        }

5336                                if (argTypes[a] != null) { // can be null if it could not be resolved properly
5337                                        if (!argTypes[a].isCompatibleWith(method.parameters[a])) {
5338                                                continue next;
5339                                        }
5340                                }
5341                        }
5342 
5343                        boolean prefixRequired = false;
5344 
5345                        for (int i = methodsFound.size; --i >= 0;) {

5348                                ReferenceBinding otherReceiverType = (ReferenceBinding) other[1];
5349                                if (method == otherMethod && receiverType == otherReceiverType)
5350                                        continue next;
5351

5354                                                if (lookupEnvironment.methodVerifier().doesMethodOverride(otherMethod, method)) {
5355                                                        if (!superCall || !otherMethod.declaringClass.isInterface()) {
5356                                                                continue next;
5357                                                        }
5358                                                }
5359                                        } else {
5360                                                if (lookupEnvironment.methodVerifier().doesMethodOverride(otherMethod, method)) {

5362

5365

5367                                                        }
5368                                                }
5369                                        }
5370                                }
5371                        }

5381//                                        }

5383//                        }

5388

5392                                parameterTypeNames[i] = type.qualifiedSourceName();

5397

5399 
5400                        // Special case for completion in javadoc
5401                        if (this.assistNodeInJavadoc > 0) {
5402                                Expression receiver = null;
5403                                if (invocationSite instanceof CompletionOnJavadocMessageSend) {
5404                                        CompletionOnJavadocMessageSend msg = (CompletionOnJavadocMessageSend) invocationSite;
5405                                        receiver = msg.receiver;
5406                                } else if (invocationSite instanceof CompletionOnJavadocFieldReference) {
5407                                        CompletionOnJavadocFieldReference fieldRef = (CompletionOnJavadocFieldReference) invocationSite;
5408                                        receiver = fieldRef.receiver;
5409                                }
5410                                if (receiver != null) {
5411                                        StringBuffer javadocCompletion = new StringBuffer();
5412                                        if (receiver.isThis()) {
5413                                                if ((this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.TEXT) != 0) {
5414                                                        javadocCompletion.append('#');
5415                                                }
5416                                        } else if ((this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.TEXT) != 0) {
5417                                                if (receiver instanceof JavadocSingleTypeReference) {
5418                                                        JavadocSingleTypeReference typeRef = (JavadocSingleTypeReference) receiver;
5419                                                        javadocCompletion.append(typeRef.token);
5420                                                        javadocCompletion.append('#');
5421                                                } else if (receiver instanceof JavadocQualifiedTypeReference) {

5425                                                                if (t>0) javadocCompletion.append('.');
5426                                                                javadocCompletion.append(typeRef.tokens[t]);
5427                                                        }
5428                                                        javadocCompletion.append('#');
5429                                                }
5430                                        }
5431                                        javadocCompletion.append(method.selector);
5432                                        // Append parameters types
5433                                        javadocCompletion.append('(');
5434                                        if (method.parameters != null) {
5435                                                boolean isVarargs = method.isVarargs();
5436                                                for (int p=0, ln=method.parameters.length; p<ln; p++) {

5438                                                        TypeBinding argTypeBinding = method.parameters[p];
5439                                                        if (isVarargs && p == ln - 1)  {
5440                                                                createVargsType(argTypeBinding.erasure(), javadocCompletion);
5441                                                        } else {
5442                                                                createType(argTypeBinding.erasure(), javadocCompletion);
5443                                                        }
5444                                                }
5445                                        }
5446                                        javadocCompletion.append(')');
5447                                        completion = javadocCompletion.toString().toCharArray();
5448                                }
5449                        } else {
5450                                // nothing to insert - do not want to replace the existing selector & arguments
5451                                if (!exactMatch) {
5452                                        if (this.source != null
5453                                                && this.source.length > this.endPosition
5454                                                && this.source[this.endPosition] == '(')
5455                                                completion = method.selector;
5456                                        else
5457                                                completion = CharOperation.concat(method.selector, new char[] { '(', ')' });

5459                                        if(prefixRequired && (this.source != null)) {
5460                                                completion = CharOperation.subarray(this.source, this.startPosition, this.endPosition);
5461                                        } else {
5462                                                this.startPosition = this.endPosition;
5463                                        }

5465 
5466                                if(prefixRequired || this.options.forceImplicitQualification){
5467                                        char[] prefix = computePrefix(scope.enclosingSourceType(), invocationScope.enclosingSourceType(), method.isStatic());
5468                                        completion = CharOperation.concat(prefix,completion,'.');
5469                                }
5470                        }
5471 
5472                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
5473                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
5474                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
5475                        if (methodName != null) relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(methodName, method.selector);
5476                        relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(method.returnType);
5477                        relevance += computeRelevanceForStatic(onlyStaticMethods, method.isStatic());
5478                        relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(prefixRequired);
5479                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE);
5480                        if (onlyStaticMethods && this.insideQualifiedReference) {
5481                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInheritance(receiverType, method.declaringClass);
5482                        }
5483                        if (missingElements != null) {
5484                                relevance += computeRelevanceForMissingElements(missingElementsHaveProblems);
5485                        }
5486 
5487                        this.noProposal = false;
5488                        // Standard proposal
5489                        if(!this.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF, missingElements != null) && (this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.ONLY_INLINE_TAG) == 0) {
5490                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
5491                                proposal.setDeclarationSignature(getSignature(method.declaringClass));
5492                                proposal.setSignature(getSignature(method));
5493                                MethodBinding original = method.original();
5494                                if(original != method) {
5495                                        proposal.setOriginalSignature(getSignature(original));
5496                                }
5497                                proposal.setDeclarationPackageName(method.declaringClass.qualifiedPackageName());
5498                                proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(method.declaringClass.qualifiedSourceName());
5499                                proposal.setParameterPackageNames(parameterPackageNames);
5500                                proposal.setParameterTypeNames(parameterTypeNames);
5501                                proposal.setPackageName(method.returnType.qualifiedPackageName());
5502                                proposal.setTypeName(method.returnType.qualifiedSourceName());
5503                                proposal.setName(method.selector);
5504                                if (missingElements != null) {
5505                                        CompletionProposal[] subProposals = new CompletionProposal[missingElements.length];
5506                                        for (int i = 0; i < missingElements.length; i++) {
5507                                                subProposals[i] =
5508                                                        createRequiredTypeProposal(
5509                                                                        missingElements[i],
5510                                                                        missingElementsStarts[i],
5511                                                                        missingElementsEnds[i],
5512                                                                        relevance);
5513                                        }
5514                                        proposal.setRequiredProposals(subProposals);
5515                                }
5516                                proposal.setCompletion(completion);
5517                                proposal.setFlags(method.modifiers);
5518                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
5519                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
5520                                if(parameterNames != null) proposal.setParameterNames(parameterNames);
5521                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
5522                                if(DEBUG) {
5523                                        this.printDebug(proposal);
5524                                }
5525                        }
5526 
5527                        // Javadoc proposal
5528                        if ((this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.TEXT) != 0 && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_METHOD_REF)) {
5529                                char[] javadocCompletion = inlineTagCompletion(completion, JavadocTagConstants.TAG_LINK);
5530                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_METHOD_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
5531                                proposal.setDeclarationSignature(getSignature(method.declaringClass));
5532                                proposal.setSignature(getSignature(method));
5533                                MethodBinding original = method.original();
5534                                if(original != method) {
5535                                        proposal.setOriginalSignature(getSignature(original));
5536                                }
5537                                proposal.setDeclarationPackageName(method.declaringClass.qualifiedPackageName());
5538                                proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(method.declaringClass.qualifiedSourceName());
5539                                proposal.setParameterPackageNames(parameterPackageNames);
5540                                proposal.setParameterTypeNames(parameterTypeNames);
5541                                proposal.setPackageName(method.returnType.qualifiedPackageName());
5542                                proposal.setTypeName(method.returnType.qualifiedSourceName());
5543                                proposal.setName(method.selector);
5544                                proposal.setCompletion(javadocCompletion);
5545                                proposal.setFlags(method.modifiers);
5546                                int start = (this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.REPLACE_TAG) != 0 ? this.javadocTagPosition : this.startPosition;
5547                                proposal.setReplaceRange(start - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
5548                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance+R_INLINE_TAG);
5549                                if(parameterNames != null) proposal.setParameterNames(parameterNames);
5550                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
5551                                if(DEBUG) {

5553                                }

5556                }

5558                methodsFound.addAll(newMethodsFound);

5561        private void findLocalMethodsFromFavorites(
5562                        char[] methodName,
5563                        MethodBinding[] methods,
5564                        Scope scope,
5565                        ObjectVector methodsFound,
5566                        ReferenceBinding receiverType,
5567                        InvocationSite invocationSite,
5568                        Scope invocationScope) {
5569 
5570                        char[] typeName = CharOperation.concatWith(receiverType.compoundName, '.');
5571 
5572                        int methodLength = methodName.length;
5573 
5574                        next : for (int f = methods.length; --f >= 0;) {
5575                                MethodBinding method = methods[f];
5576 
5577                                if (method.isSynthetic()) continue next;
5578 
5579                                if (method.isDefaultAbstract())        continue next;
5580 
5581                                if (method.isConstructor()) continue next;
5582 
5583                                if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
5584                                                method.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
5585                                                !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(method.declaringClass))
5586                                        continue next;
5587 
5588                                if (!method.isStatic()) continue next;
5589 
5590                                if (this.options.checkVisibility
5591                                        && !method.canBeSeenBy(receiverType, invocationSite, scope)) continue next;
5592 
5593                                if (methodLength > method.selector.length) continue next;
5594 
5595                                if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(methodName, method.selector, false /* ignore case */)
5596                                                && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(methodName, method.selector))) {
5597                                        continue next;
5598                                }
5599 
5600                                for (int i = methodsFound.size; --i >= 0;) {
5601                                        Object[] other = (Object[]) methodsFound.elementAt(i);
5602                                        MethodBinding otherMethod = (MethodBinding) other[0];
5603 
5604                                        if (method == otherMethod) continue next;
5605 
5606                                        if (CharOperation.equals(method.selector, otherMethod.selector, true)) {
5607                                                if (lookupEnvironment.methodVerifier().doesMethodOverride(otherMethod, method)) {
5608                                                        continue next;
5609                                                }
5610                                        }
5611                                }
5612 
5613                                boolean proposeStaticImport = !(this.compilerOptions.complianceLevel < ClassFileConstants.JDK1_5) &&
5614                                        this.options.suggestStaticImport;
5615 
5616                                boolean isAlreadyImported = false;
5617                                if (!proposeStaticImport) {
5618                                        if(!this.importCachesInitialized) {
5619                                                this.initializeImportCaches();
5620                                        }
5621                                        for (int j = 0; j < this.importCacheCount; j++) {
5622                                                char[][] importName = this.importsCache[j];
5623                                                if(CharOperation.equals(receiverType.sourceName, importName[0])) {
5624                                                        if (!CharOperation.equals(typeName, importName[1])) {
5625                                                                continue next;
5626                                                        } else {
5627                                                                isAlreadyImported = true;
5628                                                        }
5629                                                }
5630                                        }
5631                                }
5632 
5633                                methodsFound.add(new Object[]{method, receiverType});
5634 
5635                                ReferenceBinding superTypeWithSameErasure = (ReferenceBinding)receiverType.findSuperTypeWithSameErasure(method.declaringClass);
5636                                if (method.declaringClass != superTypeWithSameErasure) {
5637                                        MethodBinding[] otherMethods = superTypeWithSameErasure.getMethods(method.selector);
5638                                        for (int i = 0; i < otherMethods.length; i++) {
5639                                                if(otherMethods[i].original() == method.original()) {
5640                                                        method = otherMethods[i];
5641                                                }
5642                                        }
5643                                }
5644

5647                                char[][] parameterTypeNames = new char[length][];

5652                                        parameterTypeNames[i] = type.qualifiedSourceName();

5661                                        && this.source.length > this.endPosition
5662                                        && this.source[this.endPosition] == '(') {
5663                                        completion = method.selector;

5680

5692                                                        if(original != method) {
5693                                                                proposal.setOriginalSignature(getSignature(original));
5694                                                        }

5696                                                        proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(method.declaringClass.qualifiedSourceName());

5698                                                        proposal.setParameterTypeNames(parameterTypeNames);

5700                                                        proposal.setTypeName(method.returnType.qualifiedSourceName());
5701                                                        proposal.setName(method.selector);
5702                                                        proposal.setCompletion(completion);
5703                                                        proposal.setFlags(method.modifiers);
5704                                                        proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
5705                                                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
5706                                                        if(parameterNames != null) proposal.setParameterNames(parameterNames);

5816        private CompletionProposal createRequiredTypeProposal(Binding binding, int start, int end, int relevance) {
5817                CompletionProposal proposal = null;
5818                if (binding instanceof ReferenceBinding) {
5819                        ReferenceBinding typeBinding = (ReferenceBinding) binding;
5820 
5821                        char[] packageName = typeBinding.qualifiedPackageName();
5822                        char[] typeName = typeBinding.qualifiedSourceName();
5823                        char[] fullyQualifiedName = CharOperation.concat(packageName, typeName, '.');
5824 
5825                        proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
5826                        proposal.nameLookup = this.nameEnvironment.nameLookup;
5827                        proposal.completionEngine = this;
5828                        proposal.setDeclarationSignature(packageName);
5829                        proposal.setSignature(getSignature(typeBinding));
5830                        proposal.setPackageName(packageName);
5831                        proposal.setTypeName(typeName);
5832                        proposal.setCompletion(fullyQualifiedName);
5833                        proposal.setFlags(typeBinding.modifiers);
5834                        proposal.setReplaceRange(start - this.offset, end - this.offset);
5835                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
5836                } else if (binding instanceof PackageBinding) {
5837                        PackageBinding packageBinding = (PackageBinding) binding;
5838 
5839                        char[] packageName = CharOperation.concatWith(packageBinding.compoundName, '.');
5840 
5841                        proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.PACKAGE_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
5842                        proposal.setDeclarationSignature(packageName);
5843                        proposal.setPackageName(packageName);
5844                        proposal.setCompletion(packageName);
5845                        proposal.setReplaceRange(start - this.offset, end - this.offset);
5846                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
5847                }
5848                return proposal;
5849        }

5851        // Helper method for findMethods(char[], TypeBinding[], ReferenceBinding, Scope, ObjectVector, boolean, boolean, boolean)
5852        private void findLocalMethodsOfStaticImports(
5853                char[] methodName,
5854                MethodBinding[] methods,
5855                Scope scope,
5856                ObjectVector methodsFound,
5857                ReferenceBinding receiverType,
5858                InvocationSite invocationSite) {
5859 
5860                ObjectVector newMethodsFound =  new ObjectVector();
5861 
5862                next : for (int f = methods.length; --f >= 0;) {
5863                        MethodBinding method = methods[f];
5864 
5865                        if (method.isSynthetic()) continue next;
5866 
5867                        if (method.isDefaultAbstract())        continue next;
5868 
5869                        if (method.isConstructor()) continue next;
5870 
5871                        if (!method.isStatic()) continue next;
5872 
5873                        if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
5874                                        method.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
5875                                        !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(method.declaringClass))
5876                                continue next;
5877 
5878                        if (this.options.checkVisibility
5879                                && !method.canBeSeenBy(receiverType, invocationSite, scope)) continue next;
5880 
5881                        if (!CharOperation.equals(methodName, method.selector, false /* ignore case */)
5882                                        && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(methodName, method.selector)))
5883                                continue next;
5884 
5885                        for (int i = methodsFound.size; --i >= 0;) {
5886                                Object[] other = (Object[]) methodsFound.elementAt(i);
5887                                MethodBinding otherMethod = (MethodBinding) other[0];
5888                                ReferenceBinding otherReceiverType = (ReferenceBinding) other[1];
5889                                if (method == otherMethod && receiverType == otherReceiverType)
5890                                        continue next;
5891 
5892                                if (CharOperation.equals(method.selector, otherMethod.selector, true)) {
5893                                        if (lookupEnvironment.methodVerifier().doesMethodOverride(otherMethod, method)) {
5894                                                continue next;
5895                                        }
5896                                }
5897                        }
5898 
5899                        newMethodsFound.add(new Object[]{method, receiverType});
5900 
5901                        int length = method.parameters.length;
5902                        char[][] parameterPackageNames = new char[length][];
5903                        char[][] parameterTypeNames = new char[length][];
5904 
5905                        for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
5906                                TypeBinding type = method.original().parameters[i];
5907                                parameterPackageNames[i] = type.qualifiedPackageName();
5908                                parameterTypeNames[i] = type.qualifiedSourceName();
5909                        }
5910                        char[][] parameterNames = findMethodParameterNames(method,parameterTypeNames);
5911 
5912                        char[] completion = CharOperation.NO_CHAR;
5913 
5914                        int previousStartPosition = this.startPosition;
5915 
5916                        // nothing to insert - do not want to replace the existing selector & arguments
5917                        if (this.source != null
5918                                && this.source.length > this.endPosition
5919                                && this.source[this.endPosition] == '(') {
5920                                completion = method.selector;
5921                        } else {
5922                                completion = CharOperation.concat(method.selector, new char[] { '(', ')' });
5923                        }
5924 
5925                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
5926                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
5927                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
5928                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(methodName, method.selector);
5929                        relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(method.returnType);
5930                        relevance += computeRelevanceForStatic(true, method.isStatic());
5931                        relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(false);
5932                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE);
5933 
5934                        this.noProposal = false;
5935                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF)) {
5936                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
5937                                proposal.setDeclarationSignature(getSignature(method.declaringClass));
5938                                proposal.setSignature(getSignature(method));
5939                                MethodBinding original = method.original();
5940                                if(original != method) {
5941                                        proposal.setOriginalSignature(getSignature(original));
5942                                }
5943                                proposal.setDeclarationPackageName(method.declaringClass.qualifiedPackageName());
5944                                proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(method.declaringClass.qualifiedSourceName());
5945                                proposal.setParameterPackageNames(parameterPackageNames);
5946                                proposal.setParameterTypeNames(parameterTypeNames);
5947                                proposal.setPackageName(method.returnType.qualifiedPackageName());
5948                                proposal.setTypeName(method.returnType.qualifiedSourceName());
5949                                proposal.setName(method.selector);
5950                                proposal.setCompletion(completion);
5951                                proposal.setFlags(method.modifiers);
5952                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
5953                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
5954                                if(parameterNames != null) proposal.setParameterNames(parameterNames);
5955                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
5956                                if(DEBUG) {
5957                                        this.printDebug(proposal);
5958                                }
5959                        }
5960                        this.startPosition = previousStartPosition;
5961                }
5962 
5963                methodsFound.addAll(newMethodsFound);
5964        }
5965        int computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(char[] token, char[] proposalName){
5966                if (this.options.camelCaseMatch) {
5967                        if(CharOperation.equals(token, proposalName, true /* do not ignore case */)) {
5968                                return R_CASE + R_EXACT_NAME;
5969                        } else if (CharOperation.prefixEquals(token, proposalName, true /* do not ignore case */)) {
5970                                return R_CASE;
5971                        } else if (CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(token, proposalName)){
5972                                return R_CAMEL_CASE;
5973                        } else if(CharOperation.equals(token, proposalName, false /* ignore case */)) {
5974                                return R_EXACT_NAME;
5975                        }
5976                } else if (CharOperation.prefixEquals(token, proposalName, true /* do not ignore case */)) {
5977                        if(CharOperation.equals(token, proposalName, true /* do not ignore case */)) {
5978                                return R_CASE + R_EXACT_NAME;
5979                        } else {
5980                                return R_CASE;
5981                        }
5982                } else if(CharOperation.equals(token, proposalName, false /* ignore case */)) {
5983                        return R_EXACT_NAME;
5984                }
5985                return 0;
5986        }
5987        private int computeRelevanceForAnnotation(){
5988                if(this.assistNodeIsAnnotation) {
5989                        return R_ANNOTATION;
5990                }
5991                return 0;
5992        }
5993        private int computeRelevanceForAnnotationTarget(TypeBinding typeBinding){
5994                if (this.assistNodeIsAnnotation &&
5995                                (this.targetedElement & TagBits.AnnotationTargetMASK) != 0) {
5996                        long target = typeBinding.getAnnotationTagBits() & TagBits.AnnotationTargetMASK;
5997                        if(target == 0 || (target & this.targetedElement) != 0) {
5998                                return R_TARGET;
5999                        }
6000                }
6001                return 0;
6002        }

6055        private int computeRelevanceForException(char[] proposalName){
6056

6058                        (CharOperation.match(EXCEPTION_PATTERN, proposalName, false) ||

6063        }
6064        private int computeRelevanceForExpectingType(TypeBinding proposalType){
6065                if(this.expectedTypes != null && proposalType != null) {
6066                        for (int i = 0; i <= this.expectedTypesPtr; i++) {
6067                int relevance = R_EXPECTED_TYPE;
6068                                if(CharOperation.equals(this.expectedTypes[i].qualifiedPackageName(), proposalType.qualifiedPackageName()) &&
6069                                        CharOperation.equals(this.expectedTypes[i].qualifiedSourceName(), proposalType.qualifiedSourceName())) {
6070                    relevance = R_EXACT_EXPECTED_TYPE;
6071                                }
6072                                if((this.expectedTypesFilter & SUBTYPE) != 0
6073                                        && proposalType.isCompatibleWith(this.expectedTypes[i])) {
6074                                                return relevance;
6075                                }
6076                                if((this.expectedTypesFilter & SUPERTYPE) != 0
6077                                        && this.expectedTypes[i].isCompatibleWith(proposalType)) {
6078                                        return relevance;
6079                                }
6080                        }
6081                }
6082                return 0;
6083        }
6084        private int computeRelevanceForExpectingType(char[] packageName, char[] typeName){
6085                if(this.expectedTypes != null) {
6086                        for (int i = 0; i <= this.expectedTypesPtr; i++) {
6087                                if(CharOperation.equals(this.expectedTypes[i].qualifiedPackageName(), packageName) &&
6088                                        CharOperation.equals(this.expectedTypes[i].qualifiedSourceName(), typeName)) {
6089                                        return R_EXACT_EXPECTED_TYPE;
6090                                }
6091                        }
6092                        if(this.hasJavaLangObjectAsExpectedType) {
6093                                return R_EXPECTED_TYPE;
6094                        }
6095                }
6096                return 0;
6097        }

6099        private int computeRelevanceForInheritance(ReferenceBinding receiverType, ReferenceBinding declaringClass) {
6100                if (receiverType == declaringClass) return R_NON_INHERITED;
6101                return 0;
6102        }

6104        int computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal(){
6105                return computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal(null);

6107        private int computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal(Binding binding){
6108                if(this.uninterestingBindings != null) {
6109                        for (int i = 0; i <= this.uninterestingBindingsPtr; i++) {
6110                                if(this.uninterestingBindings[i] == binding) {
6111                                        return 0;
6112                                }
6113                        }
6114                }
6115                return R_INTERESTING;
6116        }

6118                if(parent instanceof LocalDeclaration) {
6119                        addUninterestingBindings(((LocalDeclaration)parent).binding);
6120                } else if (parent instanceof FieldDeclaration) {

6125        private void findLabels(char[] label, char[][] choices) {
6126                if(choices == null || choices.length == 0) return;
6127 
6128                int length = label.length;
6129                for (int i = 0; i < choices.length; i++) {
6130                        if (length <= choices[i].length
6131                                && CharOperation.prefixEquals(label, choices[i], false /* ignore case */
6132                        )){
6133                                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
6134                                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
6135                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
6136                                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(label, choices[i]);
6137                                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for keywors
6138 
6139                                this.noProposal = false;
6140                                if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.LABEL_REF)) {
6141                                        CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.LABEL_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
6142                                        proposal.setName(choices[i]);
6143                                        proposal.setCompletion(choices[i]);
6144                                        proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
6145                                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
6146                                        this.requestor.accept(proposal);
6147                                        if(DEBUG) {
6148                                                this.printDebug(proposal);
6149                                        }
6150                                }
6151                        }
6152                }
6153        }

6155        // Helper method for findMethods(char[], FunctionBinding[], Scope, ObjectVector, boolean, boolean, boolean, TypeBinding)
6156        private void findLocalMethodDeclarations(
6157                char[] methodName,
6158                MethodBinding[] methods,
6159                Scope scope,
6160                ObjectVector methodsFound,
6161                //        boolean noVoidReturnType, how do you know?
6162                boolean exactMatch,
6163                ReferenceBinding receiverType) {
6164 
6165                ObjectVector newMethodsFound =  new ObjectVector();
6166                // Inherited methods which are hidden by subclasses are filtered out
6167                // No visibility checks can be performed without the scope & invocationSite
6168                int methodLength = methodName.length;
6169                next : for (int f = methods.length; --f >= 0;) {
6170 
6171                        MethodBinding method = methods[f];
6172                        if (method.isSynthetic())        continue next;
6173 
6174                        if (method.isDefaultAbstract()) continue next;
6175 
6176                        if (method.isConstructor()) continue next;
6177 
6178                        if (method.isFinal()) {
6179                newMethodsFound.add(method);
6180                continue next;
6181            }
6182 
6183                        if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
6184                                        method.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
6185                                        !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(method.declaringClass))
6186                                continue next;
6187 
6188                        //                if (noVoidReturnType && method.returnType == BaseTypes.VoidBinding) continue next;
6189                        if(method.isStatic()) continue next;
6190 
6191                        if (!method.canBeSeenBy(receiverType, FakeInvocationSite , scope)) continue next;
6192 
6193                        if (exactMatch) {
6194                                if (!CharOperation.equals(methodName, method.selector, false /* ignore case */
6195                                        ))
6196                                        continue next;
6197 
6198                        } else {
6199 
6200                                if (methodLength > method.selector.length)
6201                                        continue next;
6202 
6203                                if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(methodName, method.selector, false/* ignore case */)
6204                                                && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(methodName, method.selector)))
6205                                        continue next;
6206                        }
6207 
6208                        for (int i = methodsFound.size; --i >= 0;) {
6209                                MethodBinding otherMethod = (MethodBinding) methodsFound.elementAt(i);
6210                                if (method == otherMethod)
6211                                        continue next;
6212 
6213                                if (CharOperation.equals(method.selector, otherMethod.selector, true)
6214                                                && lookupEnvironment.methodVerifier().doesMethodOverride(otherMethod, method)) {
6215                                        continue next;
6216                                }
6217                        }
6218 
6219                        newMethodsFound.add(method);
6220 
6221                        int length = method.parameters.length;
6222                        char[][] parameterPackageNames = new char[length][];
6223                        char[][] parameterFullTypeNames = new char[length][];
6224 
6225                        for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
6226                                TypeBinding type = method.parameters[i];
6227                                parameterPackageNames[i] = type.qualifiedPackageName();
6228                                parameterFullTypeNames[i] = type.qualifiedSourceName();
6229                        }
6230 
6231                        char[][] parameterNames = findMethodParameterNames(method, parameterFullTypeNames);
6232 
6233                        if(method.typeVariables != null && method.typeVariables.length > 0) {
6234                                char[][] excludedNames = findEnclosingTypeNames(scope);
6235                                char[][] substituedParameterNames = substituteMethodTypeParameterNames(method.typeVariables, excludedNames);
6236                                if(substituedParameterNames != null) {
6237                                        method = new ParameterizedMethodBinding(
6238                                                                method.declaringClass,
6239                                                                method,
6240                                                                substituedParameterNames,
6241                                                                scope.environment());
6242                                }
6243                        }
6244 
6245                        StringBuffer completion = new StringBuffer(10);
6246                        if (!exactMatch) {
6247                                createMethod(method, parameterPackageNames, parameterFullTypeNames, parameterNames, completion);
6248                        }
6249 
6250                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
6251                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
6252                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
6253                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(methodName, method.selector);
6254                        relevance += R_METHOD_OVERIDE;
6255                        if(method.isAbstract()) relevance += R_ABSTRACT_METHOD;
6256                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE);
6257 
6258                        this.noProposal = false;
6259                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.METHOD_DECLARATION)) {
6260                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.METHOD_DECLARATION, this.actualCompletionPosition);
6261                                proposal.setDeclarationSignature(getSignature(method.declaringClass));
6262                                proposal.setDeclarationKey(method.declaringClass.computeUniqueKey());
6263                                proposal.setSignature(getSignature(method));
6264                                MethodBinding original = method.original();
6265                                if(original != method) {
6266                                        proposal.setOriginalSignature(getSignature(original));
6267                                }
6268                                proposal.setKey(method.computeUniqueKey());
6269                                proposal.setDeclarationPackageName(method.declaringClass.qualifiedPackageName());
6270                                proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(method.declaringClass.qualifiedSourceName());
6271                                proposal.setParameterPackageNames(parameterPackageNames);
6272                                proposal.setParameterTypeNames(parameterFullTypeNames);
6273                                proposal.setPackageName(method.returnType.qualifiedPackageName());
6274                                proposal.setTypeName(method.returnType.qualifiedSourceName());
6275                                proposal.setCompletion(completion.toString().toCharArray());
6276                                proposal.setName(method.selector);
6277                                proposal.setFlags(method.modifiers);
6278                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
6279                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
6280                                if(parameterNames != null) proposal.setParameterNames(parameterNames);
6281                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
6282                                if(DEBUG) {
6283                                        this.printDebug(proposal);
6284                                }
6285                        }
6286                }
6287                methodsFound.addAll(newMethodsFound);
6288        }

6290        private void createTypeVariable(TypeVariableBinding typeVariable, StringBuffer completion) {
6291                completion.append(typeVariable.sourceName);
6292 
6293                if (typeVariable.superclass != null && typeVariable.firstBound == typeVariable.superclass) {
6294                    completion.append(' ');
6295                    completion.append(EXTENDS);
6296                    completion.append(' ');
6297                    createType(typeVariable.superclass, completion);
6298                }
6299                if (typeVariable.superInterfaces != null && typeVariable.superInterfaces != Binding.NO_SUPERINTERFACES) {
6300                   if (typeVariable.firstBound != typeVariable.superclass) {
6301                           completion.append(' ');
6302                           completion.append(EXTENDS);
6303                           completion.append(' ');
6304                   }
6305                   for (int i = 0, length = typeVariable.superInterfaces.length; i < length; i++) {
6306                           if (i > 0 || typeVariable.firstBound == typeVariable.superclass) {
6307                                   completion.append(' ');
6308                                   completion.append(EXTENDS);
6309                                   completion.append(' ');
6310                           }
6311                           createType(typeVariable.superInterfaces[i], completion);
6312                   }
6313                }
6314        }
