6316        private void createType(TypeBinding type, StringBuffer completion) {
6317                if (type.isBaseType()) {
6318                        completion.append(type.sourceName());
6319                } else if (type.isTypeVariable()) {
6320                        completion.append(type.sourceName());
6321                } else if (type.isWildcard()) {
6322                        WildcardBinding wildcardBinding = (WildcardBinding) type;
6323                        completion.append('?');
6324                        switch (wildcardBinding.boundKind) {
6325                                case Wildcard.EXTENDS:
6326                                        completion.append(' ');
6327                                        completion.append(EXTENDS);
6328                                        completion.append(' ');
6329                                        createType(wildcardBinding.bound, completion);
6330                                        if(wildcardBinding.otherBounds != null) {
6331 
6332                                                int length = wildcardBinding.otherBounds.length;
6333                                                for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
6334                                                        completion.append(' ');
6335                                                        completion.append('&');
6336                                                        completion.append(' ');
6337                                                        createType(wildcardBinding.otherBounds[i], completion);
6338                                                }
6339                                        }
6340                                        break;
6341                                case Wildcard.SUPER:
6342                                        completion.append(' ');
6343                                        completion.append(SUPER);
6344                                        completion.append(' ');
6345                                        createType(wildcardBinding.bound, completion);
6346                                        break;
6347                        }
6348                } else if (type.isArrayType()) {
6349                        createType(type.leafComponentType(), completion);
6350                        int dim = type.dimensions();
6351                        for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
6352                                completion.append('[');
6353                                completion.append(']');
6354                        }
6355                } else if (type.isParameterizedType()) {
6356                        ParameterizedTypeBinding parameterizedType = (ParameterizedTypeBinding) type;
6357                        if (type.isMemberType()) {
6358                                createType(parameterizedType.enclosingType(), completion);
6359                                completion.append('.');
6360                                completion.append(parameterizedType.sourceName);
6361                        } else {
6362                                completion.append(CharOperation.concatWith(parameterizedType.genericType().compoundName, '.'));
6363                        }
6364                        if (parameterizedType.arguments != null) {
6365                                completion.append('<');
6366                            for (int i = 0, length = parameterizedType.arguments.length; i < length; i++) {
6367                                if (i != 0) completion.append(',');
6368                                createType(parameterizedType.arguments[i], completion);
6369                            }
6370                            completion.append('>');
6371                        }
6372                } else {
6373                        char[] packageName = type.qualifiedPackageName();
6374                        char[] typeName = type.qualifiedSourceName();
6375                        if(mustQualifyType(
6376                                        packageName,
6377                                        type.sourceName(),
6378                                        type.isMemberType() ? type.enclosingType().qualifiedSourceName() : null,
6379                                        ((ReferenceBinding)type).modifiers)) {
6380                                completion.append(CharOperation.concat(packageName, typeName,'.'));
6381                        } else {
6382                                completion.append(type.sourceName());
6383                        }
6384                }
6385        }
6386 
6387        private void createVargsType(TypeBinding type, StringBuffer completion) {
6388                if (type.isArrayType()) {
6389                        createType(type.leafComponentType(), completion);
6390                        int dim = type.dimensions() - 1;
6391                        for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
6392                                completion.append('[');
6393                                completion.append(']');
6394                        }
6395                        completion.append(VARARGS);
6396                } else {
6397                        createType(type, completion);
6398                }
6399        }
6400        private char[] createImportCharArray(char[] importedElement, boolean isStatic, boolean onDemand) {
6401                char[] result = IMPORT;
6402                if (isStatic) {
6403                        result = CharOperation.concat(result, STATIC, ' ');
6404                }
6405                result = CharOperation.concat(result, importedElement, ' ');
6406                if (onDemand) {
6407                        result = CharOperation.concat(result, ON_DEMAND);
6408                }
6409                return CharOperation.concat(result, IMPORT_END);
6410        }
6411        private void createMethod(MethodBinding method, char[][] parameterPackageNames, char[][] parameterTypeNames, char[][] parameterNames, StringBuffer completion) {
6412                //// Modifiers
6413                // flush uninteresting modifiers
6414                int insertedModifiers = method.modifiers & ~(ClassFileConstants.AccNative | ClassFileConstants.AccAbstract);
6415                if(insertedModifiers != ClassFileConstants.AccDefault){
6416                        ASTNode.printModifiers(insertedModifiers, completion);
6417                }
6418 
6419                //// Type parameters
6420 
6421                TypeVariableBinding[] typeVariableBindings = method.typeVariables;
6422                if(typeVariableBindings != null && typeVariableBindings.length != 0) {
6423                        completion.append('<');
6424                        for (int i = 0; i < typeVariableBindings.length; i++) {
6425                                if(i != 0) {
6426                                        completion.append(',');
6427                                        completion.append(' ');
6428                                }
6429                                createTypeVariable(typeVariableBindings[i], completion);
6430                        }
6431                        completion.append('>');
6432                        completion.append(' ');
6433                }
6434 
6435                //// Return type
6436                createType(method.returnType, completion);
6437                completion.append(' ');
6438 
6439                //// Selector
6440                completion.append(method.selector);
6441 
6442                completion.append('(');
6443 
6444                ////Parameters
6445                TypeBinding[] parameterTypes = method.parameters;
6446                int length = parameterTypes.length;
6447                for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
6448                        if(i != 0) {
6449                                completion.append(',');
6450                                completion.append(' ');
6451                        }
6452                        createType(parameterTypes[i], completion);
6453                        completion.append(' ');
6454                        if(parameterNames != null){
6455                                completion.append(parameterNames[i]);
6456                        } else {
6457                                completion.append('%');
6458                        }
6459                }
6460 
6461                completion.append(')');
6462 
6463                //// Exceptions
6464                ReferenceBinding[] exceptions = method.thrownExceptions;
6465 
6466                if (exceptions != null && exceptions.length > 0){
6467                        completion.append(' ');
6468                        completion.append(THROWS);
6469                        completion.append(' ');
6470                        for(int i = 0; i < exceptions.length ; i++){
6471                                if(i != 0) {
6472                                        completion.append(' ');
6473                                        completion.append(',');
6474                                }
6475                                createType(exceptions[i], completion);
6476                        }
6477                }
6478        }

6482                        (missingTypes && !this.requestor.isAllowingRequiredProposals(kind, CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF));
6483        }

6494        private void findMethods(
6495                char[] selector,
6496                TypeBinding[] typeArgTypes,
6497                TypeBinding[] argTypes,
6498                ReferenceBinding receiverType,
6499                Scope scope,
6500                ObjectVector methodsFound,
6501                boolean onlyStaticMethods,
6502                boolean exactMatch,
6503                boolean isCompletingDeclaration,
6504                InvocationSite invocationSite,
6505                Scope invocationScope,
6506                boolean implicitCall,
6507                boolean superCall,
6508                boolean canBePrefixed,
6509                Binding[] missingElements,
6510                int[] missingElementsStarts,
6511                int[] missingElementsEnds,
6512                boolean missingElementsHaveProblems) {
6513 
6514                boolean notInJavadoc = this.assistNodeInJavadoc == 0;
6515                if (selector == null && notInJavadoc) {
6516                        return;
6517                }
6518 
6519                if(isCompletingDeclaration) {
6520                        MethodBinding[] methods = receiverType.availableMethods();
6521                        if (methods != null){
6522                                for (int i = 0; i < methods.length; i++) {
6523                                        if(!methods[i].isDefaultAbstract()) {

6710        private char[][] findMethodParameterNames(MethodBinding method, char[][] parameterTypeNames){
6711                TypeBinding erasure =  method.declaringClass.erasure();
6712                if(!(erasure instanceof ReferenceBinding)) return null;
6713 
6714                char[][] parameterNames = null;
6715 
6716                int length = parameterTypeNames.length;
6717 
6718                if (length == 0){
6719                        return CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR;
6720                }
6721                // look into the corresponding unit if it is available
6722                if (erasure instanceof SourceTypeBinding){
6723                        SourceTypeBinding sourceType = (SourceTypeBinding) erasure;
6724 
6725                        if (sourceType  instanceof CompilationUnitBinding){
6726                                CompilationUnitDeclaration parsedType;
6727 
6728                                if ((parsedType = ((CompilationUnitScope)sourceType.scope).referenceContext) != null){
6729                                        AbstractMethodDeclaration methodDecl = parsedType.declarationOf(method.original());
6730 
6731                                        if (methodDecl != null){
6732                                                Argument[] arguments = methodDecl.arguments;
6733                                                parameterNames = new char[length][];
6734 
6735                                                for(int i = 0 ; i < length ; i++){
6736                                                        parameterNames[i] = arguments[i].name;
6737                                                }
6738                                        }
6739                                }
6740                        }
6741                        else if (sourceType  instanceof MetatdataTypeBinding){
6742                                MetatdataTypeBinding metatdataTypeBinding=(MetatdataTypeBinding)sourceType;
6743                                ClassData classData = metatdataTypeBinding.getClassData();
6744                                Method meth = classData.getMethod(new String (method.selector));
6745                                        if (meth != null){
6746                                                int argLength=meth.parameters!=null ? meth.parameters.length : 0;
6747                                                parameterNames = new char[argLength][];
6748 
6749                                                for(int i = 0 ; i < argLength ; i++){
6750                                                        parameterNames[i] = meth.parameters[i].name.toCharArray();
6751                                                }
6752                                        }
6753                        }
6754                        else
6755                        if (sourceType.scope != null){
6756                                TypeDeclaration parsedType;
6757                                AbstractMethodDeclaration methodDecl = null;
6758                                if ((parsedType = ((ClassScope)sourceType.scope).referenceContext) != null)
6759                                         methodDecl = parsedType.declarationOf(method.original());
6760                                else if ( ((ClassScope)sourceType.scope).inferredType  != null)
6761                                                 methodDecl = (AbstractMethodDeclaration) ((ClassScope)sourceType.scope).inferredType.declarationOf(method.original());
6762 
6763                                        if (methodDecl != null){
6764                                                Argument[] arguments = methodDecl.arguments;
6765                                                parameterNames = new char[length][];
6766 
6767                                                for(int i = 0 ; i < length ; i++){
6768                                                        parameterNames[i] = arguments[i].name;
6769                                                }
6770                                        }
6771                        }
6772                }
6773                // look into the model
6774                if(parameterNames == null){
6775 
6776                        ReferenceBinding bindingType = (ReferenceBinding)erasure;
6777 
6778                        char[] compoundName = CharOperation.concatWith(bindingType.compoundName, '.');
6779                        Object type = this.typeCache.get(compoundName);
6780 
6781                        ISourceType sourceType = null;
6782                        if(type != null) {
6783                                if(type instanceof ISourceType) {
6784                                        sourceType = (ISourceType) type;
6785                                }
6786                        } else {
6787                                NameEnvironmentAnswer answer = this.nameEnvironment.findType(bindingType.compoundName,this);
6788                                if(answer != null && answer.isSourceType()) {
6789                                        sourceType = answer.getSourceTypes()[0];
6790                                        this.typeCache.put(compoundName, sourceType);
6791                                }
6792                        }
6793 
6794                        if(sourceType != null) {
6795                                IType typeHandle = ((SourceTypeElementInfo) sourceType).getHandle();
6796 
6797                                String[] parameterTypeSignatures = new String[length];
6798                                for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
6799                                        parameterTypeSignatures[i] = Signature.createTypeSignature(parameterTypeNames[i], false);
6800                                }
6801                                IFunction searchedMethod = typeHandle.getFunction(String.valueOf(method.selector), parameterTypeSignatures);
6802                                IFunction[] foundMethods = typeHandle.findMethods(searchedMethod);
6803 
6804                                if(foundMethods != null) {
6805                                        int len = foundMethods.length;
6806                                        if(len == 1) {
6807                                                try {
6808                                                        SourceMethod sourceMethod = (SourceMethod) foundMethods[0];
6809                                                        parameterNames = ((SourceMethodElementInfo) sourceMethod.getElementInfo()).getArgumentNames();
6810                                                } catch (JavaScriptModelException e) {
6811                                                        // method doesn't exist: ignore
6812                                                }
6813                                        }
6814                                }
6815                        }
6816                }
6817                return parameterNames;
6818        }

6820        private void findNestedTypes(
6821                char[] typeName,
6822                SourceTypeBinding currentType,
6823                Scope scope,
6824                boolean proposeAllMemberTypes,
6825                ObjectVector typesFound) {
6826                if (typeName == null)
6827                        return;
6828 
6829                int typeLength = typeName.length;
6830 
6831                SourceTypeBinding nextTypeToIgnore = null;
6832                while (scope != null) { // done when a COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE is found
6833 
6834                        switch (scope.kind) {
6835 
6836                                case Scope.METHOD_SCOPE :
6837                                case Scope.BLOCK_SCOPE :
6838                                        BlockScope blockScope = (BlockScope) scope;
6839 
6840                                        next : for (int i = 0, length = blockScope.subscopeCount; i < length; i++) {
6841 
6842                                                if (blockScope.subscopes[i] instanceof ClassScope) {
6843                                                        SourceTypeBinding localType =
6844                                                                ((ClassScope) blockScope.subscopes[i]).getReferenceBinding();
6845 
6846                                                        if (!localType.isAnonymousType()) {
6847                                                                if (this.isForbidden(localType))
6848                                                                        continue next;
6849 
6850                                                                if (typeLength > localType.sourceName.length)
6851                                                                        continue next;
6852                                                                if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(typeName, localType.sourceName, false/* ignore case */)
6853                                                                                && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(typeName, localType.sourceName)))
6854                                                                        continue next;
6855 
6856                                                                for (int j = typesFound.size; --j >= 0;) {
6857                                                                        ReferenceBinding otherType = (ReferenceBinding) typesFound.elementAt(j);
6858 
6859                                                                        if (localType == otherType)
6860                                                                                continue next;
6861                                                                }
6862 
6863                                                                if(this.assistNodeIsClass) {
6864                                                                        if(!localType.isClass()) continue next;
6865                                                                } else if(this.assistNodeIsInterface) {
6866                                                                        if(!localType.isInterface() && !localType.isAnnotationType()) continue next;
6867                                                                } else if (this.assistNodeIsAnnotation) {
6868                                                                        if(!localType.isAnnotationType()) continue next;
6869                                                                }
6870 
6871                                                                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
6872                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
6873                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
6874                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(typeName, localType.sourceName);
6875                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(localType);
6876                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForException(localType.sourceName);
6877                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForClass();
6878                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(false);
6879                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for nested type
6880                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForAnnotationTarget(localType);
6881 
6882                                                                this.noProposal = false;
6883                                                                if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
6884                                                                        createTypeProposal(localType, localType.sourceName, IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE, localType.sourceName, relevance);
6885                                                                }
6886                                                        }
6887                                                }
6888                                        }
6889                                        break;
6890 
6891                                case Scope.CLASS_SCOPE :
6892                                        SourceTypeBinding enclosingSourceType = scope.enclosingSourceType();
6893                                        findMemberTypes(typeName, enclosingSourceType, scope, currentType, false, false, false, false, proposeAllMemberTypes, nextTypeToIgnore, typesFound);
6894                                        nextTypeToIgnore = enclosingSourceType;
6895                                        if (typeLength == 0)
6896                                                return; // do not search outside the class scope if no prefix was provided
6897                                        break;
6898 
6899                                case Scope.COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE :
6900                                        return;
6901                        }
6902                        scope = scope.parent;
6903                }
6904        }

6916        private void findParameterizedType(TypeReference ref, Scope scope) {
6917                ReferenceBinding refBinding = (ReferenceBinding) ref.resolvedType;
6918                if(refBinding != null) {
6919                        if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
6920                                        refBinding.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
6921                                        !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(refBinding))
6922                                return;
6923 
6924                        int accessibility = IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE;
6925                        if(refBinding.hasRestrictedAccess()) {
6926                                AccessRestriction accessRestriction = lookupEnvironment.getAccessRestriction(refBinding);
6927                                if(accessRestriction != null) {
6928                                        switch (accessRestriction.getProblemId()) {
6929                                                case IProblem.ForbiddenReference:
6930                                                        if (this.options.checkForbiddenReference) {
6931                                                                return;
6932                                                        }
6933                                                        accessibility = IAccessRule.K_NON_ACCESSIBLE;
6934                                                        break;
6935                                                case IProblem.DiscouragedReference:
6936                                                        if (this.options.checkDiscouragedReference) {
6937                                                                return;
6938                                                        }
6939                                                        accessibility = IAccessRule.K_DISCOURAGED;
6940                                                        break;
6941                                        }
6942                                }
6943                        }
6944 
6945                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
6946                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
6947                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
6948                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(refBinding.sourceName, refBinding.sourceName);
6949                        relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(refBinding);
6950                        relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(false);
6951                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(accessibility); // no access restriction for type in the current unit
6952 
6953                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
6954                                createTypeProposal(refBinding, refBinding.qualifiedSourceName(), IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE, CharOperation.NO_CHAR, relevance);
6955                        }
6956                }
6957        }
6958        private void findTypeParameters(char[] token, Scope scope) {
6959                if (this.compilerOptions.sourceLevel < ClassFileConstants.JDK1_5) return;
6960 
6961                TypeParameter[] typeParameters = null;
6962                while (scope != null) { // done when a COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE is found
6963                        typeParameters = null;
6964                        switch (scope.kind) {
6965                                case Scope.METHOD_SCOPE :
6966                                        MethodScope methodScope = (MethodScope) scope;
6967                                        if(methodScope.referenceContext instanceof MethodDeclaration) {
6968                                                MethodDeclaration methodDeclaration = (MethodDeclaration) methodScope.referenceContext;
6969                                                typeParameters = methodDeclaration.typeParameters;
6970                                        } else if(methodScope.referenceContext instanceof ConstructorDeclaration) {
6971                                                ConstructorDeclaration methodDeclaration = (ConstructorDeclaration) methodScope.referenceContext;
6972                                                typeParameters = methodDeclaration.typeParameters;
6973                                        }
6974                                        break;
6975                                case Scope.CLASS_SCOPE :
6976                                        ClassScope classScope = (ClassScope) scope;
6977                                        typeParameters = classScope.referenceContext.typeParameters;
6978                                        break;
6979                                case Scope.COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE :
6980                                        return;
6981                        }
6982                        if(typeParameters != null) {
6983                                for (int i = 0; i < typeParameters.length; i++) {
6984                                        int typeLength = token.length;
6985                                        TypeParameter typeParameter = typeParameters[i];
6986 
6987                                        if(typeParameter.binding == null) continue;
6988 
6989                                        if (typeLength > typeParameter.name.length) continue;
6990 
6991                                        if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(token, typeParameter.name, false)
6992                                                        && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(token, typeParameter.name))) continue;
6993 
6994                                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
6995                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
6996                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
6997                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(token, typeParameter.name);
6998                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(typeParameter.type == null ? null :typeParameter.type.resolvedType);
6999                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(false);
7000                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForException(typeParameter.name);
7001                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction fot type parameter
7002 
7003                                        this.noProposal = false;
7004                                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
7005                                                createTypeParameterProposal(typeParameter, relevance);
7006                                        }
7007                                }
7008                        }
7009                        scope = scope.parent;
7010                }
7011        }
7012        private void findTypesAndPackages(char[] token, Scope scope, ObjectVector typesFound) {
7013 
7014                if (token == null)
7015                        return;
7016 
7017                // do not propose type if completion token is empty
7018                boolean skip = false;
7019                if (token.length == 0 && NO_TYPE_COMPLETION_ON_EMPTY_TOKEN) {
7020                        if(!assistNodeIsConstructor && (this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.EXCEPTION) == 0) {
7021                                return;
7022                        }
7023                        skip = true;
7024                }
7025 
7026                boolean proposeType =
7027                        !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF) ||
7028                        ((this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.TEXT) != 0 && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_TYPE_REF));
7029                boolean proposeAllMemberTypes = !this.assistNodeIsConstructor;
7030 
7031                if (!skip && proposeType && scope.enclosingSourceType() != null) {
7032                        findNestedTypes(token, scope.enclosingSourceType(), scope, proposeAllMemberTypes, typesFound);
7033                        if((!assistNodeIsConstructor && !assistNodeIsAnnotation) && this.assistNodeInJavadoc == 0) {
7034                                // don't propose type parameters if the completion is a constructor ('new |')
7035                                findTypeParameters(token, scope);
7036                        }
7037                }
7038                boolean isEmptyPrefix = token.length == 0;
7039 
7040 
7041                if (!skip && proposeType && this.unitScope != null) {
7042                        ReferenceBinding outerInvocationType = scope.enclosingSourceType();
7043                        if(outerInvocationType != null) {
7044                                ReferenceBinding temp = outerInvocationType.enclosingType();
7045                                while(temp != null) {
7046                                        outerInvocationType = temp;
7047                                        temp = temp.enclosingType();
7048                                }
7049                        }
7050 
7051                        int typeLength = token.length;
7052                        SourceTypeBinding[] types = this.unitScope.topLevelTypes;
7053 
7054                        next : for (int i = 0, length = types.length; i < length; i++) {
7055                                SourceTypeBinding sourceType = types[i];
7056 
7057                                if(isForbidden(sourceType)) continue next;
7058 
7059                                //@GINO: Anonymous UI Hide types
7060                                if( sourceType.isAnonymousType() )continue next;
7061 
7062                                if(proposeAllMemberTypes &&
7063                                        sourceType != outerInvocationType) {
7064                                        findSubMemberTypes(
7065                                                        token,
7066                                                        sourceType,
7067                                                        scope,
7068                                                        scope.enclosingSourceType(),
7069                                                        false,
7070                                                        false,
7071                                                        false,
7072                                                        typesFound);
7073                                }
7074 
7075                                if (sourceType.sourceName == CompletionParser.FAKE_TYPE_NAME) continue next;
7076                                if (sourceType.sourceName == TypeConstants.PACKAGE_INFO_NAME) continue next;
7077 
7078                                if (typeLength > sourceType.sourceName.length) continue next;
7079 
7080                                int index = CharOperation.lastIndexOf('.', sourceType.sourceName);
7081                                if (index > 0) {
7082//                                        char[] pkg = CharOperation.subarray(sourceType.sourceName, 0, index);
7083                                        char[] simpleName = CharOperation.subarray(sourceType.sourceName, index+1, sourceType.sourceName.length);
7084                                        
7085                                        if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(token, simpleName, false)
7086                                                        && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(token, simpleName))) continue ;
7087                                        
7088                                } else if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(token, sourceType.sourceName, false)
7089                                                && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(token, sourceType.sourceName))) continue ;
7090 
7091                                if (this.assistNodeIsAnnotation && !hasPossibleAnnotationTarget(sourceType, scope)) {
7092                                        continue next;
7093                                }
7094 
7095                                for (int j = typesFound.size; --j >= 0;) {
7096                                        ReferenceBinding otherType = (ReferenceBinding) typesFound.elementAt(j);
7097 
7098                                        if (sourceType == otherType) continue next;
7099                                }
7100 
7101                                this.knownTypes.put(CharOperation.concat(sourceType.qualifiedPackageName(), sourceType.sourceName(), '.'), this);
7102 
7103                                if(this.assistNodeIsClass) {
7104                                        if(!sourceType.isClass()) continue next;
7105                                } else if(this.assistNodeIsInterface) {
7106                                        if(!sourceType.isInterface() && !sourceType.isAnnotationType()) continue next;
7107                                } else if (this.assistNodeIsAnnotation) {
7108                                        if(!sourceType.isAnnotationType()) continue next;
7109                                }
7110 
7111                                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
7112                                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
7113                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
7114                                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(token, sourceType.sourceName);
7115                                relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(sourceType);
7116                                relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(false);
7117                                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for type in the current unit
7118 
7119                                if (sourceType.isAnnotationType()) {
7120                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForAnnotation();
7121                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForAnnotationTarget(sourceType);
7122                                } else if (sourceType.isInterface()) {
7123                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterface();
7124                                } else if(sourceType.isClass()){
7125                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForClass();
7126                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForException(sourceType.sourceName);
7127                                }
7128                                this.noProposal = false;
7129                                if(proposeType) {
7130                                        char[] typeName = sourceType.sourceName();
7131                                        createTypeProposal(sourceType, typeName, IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE, typeName, relevance);
7132                                }
7133                        }
7134                }
7135 
7136                if (isEmptyPrefix && !this.assistNodeIsAnnotation) {
7137                        if(proposeType && this.expectedTypesPtr > -1) {
7138                                next : for (int i = 0; i <= this.expectedTypesPtr; i++) {
7139                                        if(this.expectedTypes[i] instanceof ReferenceBinding) {
7140                                                ReferenceBinding refBinding = (ReferenceBinding)this.expectedTypes[i];
7141 
7142                                                if(refBinding.isTypeVariable() && assistNodeIsConstructor) {
7143                                                        // don't propose type variable if the completion is a constructor ('new |')
7144                                                        continue next;
7145                                                }
7146                                                if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
7147                                                                refBinding.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
7148                                                                !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(refBinding))
7149                                                        continue next;
7150 
7151                                                int accessibility = IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE;
7152                                                if(refBinding.hasRestrictedAccess()) {
7153                                                        AccessRestriction accessRestriction = lookupEnvironment.getAccessRestriction(refBinding);
7154                                                        if(accessRestriction != null) {
7155                                                                switch (accessRestriction.getProblemId()) {
7156                                                                        case IProblem.ForbiddenReference:
7157                                                                                if (this.options.checkForbiddenReference) {
7158                                                                                        continue next;
7159                                                                                }
7160                                                                                accessibility = IAccessRule.K_NON_ACCESSIBLE;
7161                                                                                break;
7162                                                                        case IProblem.DiscouragedReference:
7163                                                                                if (this.options.checkDiscouragedReference) {
7164                                                                                        continue next;
7165                                                                                }
7166                                                                                accessibility = IAccessRule.K_DISCOURAGED;
7167                                                                                break;
7168                                                                }
7169                                                        }
7170                                                }
7171 
7172                                                for (int j = 0; j < typesFound.size(); j++) {
7173                                                        ReferenceBinding typeFound = (ReferenceBinding)typesFound.elementAt(j);
7174                                                        if (typeFound == refBinding) {
7175                                                                continue next;
7176                                                        }
7177                                                }
7178 
7179                                                boolean inSameUnit = this.unitScope.isDefinedInSameUnit(refBinding);
7180 
7181                                                // top level types of the current unit are already proposed.
7182                                                if(skip || !inSameUnit || (inSameUnit && refBinding.isMemberType())) {
7183                                                        char[] packageName = refBinding.qualifiedPackageName();
7184                                                        char[] typeName = refBinding.sourceName();
7185                                                        char[] completionName = typeName;
7186 
7187                                                        boolean isQualified = false;
7188                                                        if (!this.insideQualifiedReference && !refBinding.isMemberType()) {
7189                                                                if (mustQualifyType(packageName, typeName, null, refBinding.modifiers)) {
7190                                                                        if (packageName == null || packageName.length == 0)
7191                                                                                if (this.unitScope != null && this.unitScope.getDefaultPackage().compoundName != CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR)
7192                                                                                        continue next; // ignore types from the default package from outside it
7193                                                                        completionName = CharOperation.concat(packageName, typeName, '.');
7194                                                                        isQualified = true;
7195                                                                }
7196                                                        }
7197 
7198                                                        if(this.assistNodeIsClass) {
7199                                                                if(!refBinding.isClass()) continue next;
7200                                                        } else if(this.assistNodeIsInterface) {
7201                                                                if(!refBinding.isInterface() && !refBinding.isAnnotationType()) continue next;
7202                                                        } else if (this.assistNodeIsAnnotation) {
7203                                                                if(!refBinding.isAnnotationType()) continue next;
7204                                                        }
7205 
7206                                                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
7207                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
7208                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
7209                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(token, typeName);
7210                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(refBinding);
7211                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(isQualified);
7212                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(accessibility);
7213 
7214                                                        if(refBinding.isClass()) {
7215                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForClass();
7216                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForException(typeName);
7217                                                        } else if(refBinding.isEnum()) {
7218                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForEnum();
7219                                                        } else if(refBinding.isInterface()) {
7220                                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterface();
7221                                                        }
7222 
7223                                                        this.noProposal = false;
7224                                                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF)) {
7225                                                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
7226                                                                proposal.setDeclarationSignature(packageName);
7227                                                                proposal.setSignature(getSignature(refBinding));
7228                                                                proposal.setPackageName(packageName);
7229                                                                proposal.setTypeName(typeName);
7230                                                                proposal.setCompletion(completionName);
7231                                                                proposal.setFlags(refBinding.modifiers);
7232                                                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
7233                                                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
7234                                                                proposal.setAccessibility(accessibility);
7235                                                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
7236                                                                if(DEBUG) {
7237                                                                        this.printDebug(proposal);
7238                                                                }
7239                                                        }
7240                                                }
7241                                        }
7242                                }
7243                        }
7244                } else {
7245                        if(!isEmptyPrefix && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.KEYWORD)) {
7246                                if (this.assistNodeInJavadoc == 0 || (this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.BASE_TYPES) != 0) {
7247                                        findKeywords(token, BASE_TYPE_NAMES, false, false);
7248                                }
7249                        }
7250                        if(proposeType) {
7251                                int l = typesFound.size();
7252                                for (int i = 0; i < l; i++) {
7253                                        ReferenceBinding typeFound = (ReferenceBinding) typesFound.elementAt(i);
7254                                        char[] fullyQualifiedTypeName =
7255                                                CharOperation.concat(
7256                                                                typeFound.qualifiedPackageName(),
7257                                                                typeFound.qualifiedSourceName(),
7258                                                                '.');
7259                                        this.knownTypes.put(fullyQualifiedTypeName, this);
7260                                }
7261                                int searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.TYPE;
7262                                if(this.assistNodeIsClass) {
7263                                        searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.CLASS;
7264                                } else if(this.assistNodeIsInterface) {
7265                                        searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.INTERFACE_AND_ANNOTATION;
7266                                } else if(this.assistNodeIsEnum) {
7267                                        searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.ENUM;
7268                                } else if(this.assistNodeIsAnnotation) {
7269                                        searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.ANNOTATION_TYPE;
7270                                }
7271                                this.nameEnvironment.findTypes(
7272                                                token,
7273                                                proposeAllMemberTypes,
7274                                                this.options.camelCaseMatch,
7275                                                searchFor,
7276                                                this);
7277                                acceptTypes(scope);
7278                        }
7279//                        if(!isEmptyPrefix && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.PACKAGE_REF)) {
7280//                                this.nameEnvironment.findPackages(token, this);
7281//                        }
7282                }
7283        }

7285        private void findTypesAndSubpackages(
7286                char[] token,
7287                PackageBinding packageBinding,
7288                Scope scope) {
7289 
7290                boolean proposeType =
7291                        !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF) ||
7292                        ((this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.TEXT) != 0 && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_TYPE_REF));
7293 
7294                char[] qualifiedName =
7295                        CharOperation.concatWith(packageBinding.compoundName, token, '.');
7296 
7297                if (token == null || token.length == 0) {
7298                        int length = qualifiedName.length;
7299                        System.arraycopy(
7300                                qualifiedName,
7301                                0,
7302                                qualifiedName = new char[length + 1],
7303                                0,
7304                                length);
7305                        qualifiedName[length] = '.';
7306                }
7307 
7308                this.qualifiedCompletionToken = qualifiedName;
7309 
7310                if (proposeType && this.unitScope != null) {
7311                        int typeLength = qualifiedName.length;
7312                        SourceTypeBinding[] types = this.unitScope.topLevelTypes;
7313 
7314                        for (int i = 0, length = types.length; i < length; i++) {
7315                                SourceTypeBinding sourceType = types[i];
7316 
7317                                char[] qualifiedSourceTypeName = CharOperation.concatWith(sourceType.compoundName, '.');
7318 
7319                                if (sourceType.sourceName == CompletionParser.FAKE_TYPE_NAME) continue;
7320                                if (sourceType.sourceName == TypeConstants.PACKAGE_INFO_NAME) continue;
7321                                if (typeLength > qualifiedSourceTypeName.length) continue;
7322                                if (!(packageBinding == sourceType.getPackage())) continue;
7323 
7324                                if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(qualifiedName, qualifiedSourceTypeName, false)
7325                                                && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(token, sourceType.sourceName)))        continue;
7326 
7327                                if (this.options.checkDeprecation &&
7328                                                sourceType.isViewedAsDeprecated() &&
7329                                                !scope.isDefinedInSameUnit(sourceType))
7330                                        continue;
7331 
7332                                int accessibility = IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE;
7333                                if(sourceType.hasRestrictedAccess()) {
7334                                        AccessRestriction accessRestriction = lookupEnvironment.getAccessRestriction(sourceType);
7335                                        if(accessRestriction != null) {
7336                                                switch (accessRestriction.getProblemId()) {
7337                                                        case IProblem.ForbiddenReference:
7338                                                                if (this.options.checkForbiddenReference) {
7339                                                                        continue;
7340                                                                }
7341                                                                accessibility = IAccessRule.K_NON_ACCESSIBLE;
7342                                                                break;
7343                                                        case IProblem.DiscouragedReference:
7344                                                                if (this.options.checkDiscouragedReference) {
7345                                                                        continue;
7346                                                                }
7347                                                                accessibility = IAccessRule.K_DISCOURAGED;
7348                                                                break;
7349                                                }
7350                                        }
7351                                }
7352 
7353                                this.knownTypes.put(CharOperation.concat(sourceType.qualifiedPackageName(), sourceType.sourceName(), '.'), this);
7354 
7355                                int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
7356                                relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
7357                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
7358                                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(qualifiedName, qualifiedSourceTypeName);
7359                                relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(sourceType);
7360                                relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(false);
7361                                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(accessibility);
7362 
7363                                if (sourceType.isAnnotationType()) {
7364                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForAnnotation();
7365                                } else if (sourceType.isInterface()) {
7366                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterface();
7367                                } else if (sourceType.isClass()) {
7368                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForClass();
7369                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForException(sourceType.sourceName);
7370                                }
7371                                this.noProposal = false;
7372                                if(proposeType) {
7373                                        char[] typeName = sourceType.sourceName();
7374                                        createTypeProposal(sourceType, typeName, IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE, typeName, relevance);
7375                                }
7376                        }
7377                }
7378 
7379                if(proposeType) {
7380                        int searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.TYPE;
7381                        if(this.assistNodeIsClass) {
7382                                searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.CLASS;
7383                        } else if(this.assistNodeIsInterface) {
7384                                searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.INTERFACE_AND_ANNOTATION;
7385                        } else if(this.assistNodeIsEnum) {
7386                                searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.ENUM;
7387                        } else if(this.assistNodeIsAnnotation) {
7388                                searchFor = IJavaScriptSearchConstants.ANNOTATION_TYPE;
7389                        }
7390                        this.nameEnvironment.findTypes(
7391                                        qualifiedName,
7392                                        false,
7393                                        this.options.camelCaseMatch,
7394                                        searchFor,
7395                                        this);
7396                        acceptTypes(scope);
7397                }
7398//                if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.PACKAGE_REF)) {
7399//                        this.nameEnvironment.findPackages(qualifiedName, this);
7400//                }
7401        }
7402 
7403        private void findVariablesAndMethods(
7404                char[] token,
7405                Scope scope,
7406                InvocationSite invocationSite,
7407                Scope invocationScope,
7408                boolean insideTypeAnnotation,
7409                boolean insideAnnotationAttribute) {
7410 
7411                if (token == null)
7412                        return;
7413 
7414                // Should local variables hide fields from the receiver type or any of its enclosing types?
7415                // we know its an implicit field/method access... see BlockScope getBinding/getImplicitMethod
7416 
7417                boolean staticsOnly = false;
7418                // need to know if we're in a static context (or inside a constructor)
7419                int tokenLength = token.length;
7420 
7421                ObjectVector localsFound = new ObjectVector();
7422                ObjectVector fieldsFound = new ObjectVector();
7423                ObjectVector methodsFound = new ObjectVector();
7424 
7425                Scope currentScope = scope;
7426 
7427                if (!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.LOCAL_VARIABLE_REF)) {
7428                        done1 : while (true) { // done when a COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE is found
7429 
7430                                switch (currentScope.kind) {
7431 
7432                                        case Scope.METHOD_SCOPE :
7433                                                // handle the error case inside an explicit constructor call (see MethodScope>>findField)
7434                                                MethodScope methodScope = (MethodScope) currentScope;
7435                                                staticsOnly |= methodScope.isStatic | methodScope.isConstructorCall;
7436 
7437                                        case Scope.BLOCK_SCOPE :
7438                                        case Scope.COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE :
7439                                                BlockScope blockScope = (BlockScope) currentScope;
7440 
7441                                                next : for (int i = 0, length = blockScope.locals.length; i < length; i++) {
7442                                                        LocalVariableBinding local = blockScope.locals[i];
7443 
7444                                                        if (local == null)
7445                                                                break next;
7446                                                        
7447 
7448                                                        if (tokenLength > local.name.length)
7449                                                                continue next;
7450 
7451                                                        if (!CharOperation.prefixEquals(token, local.name, false /* ignore case */)
7452                                                                        && !(this.options.camelCaseMatch && CharOperation.camelCaseMatch(token, local.name)))
7453                                                                continue next;
7454 
7455                                                        if (local.isSecret())
7456                                                                continue next;
7457 
7458                                                        for (int f = 0; f < localsFound.size; f++) {
7459                                                                LocalVariableBinding otherLocal =
7460                                                                        (LocalVariableBinding) localsFound.elementAt(f);
7461                                                                if (CharOperation.equals(otherLocal.name, local.name, true))
7462                                                                        continue next;
7463                                                        }
7464                                                        localsFound.add(local);
7465 
7466                                                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
7467                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
7468                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal(local);
7469                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(token, local.name);
7470                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForExpectingType(local.type);
7471                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForQualification(false);
7472                                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for local variable
7473                                                        this.noProposal = false;
7474                                                        if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.LOCAL_VARIABLE_REF)) {
7475                                                                CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.LOCAL_VARIABLE_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition);
7476                                                                proposal.setSignature(
7477                                                                        local.type == null
7478                                                                        ? createTypeSignature(
7479                                                                                        CharOperation.NO_CHAR,
7480                                                                                        local.declaration.getTypeName().toCharArray())
7481                                                                        : getSignature(local.type));
7482                                                                if(local.type == null) {
7483                                                                        //proposal.setPackageName(null);
7484                                                                        proposal.setTypeName(local.declaration.getTypeName().toCharArray());
7485                                                                } else {
7486                                                                        proposal.setPackageName(local.type.qualifiedPackageName());
7487                                                                        proposal.setTypeName(local.type.qualifiedSourceName());
7488                                                                }
7489                                                                proposal.setName(local.name);
7490                                                                proposal.setCompletion(local.name);
7491                                                                proposal.setFlags(local.modifiers);
7492                                                                proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
7493                                                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
7494                                                                this.requestor.accept(proposal);
7495                                                                if(DEBUG) {
7496                                                                        this.printDebug(proposal);
7497                                                                }
7498                                                        }
7499                                                }
7500 
7501                                                if (currentScope.kind==Scope.COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE )
7502                                                        break done1;
7503                                                        else
7504                                                                break;
7505                                }
7506                                currentScope = currentScope.parent;
7507                        }
7508                }
7509 
7510                boolean proposeField = !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.FIELD_REF);
7511                boolean proposeMethod = !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.METHOD_REF);
7512

7518

7642        private char[][] findVariableFromUnresolvedReference(LocalDeclaration variable, BlockScope scope, final char[][] discouragedNames) {
7643                final TypeReference type = variable.type;
7644                if(type != null &&
7645                                type.resolvedType != null &&
7646                                type.resolvedType.problemId() == ProblemReasons.NoError){
7647 
7648                        final ArrayList proposedNames = new ArrayList();
7649

7655                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
7656                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(completionToken, name);
7657                                                relevance += R_NAME_FIRST_PREFIX;
7658                                                relevance += R_NAME_FIRST_SUFFIX;
7659                                                relevance += R_NAME_LESS_NEW_CHARACTERS;
7660                                                relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for variable name
7661

7663                                                CompletionEngine.this.noProposal = false;
7664                                                if(!CompletionEngine.this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.VARIABLE_DECLARATION)) {
7665                                                        CompletionProposal proposal = CompletionEngine.this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.VARIABLE_DECLARATION, CompletionEngine.this.actualCompletionPosition);
7666                                                        proposal.setSignature(getSignature(type.resolvedType));

7668                                                        proposal.setTypeName(type.resolvedType.qualifiedSourceName());
7669                                                        proposal.setName(name);

7672                                                        proposal.setReplaceRange(CompletionEngine.this.startPosition - CompletionEngine.this.offset, CompletionEngine.this.endPosition - CompletionEngine.this.offset);

7679                                                proposedNames.add(name);
7680                                        }
7681                                };

7683                        ReferenceContext referenceContext = scope.referenceContext();

7685                                AbstractMethodDeclaration md = (AbstractMethodDeclaration)referenceContext;
7686

7691                                                variable.declarationSourceEnd + 1,
7692                                                discouragedNames,
7693                                                nameRequestor);
7694                        } else if (referenceContext instanceof TypeDeclaration) {
7695                                TypeDeclaration typeDeclaration = (TypeDeclaration) referenceContext;
7696                                FieldDeclaration[] fields = typeDeclaration.fields;
7697                                if (fields != null) {
7698                                        done : for (int i = 0; i < fields.length; i++) {

7702                                                                        variable.sourceStart < initializer.bodyEnd) {

7708                                                                                variable.declarationSourceEnd + 1,
7709                                                                                discouragedNames,

7712                                                        }

7714                                        }

7784        private void findUnresolvedReference(int completedNameStart, int completedNameEnd, BlockScope scope, char[][] discouragedNames) {
7785                char[][] foundNames = findUnresolvedReferenceBefore(completedNameStart - 1, completedNameEnd, scope, discouragedNames);
7786                if (foundNames != null && foundNames.length > 1) {
7787                        int discouragedNamesLength = discouragedNames.length;
7788                        int foundNamesLength = foundNames.length;
7789                        int newLength = discouragedNamesLength + foundNamesLength;
7790                        System.arraycopy(discouragedNames, 0, discouragedNames = new char[newLength][], 0, discouragedNamesLength);
7791                        System.arraycopy(foundNames, 0, discouragedNames, discouragedNamesLength, foundNamesLength);
7792                }
7793                findUnresolvedReferenceAfter(completedNameEnd + 1, scope, discouragedNames);
7794        }

7867                // Helper method for private void findVariableNames(char[] name, TypeReference type )
7868        private void findVariableName(
7869                char[] token,
7870                char[] qualifiedPackageName,
7871                char[] qualifiedSourceName,
7872                char[] sourceName,
7873                final TypeBinding typeBinding,
7874                char[][] discouragedNames,
7875                final char[][] forbiddenNames,
7876                int dim,
7877                int kind,
7878                int modifiers){
7879 
7880                if(sourceName == null || sourceName.length == 0)
7881                        return;
7882 
7883                // compute variable name for non base type
7884                final char[] displayName;
7885                if (dim > 0){
7886                        int l = qualifiedSourceName.length;
7887                        displayName = new char[l+(2*dim)];
7888                        System.arraycopy(qualifiedSourceName, 0, displayName, 0, l);
7889                        for(int i = 0; i < dim; i++){
7890                                displayName[l+(i*2)] = '[';
7891                                displayName[l+(i*2)+1] = ']';
7892                        }
7893                } else {
7894                        displayName = qualifiedSourceName;
7895                }
7896 
7897                final char[] t = token;
7898                final char[] q = qualifiedPackageName;
7899                INamingRequestor namingRequestor = new INamingRequestor() {
7900                        public void acceptNameWithPrefixAndSuffix(char[] name, boolean isFirstPrefix, boolean isFirstSuffix, int reusedCharacters) {
7901                                accept(
7902                                                name,
7903                                                (isFirstPrefix ? R_NAME_FIRST_PREFIX : R_NAME_PREFIX) + (isFirstSuffix ? R_NAME_FIRST_SUFFIX : R_NAME_SUFFIX),
7904                                                reusedCharacters);

7918                        void accept(char[] name, int prefixAndSuffixRelevance, int reusedCharacters){
7919                                int l = forbiddenNames == null ? 0 : forbiddenNames.length;
7920                                for (int i = 0; i < l; i++) {
7921                                        if (CharOperation.equals(forbiddenNames[i], name, false)) return;
7922                                }
7923 
7924                                if (CharOperation.prefixEquals(t, name, false)) {
7925                                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
7926                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
7927                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForCaseMatching(t, name);
7928                                        relevance += prefixAndSuffixRelevance;
7929                                        if(reusedCharacters > 0) relevance += R_NAME_LESS_NEW_CHARACTERS;
7930                                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for variable name
7931 
7932                                        // accept result
7933                                        CompletionEngine.this.noProposal = false;
7934                                        if(!CompletionEngine.this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.VARIABLE_DECLARATION)) {
7935                                                CompletionProposal proposal = CompletionEngine.this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.VARIABLE_DECLARATION, CompletionEngine.this.actualCompletionPosition);
7936                                                proposal.setSignature(getSignature(typeBinding));
7937                                                proposal.setPackageName(q);
7938                                                proposal.setTypeName(displayName);
7939                                                proposal.setName(name);
7940                                                proposal.setCompletion(name);
7941                                                //proposal.setFlags(Flags.AccDefault);
7942                                                proposal.setReplaceRange(CompletionEngine.this.startPosition - CompletionEngine.this.offset, CompletionEngine.this.endPosition - CompletionEngine.this.offset);
7943                                                proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
7944                                                CompletionEngine.this.requestor.accept(proposal);
7945                                                if(DEBUG) {
7946                                                        CompletionEngine.this.printDebug(proposal);
7947                                                }
7948                                        }
7949                                }
7950                        }
7951                };
7952 
7953                switch (kind) {
7954                        case FIELD :
7955                                InternalNamingConventions.suggestFieldNames(
7956                                        this.javaProject,
7957                                        qualifiedPackageName,
7958                                        qualifiedSourceName,
7959                                        dim,
7960                                        modifiers,
7961                                        token,
7962                                        discouragedNames,
7963                                        namingRequestor);
7964                                break;
7965                        case LOCAL :
7966                                InternalNamingConventions.suggestLocalVariableNames(
7967                                        this.javaProject,
7968                                        qualifiedPackageName,
7969                                        qualifiedSourceName,
7970                                        dim,
7971                                        token,
7972                                        discouragedNames,
7973                                        namingRequestor);
7974                                break;
7975                        case ARGUMENT :
7976                                InternalNamingConventions.suggestArgumentNames(
7977                                        this.javaProject,
7978                                        qualifiedPackageName,
7979                                        qualifiedSourceName,
7980                                        dim,
7981                                        token,
7982                                        discouragedNames,
7983                                        namingRequestor);
7984                                break;
7985                }
