8017        private ImportBinding[] getFavoriteReferenceBindings(Scope scope) {
8018                if (this.favoriteReferenceBindings != null) return this.favoriteReferenceBindings;
8019 
8020                String[] favoriteReferences = this.requestor.getFavoriteReferences();
8021 
8022                if (favoriteReferences == null || favoriteReferences.length == 0) return null;
8023 
8024                ImportBinding[] resolvedImports = new ImportBinding[favoriteReferences.length];
8025 
8026                int count = 0;
8027                next : for (int i = 0; i < favoriteReferences.length; i++) {
8028                        String favoriteReference = favoriteReferences[i];
8029 
8030                        int length;
8031                        if (favoriteReference == null || (length = favoriteReference.length()) == 0) continue next;
8032 
8033                        boolean onDemand = favoriteReference.charAt(length - 1) == '*';
8034 
8035                        char[][] compoundName = CharOperation.splitOn('.', favoriteReference.toCharArray());
8036                        if (onDemand) {
8037                                compoundName = CharOperation.subarray(compoundName, 0, compoundName.length - 1);
8038                        }
8039 
8040                        // remove duplicate and conflicting
8041                        for (int j = 0; j < count; j++) {
8042                                ImportReference f = resolvedImports[j].reference;
8043 
8044                                if (CharOperation.equals(f.tokens, compoundName)) continue next;
8045 
8046                                if (!onDemand && ((f.bits & ASTNode.OnDemand) == 0)) {
8047                                        if (CharOperation.equals(f.tokens[f.tokens.length - 1], compoundName[compoundName.length - 1]))
8048                                                continue next;
8049                                }
8050                        }
8051 
8052                        boolean isStatic = true;
8053 
8054                        ImportReference importReference =
8055                                new ImportReference(
8056                                                compoundName,
8057                                                new long[compoundName.length],
8058                                                onDemand);
8059 
8060                        Binding importBinding = this.unitScope.findImport(compoundName, onDemand);
8061 
8062                        if (!importBinding.isValidBinding()) {
8063                                continue next;
8064                        }
8065 
8066                        if (importBinding instanceof PackageBinding) {
8067                                continue next;
8068                        }
8069 
8070                        resolvedImports[count++] =
8071                                new ImportBinding(compoundName, onDemand, importBinding, importReference);
8072                }
8073 
8074                if (resolvedImports.length > count)
8075                        System.arraycopy(resolvedImports, 0, resolvedImports = new ImportBinding[count], 0, count);
8076 
8077                return this.favoriteReferenceBindings = resolvedImports;
8078        }

8080        protected boolean hasPossibleAnnotationTarget(TypeBinding typeBinding, Scope scope) {
8081                if (this.targetedElement == TagBits.AnnotationForPackage) {
8082                        long target = typeBinding.getAnnotationTagBits() & TagBits.AnnotationTargetMASK;
8083                        if(target != 0 && (target & TagBits.AnnotationForPackage) == 0) {
8084                                return false;
8085                        }
8086                } else if ((this.targetedElement & TagBits.AnnotationForType) != 0) {
8087                        if (scope.parent != null &&
8088                                        scope.parent.parent != null &&
8089                                        scope.parent.referenceContext() instanceof CompletionOnAnnotationOfType &&
8090                                        scope.parent.parent instanceof CompilationUnitScope) {
8091                                long target = typeBinding.getAnnotationTagBits() & TagBits.AnnotationTargetMASK;
8092                                if ((this.targetedElement & TagBits.AnnotationForAnnotationType) != 0) {
8093                                        if(target != 0 && (target &(TagBits.AnnotationForType | TagBits.AnnotationForAnnotationType)) == 0) {
8094                                                return false;
8095                                        }
8096                                } else {
8097                                        if(target != 0 && (target &(TagBits.AnnotationForType)) == 0) {
8098                                                return false;
8099                                        }
8100                                }
8101                        }
8102                }
8103                return true;
8104        }

8123        private void setSourceRange(int start, int end, boolean emptyTokenAdjstment) {

8125                if(emptyTokenAdjstment) {
8126                        int endOfEmptyToken = ((CompletionScanner)this.parser.scanner).endOfEmptyToken;
8127                        this.endPosition = endOfEmptyToken > end ? endOfEmptyToken + 1 : end + 1;

8132        private char[][] computeAlreadyDefinedName(
8133                        BlockScope scope,
8134                        InvocationSite invocationSite) {
8135                ArrayList result = new ArrayList();
8136 
8137                boolean staticsOnly = false;
8138 
8139                Scope currentScope = scope;
8140 
8141                done1 : while (true) { // done when a COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE is found
8142 
8143                        switch (currentScope.kind) {
8144 
8145                                case Scope.METHOD_SCOPE :
8146                                        // handle the error case inside an explicit constructor call (see MethodScope>>findField)
8147                                        MethodScope methodScope = (MethodScope) currentScope;
8148                                        staticsOnly |= methodScope.isStatic | methodScope.isConstructorCall;
8149 
8150                                case Scope.BLOCK_SCOPE :
8151                                        BlockScope blockScope = (BlockScope) currentScope;
8152 
8153                                        next : for (int i = 0, length = blockScope.locals.length; i < length; i++) {
8154                                                LocalVariableBinding local = blockScope.locals[i];
8155 
8156                                                if (local == null)
8157                                                        break next;
8158 
8159                                                if (local.isSecret())
8160                                                        continue next;
8161 
8162                                                result.add(local.name);
8163                                        }
8164                                        break;
8165 
8166                                case Scope.CLASS_SCOPE :
8167                                        ClassScope classScope = (ClassScope) currentScope;
8168                                        SourceTypeBinding enclosingType = classScope.getReferenceBinding();
8169                                        computeAlreadyDefinedName(
8170                                                        enclosingType,
8171                                                        classScope,
8172                                                        staticsOnly,
8173                                                        invocationSite,
8174                                                        result);
8175                                        staticsOnly |= enclosingType.isStatic();
8176                                        break;
8177 
8178                                case Scope.COMPILATION_UNIT_SCOPE :
8179                                        break done1;
8180                        }
8181                        currentScope = currentScope.parent;
8182                }
8183 
8184                if (result.size() == 0) return CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR;
8185 
8186                return (char[][])result.toArray(new char[result.size()][]);
8187        }

8189        private void computeAlreadyDefinedName(
8190                        SourceTypeBinding receiverType,
8191                        ClassScope scope,
8192                        boolean onlyStaticFields,
8193                        InvocationSite invocationSite,
8194                        ArrayList result) {
8195 
8196                ReferenceBinding currentType = receiverType;
8197                ReferenceBinding[] interfacesToVisit = null;
8198                int nextPosition = 0;
8199                do {
8200                        ReferenceBinding[] itsInterfaces = currentType.superInterfaces();
8201                        if (itsInterfaces != Binding.NO_SUPERINTERFACES) {
8202                                if (interfacesToVisit == null) {
8203                                        interfacesToVisit = itsInterfaces;
8204                                        nextPosition = interfacesToVisit.length;
8205                                } else {
8206                                        int itsLength = itsInterfaces.length;
8207                                        if (nextPosition + itsLength >= interfacesToVisit.length)
8208                                                System.arraycopy(interfacesToVisit, 0, interfacesToVisit = new ReferenceBinding[nextPosition + itsLength + 5], 0, nextPosition);
8209                                        nextInterface : for (int a = 0; a < itsLength; a++) {
8210                                                ReferenceBinding next = itsInterfaces[a];
8211                                                for (int b = 0; b < nextPosition; b++)
8212                                                        if (next == interfacesToVisit[b]) continue nextInterface;
8213                                                interfacesToVisit[nextPosition++] = next;
8214                                        }
8215                                }
8216                        }
8217 
8218                        FieldBinding[] fields = currentType.availableFields();
8219                        if(fields != null && fields.length > 0) {
8220                                computeAlreadyDefinedName(
8221                                        fields,
8222                                        scope,
8223                                        onlyStaticFields,
8224                                        receiverType,
8225                                        invocationSite,
8226                                        result);
8227                        }
8228                        currentType = currentType.superclass();
8229                } while ( currentType != null);
8230 
8231                if (interfacesToVisit != null) {
8232                        for (int i = 0; i < nextPosition; i++) {
8233                                ReferenceBinding anInterface = interfacesToVisit[i];
8234                                FieldBinding[] fields = anInterface.availableFields();
8235                                if(fields !=  null) {
8236                                        computeAlreadyDefinedName(
8237                                                fields,
8238                                                scope,
8239                                                onlyStaticFields,
8240                                                receiverType,
8241                                                invocationSite,
8242                                                result);
8243                                }
8244 
8245                                ReferenceBinding[] itsInterfaces = anInterface.superInterfaces();
8246                                if (itsInterfaces != Binding.NO_SUPERINTERFACES) {
8247                                        int itsLength = itsInterfaces.length;
8248                                        if (nextPosition + itsLength >= interfacesToVisit.length)
8249                                                System.arraycopy(interfacesToVisit, 0, interfacesToVisit = new ReferenceBinding[nextPosition + itsLength + 5], 0, nextPosition);
8250                                        nextInterface : for (int a = 0; a < itsLength; a++) {
8251                                                ReferenceBinding next = itsInterfaces[a];
8252                                                for (int b = 0; b < nextPosition; b++)
8253                                                        if (next == interfacesToVisit[b]) continue nextInterface;
8254                                                interfacesToVisit[nextPosition++] = next;
8255                                        }
8256                                }
8257                        }
8258                }
8259        }

8261        private void computeAlreadyDefinedName(
8262                        FieldBinding[] fields,
8263                        Scope scope,
8264                        boolean onlyStaticFields,
8265                        ReferenceBinding receiverType,
8266                        InvocationSite invocationSite,
8267                        ArrayList result) {
8268

8270                        FieldBinding field = fields[f];
8271

8273

8275 
8276                        if (!field.canBeSeenBy(receiverType, invocationSite, scope)) continue next;
8277 
8278                        result.add(field.name);
8279                }

8294        private void computeExpectedTypes(ASTNode parent, ASTNode node, Scope scope){
8295 
8296                // default filter
8297                this.expectedTypesFilter = SUBTYPE;
8298                this.hasJavaLangObjectAsExpectedType = false;
8299 
8300                // find types from parent
8301                if(parent instanceof AbstractVariableDeclaration) {
8302                        AbstractVariableDeclaration variable = (AbstractVariableDeclaration)parent;
8303                        TypeBinding binding = variable.getTypeBinding();
8304                        if(binding != null) {
8305                                if(!(variable.initialization instanceof ArrayInitializer)) {
8306                                        addExpectedType(binding, scope);
8307                                }
8308                        }
8309                } else if(parent instanceof Assignment) {
8310                        TypeBinding binding = ((Assignment)parent).lhs.resolvedType;
8311                        if(binding != null) {
8312                                addExpectedType(binding, scope);
8313                        }
8314                } else if(parent instanceof ReturnStatement) {
8315                        if(scope.methodScope().referenceContext instanceof AbstractMethodDeclaration) {
8316                                MethodBinding methodBinding = ((AbstractMethodDeclaration) scope.methodScope().referenceContext).binding;
8317                                TypeBinding binding = methodBinding  == null ? null : methodBinding.returnType;
8318                                if(binding != null) {
8319                                        addExpectedType(binding, scope);
8320                                }
8321                        }
8322                } else if(parent instanceof CastExpression) {
8323                        Expression e = ((CastExpression)parent).type;
8324                        TypeBinding binding = e.resolvedType;
8325                        if(binding != null){
8326                                addExpectedType(binding, scope);
8327                                this.expectedTypesFilter = SUBTYPE | SUPERTYPE;
8328                        }
8329                } else if(parent instanceof MessageSend) {
8330                        MessageSend messageSend = (MessageSend) parent;
8331 
8332                        if(messageSend.actualReceiverType instanceof ReferenceBinding) {
8333                                ReferenceBinding binding = (ReferenceBinding)messageSend.actualReceiverType;
8334                                boolean isStatic = messageSend.receiver!=null && messageSend.receiver.isTypeReference();
8335 
8336                                while(binding != null) {
8337                                        computeExpectedTypesForMessageSend(
8338                                                binding,
8339                                                messageSend.selector,
8340                                                messageSend.arguments,
8341                                                (ReferenceBinding)messageSend.actualReceiverType,
8342                                                scope,
8343                                                messageSend,
8344                                                isStatic);
8345                                        computeExpectedTypesForMessageSendForInterface(
8346                                                binding,
8347                                                messageSend.selector,
8348                                                messageSend.arguments,
8349                                                (ReferenceBinding)messageSend.actualReceiverType,
8350                                                scope,
8351                                                messageSend,
8352                                                isStatic);
8353                                        binding = binding.superclass();
8354                                }
8355                        }
8356                } else if(parent instanceof AllocationExpression) {
8357                        AllocationExpression allocationExpression = (AllocationExpression) parent;
8358 
8359                        ReferenceBinding binding =null;
8360                        if (allocationExpression.type!=null)
8361                                binding=(ReferenceBinding)allocationExpression.type.resolvedType;
8362                        else
8363                                if (allocationExpression.member.resolvedType instanceof ReferenceBinding)
8364                                        binding=(ReferenceBinding)allocationExpression.member.resolvedType;
8365 
8366 
8367                        if(binding != null) {
8368                                computeExpectedTypesForAllocationExpression(
8369                                        binding,
8370                                        allocationExpression.arguments,
8371                                        scope,
8372                                        allocationExpression);
8373                        }
8374                } else if(parent instanceof OperatorExpression) {
8375                        int operator = (parent.bits & ASTNode.OperatorMASK) >> ASTNode.OperatorSHIFT;
8376                        if(parent instanceof ConditionalExpression) {
8377                                // for future use
8378                        } else if(parent instanceof InstanceOfExpression) {
8379                                InstanceOfExpression e = (InstanceOfExpression) parent;
8380                                TypeBinding binding = e.expression.resolvedType;
8381                                if(binding != null){
8382                                        addExpectedType(binding, scope);
8383                                        this.expectedTypesFilter = SUBTYPE | SUPERTYPE;
8384                                }
8385                        } else if(parent instanceof BinaryExpression) {
8386                                switch(operator) {
8387                                        case OperatorIds.PLUS :
8388                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.SHORT, scope);
8389                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.INT, scope);
8390                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.LONG, scope);
8391                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.FLOAT, scope);
8392                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.DOUBLE, scope);
8393                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.CHAR, scope);
8394                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.BYTE, scope);
8395                                                addExpectedType(scope.getJavaLangString(), scope);
8396                                                break;
8397                                        case OperatorIds.AND_AND :
8398                                        case OperatorIds.OR_OR :
8399                                        case OperatorIds.XOR :
8400                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.BOOLEAN, scope);
8401                                                break;
8402                                        default :
8403                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.SHORT, scope);
8404                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.INT, scope);
8405                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.LONG, scope);
8406                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.FLOAT, scope);
8407                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.DOUBLE, scope);
8408                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.CHAR, scope);
8409                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.BYTE, scope);
8410                                                break;
8411                                }
8412                                BinaryExpression binaryExpression = (BinaryExpression) parent;
8413                                if(operator == OperatorIds.LESS) {
8414                                        if(binaryExpression.left instanceof SingleNameReference){
8415                                                SingleNameReference name = (SingleNameReference) binaryExpression.left;
8416                                                Binding b = scope.getBinding(name.token, Binding.VARIABLE | Binding.TYPE, name, false);
8417                                                if(b instanceof ReferenceBinding) {
8418                                                        TypeVariableBinding[] typeVariableBindings =((ReferenceBinding)b).typeVariables();
8419                                                        if(typeVariableBindings != null && typeVariableBindings.length > 0) {
8420                                                                addExpectedType(typeVariableBindings[0].firstBound, scope);
8421                                                        }
8422 
8423                                                }
8424                                        }
8425                                }
8426                        } else if(parent instanceof UnaryExpression) {
8427                                switch(operator) {
8428                                        case OperatorIds.NOT :
8429                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.BOOLEAN, scope);
8430                                                break;
8431                                        case OperatorIds.TWIDDLE :
8432                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.SHORT, scope);
8433                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.INT, scope);
8434                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.LONG, scope);
8435                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.CHAR, scope);
8436                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.BYTE, scope);
8437                                                break;
8438                                        case OperatorIds.PLUS :
8439                                        case OperatorIds.MINUS :
8440                                        case OperatorIds.PLUS_PLUS :
8441                                        case OperatorIds.MINUS_MINUS :
8442                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.SHORT, scope);
8443                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.INT, scope);
8444                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.LONG, scope);
8445                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.FLOAT, scope);
8446                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.DOUBLE, scope);
8447                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.CHAR, scope);
8448                                                addExpectedType(TypeBinding.BYTE, scope);
8449                                                break;
8450                                }
8451                        }
8452                } else if(parent instanceof ArrayReference) {
8453                        addExpectedType(TypeBinding.SHORT, scope);
8454                        addExpectedType(TypeBinding.INT, scope);
8455                        addExpectedType(TypeBinding.LONG, scope);
8456                } else if(parent instanceof ParameterizedSingleTypeReference) {
8457                        ParameterizedSingleTypeReference ref = (ParameterizedSingleTypeReference) parent;
8458                        TypeVariableBinding[] typeVariables = ((ReferenceBinding)ref.resolvedType).typeVariables();
8459                        int length = ref.typeArguments == null ? 0 : ref.typeArguments.length;
8460                        if(typeVariables != null && typeVariables.length >= length) {
8461                                int index = length - 1;
8462                                while(index > -1 && ref.typeArguments[index] != node) index--;
8463 
8464                                TypeBinding bound = typeVariables[index].firstBound;
8465                                addExpectedType(bound == null ? scope.getJavaLangObject() : bound, scope);
8466                        }
8467                } else if(parent instanceof ParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference) {
8468                        ParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference ref = (ParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference) parent;
8469                        TypeVariableBinding[] typeVariables = ((ReferenceBinding)ref.resolvedType).typeVariables();
8470                        TypeReference[][] arguments = ref.typeArguments;
8471                        if(typeVariables != null) {
8472                                int iLength = arguments == null ? 0 : arguments.length;
8473                                done: for (int i = 0; i < iLength; i++) {
8474                                        int jLength = arguments[i] == null ? 0 : arguments[i].length;
8475                                        for (int j = 0; j < jLength; j++) {
8476                                                if(arguments[i][j] == node && typeVariables.length > j) {
8477                                                        TypeBinding bound = typeVariables[j].firstBound;
8478                                                        addExpectedType(bound == null ? scope.getJavaLangObject() : bound, scope);
8479                                                        break done;
8480                                                }
8481                                        }
8482                                }
8483                        }
8484                } else if(parent instanceof MemberValuePair) {
8485                        MemberValuePair memberValuePair = (MemberValuePair) parent;
8486                        if(memberValuePair.binding != null) {
8487                                addExpectedType(memberValuePair.binding.returnType, scope);
8488                        }
8489                } else if (parent instanceof TryStatement) {
8490                        boolean isException = false;
8491                        if (node instanceof CompletionOnSingleTypeReference) {
8492                                isException = ((CompletionOnSingleTypeReference)node).isException();
8493                        } else if (node instanceof CompletionOnQualifiedTypeReference) {
8494                                isException = ((CompletionOnQualifiedTypeReference)node).isException();
8495                        } else if (node instanceof CompletionOnParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference) {
8496                                isException = ((CompletionOnParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference)node).isException();
8497                        }
8498                        if (isException) {
8499                                ThrownExceptionFinder thrownExceptionFinder = new ThrownExceptionFinder();
8500                                ReferenceBinding[] bindings = thrownExceptionFinder.find((TryStatement) parent, (BlockScope)scope);
8501                                if (bindings != null && bindings.length > 0) {
8502                                        for (int i = 0; i < bindings.length; i++) {
8503                                                addExpectedType(bindings[i], scope);
8504                                        }
8505                                        this.expectedTypesFilter = SUPERTYPE;
8506                                }
8507                        }
8508 
8509                // Expected types for javadoc
8510                } else if (parent instanceof Javadoc) {
8511                        if (scope.kind == Scope.METHOD_SCOPE) {
8512                                MethodScope methodScope = (MethodScope) scope;
8513                                AbstractMethodDeclaration methodDecl = methodScope.referenceMethod();
8514                                if (methodDecl != null && methodDecl.binding != null) {
8515                                        ReferenceBinding[] exceptions = methodDecl.binding.thrownExceptions;
8516                                        if (exceptions != null) {
8517                                                for (int i = 0; i < exceptions.length; i++) {
8518                                                        addExpectedType(exceptions[i], scope);
8519                                                }
8520                                        }
8521                                }
8522                        }
8523                }
8524 
8525                if(this.expectedTypesPtr + 1 != this.expectedTypes.length) {
8526                        System.arraycopy(this.expectedTypes, 0, this.expectedTypes = new TypeBinding[this.expectedTypesPtr + 1], 0, this.expectedTypesPtr + 1);
8527                }
8528        }

8530        private void computeExpectedTypesForAllocationExpression(
8531                ReferenceBinding binding,
8532                Expression[] arguments,
8533                Scope scope,
8534                InvocationSite invocationSite) {
8535 
8536                MethodBinding[] methods = binding.availableMethods();
8537                nextMethod : for (int i = 0; i < methods.length; i++) {
8538                        MethodBinding method = methods[i];
8539 
8540                        if (!method.isConstructor()) continue nextMethod;
8541 
8542                        if (method.isSynthetic()) continue nextMethod;
8543 
8544                        if (this.options.checkVisibility && !method.canBeSeenBy(invocationSite, scope)) continue nextMethod;
8545 
8546                        TypeBinding[] parameters = method.parameters;
8547                        if(parameters.length < arguments.length)
8548                                continue nextMethod;
8549 
8550                        int length = arguments.length - 1;
8551 
8552                        for (int j = 0; j < length; j++) {
8553                                Expression argument = arguments[j];
8554                                TypeBinding argType = argument.resolvedType;
8555                                if(argType != null && !argType.isCompatibleWith(parameters[j]))
8556                                        continue nextMethod;
8557                        }
8558 
8559                        TypeBinding expectedType = method.parameters[arguments.length - 1];
8560                        if(expectedType != null) {
8561                                addExpectedType(expectedType, scope);
8562                        }
8563                }
8564        }

8566        private void computeExpectedTypesForMessageSendForInterface(
8567                ReferenceBinding binding,
8568                char[] selector,
8569                Expression[] arguments,
8570                ReferenceBinding receiverType,
8571                Scope scope,
8572                InvocationSite invocationSite,
8573                boolean isStatic) {
8574 
8575                ReferenceBinding[] itsInterfaces = binding.superInterfaces();
8576                if (itsInterfaces != Binding.NO_SUPERINTERFACES) {
8577                        ReferenceBinding[] interfacesToVisit = itsInterfaces;
8578                        int nextPosition = interfacesToVisit.length;
8579 
8580                        for (int i = 0; i < nextPosition; i++) {
8581                                ReferenceBinding currentType = interfacesToVisit[i];
8582                                computeExpectedTypesForMessageSend(
8583                                        currentType,
8584                                        selector,
8585                                        arguments,
8586                                        receiverType,
8587                                        scope,
8588                                        invocationSite,
8589                                        isStatic);
8590 
8591                                if ((itsInterfaces = currentType.superInterfaces()) != Binding.NO_SUPERINTERFACES) {
8592                                        int itsLength = itsInterfaces.length;
8593                                        if (nextPosition + itsLength >= interfacesToVisit.length)
8594                                                System.arraycopy(interfacesToVisit, 0, interfacesToVisit = new ReferenceBinding[nextPosition + itsLength + 5], 0, nextPosition);
8595                                        nextInterface : for (int a = 0; a < itsLength; a++) {
8596                                                ReferenceBinding next = itsInterfaces[a];
8597                                                for (int b = 0; b < nextPosition; b++)
8598                                                        if (next == interfacesToVisit[b]) continue nextInterface;
8599                                                interfacesToVisit[nextPosition++] = next;
8600                                        }
8601                                }
8602                        }
8603                }
8604        }

8606        private void computeExpectedTypesForMessageSend(
8607                ReferenceBinding binding,
8608                char[] selector,
8609                Expression[] arguments,
8610                ReferenceBinding receiverType,
8611                Scope scope,
8612                InvocationSite invocationSite,
8613                boolean isStatic) {
8614 
8615                MethodBinding[] methods = binding.availableMethods();
8616                nextMethod : for (int i = 0; i < methods.length; i++) {
8617                        MethodBinding method = methods[i];
8618 
8619                        if (method.isSynthetic()) continue nextMethod;
8620 
8621                        if (method.isDefaultAbstract())        continue nextMethod;
8622 
8623                        if (method.isConstructor()) continue nextMethod;
8624

8628

8632                        if(parameters.length < arguments.length)

8639                                TypeBinding argType = argument.resolvedType;
8640                                if(argType != null && !argType.isCompatibleWith(parameters[j]))
8641                                        continue nextMethod;
8642                        }
8643 
8644                        TypeBinding expectedType = method.parameters[arguments.length - 1];
8645                        if(expectedType != null) {
8646                                addExpectedType(expectedType, scope);
8647                        }

8650        private void addExpectedType(TypeBinding type, Scope scope){
8651                if (type == null || !type.isValidBinding()) return;
8652 
8653                int length = this.expectedTypes.length;
8654                if (++this.expectedTypesPtr >= length)
8655                        System.arraycopy(this.expectedTypes, 0, this.expectedTypes = new TypeBinding[length * 2], 0, length);
8656                this.expectedTypes[this.expectedTypesPtr] = type;
8657 
8658                if(type == scope.getJavaLangObject()) {
8659                        this.hasJavaLangObjectAsExpectedType = true;
8660                }
8661        }

8668                this.forbbidenBindings[this.forbbidenBindingsPtr] = binding;
8669        }

8679        private Scope computeForbiddenBindings(ASTNode astNode, ASTNode astNodeParent, Scope scope) {
8680                this.forbbidenBindingsFilter = NONE;
8681                if(scope instanceof ClassScope) {
8682                        TypeDeclaration typeDeclaration = ((ClassScope)scope).referenceContext;
8683                        if(typeDeclaration.superclass == astNode) {
8684                                this.addForbiddenBindings(typeDeclaration.binding);
8685                                return scope.parent;
8686                        }
8687                        TypeReference[] superInterfaces = typeDeclaration.superInterfaces;
8688                        int length = superInterfaces == null ? 0 : superInterfaces.length;
8689                        for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
8690                                if(superInterfaces[i] == astNode) {
8691                                        this.addForbiddenBindings(typeDeclaration.binding);
8692                                        return scope.parent;
8693                                }
8694                        }
8695                } else {
8696                        if (astNodeParent != null && astNodeParent instanceof TryStatement) {
8697                                boolean isException = false;
8698                                if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnSingleTypeReference) {
8699                                        isException = ((CompletionOnSingleTypeReference)astNode).isException();
8700                                } else if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnQualifiedTypeReference) {
8701                                        isException = ((CompletionOnQualifiedTypeReference)astNode).isException();
8702                                } else if (astNode instanceof CompletionOnParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference) {
8703                                        isException = ((CompletionOnParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference)astNode).isException();
8704                                }
8705                                if (isException) {
8706                                        Argument[] catchArguments = ((TryStatement) astNodeParent).catchArguments;
8707                                        int length = catchArguments == null ? 0 : catchArguments.length;
8708                                        for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
8709                                                TypeBinding caughtException = catchArguments[i].type.resolvedType;
8710                                                if (caughtException != null) {
8711                                                        this.addForbiddenBindings(caughtException);
8712                                                        this.knownTypes.put(CharOperation.concat(caughtException.qualifiedPackageName(), caughtException.qualifiedSourceName(), '.'), this);
8713                                                }
8714                                        }
8715                                        this.forbbidenBindingsFilter = SUBTYPE;
8716                                }
8717                        }
8718                }
8719//                else if(scope instanceof MethodScope) {
8720//                        MethodScope methodScope = (MethodScope) scope;
8721//                        if(methodScope.insideTypeAnnotation) {
8722//                                return methodScope.parent.parent;
8723//                        }
8724//                }
8725                return scope;
8726        }
8727        private char[] computePrefix(SourceTypeBinding declarationType, SourceTypeBinding invocationType, boolean isStatic){
8728 
8729                StringBuffer completion = new StringBuffer(10);
8730 
8731                if (isStatic) {
8732                        completion.append(declarationType.sourceName());
8733 
8734                } else if (declarationType == invocationType) {
8735                        completion.append(THIS);
8736 
8737                } else {
8738 
8739                        if (!declarationType.isNestedType()) {
8740 
8741                                completion.append(declarationType.sourceName());
8742                                completion.append('.');
8743                                completion.append(THIS);
8744 
8745                        } else if (!declarationType.isAnonymousType()) {
8746 
8747                                completion.append(declarationType.sourceName());
8748                                completion.append('.');
8749                                completion.append(THIS);
8750 
8751                        }
8752                }
8753 
8754                return completion.toString().toCharArray();
8755        }

8757        private void proposeNewMethod(char[] token, ReferenceBinding reference) {
8758                if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.POTENTIAL_METHOD_DECLARATION)) {
8759                        int relevance = computeBaseRelevance();
8760                        relevance += computeRelevanceForResolution();
8761                        relevance += computeRelevanceForInterestingProposal();
8762                        relevance += computeRelevanceForRestrictions(IAccessRule.K_ACCESSIBLE); // no access restriction for new method
8763 
8764                        CompletionProposal proposal = this.createProposal(CompletionProposal.POTENTIAL_METHOD_DECLARATION, this.actualCompletionPosition);
8765                        proposal.setDeclarationSignature(getSignature(reference));
8766                        proposal.setSignature(
8767                                        createMethodSignature(
8768                                                        CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR,
8769                                                        CharOperation.NO_CHAR_CHAR,
8770                                                        CharOperation.NO_CHAR,
8771                                                        VOID));
8772                        proposal.setDeclarationPackageName(reference.qualifiedPackageName());
8773                        proposal.setDeclarationTypeName(reference.qualifiedSourceName());
8774 
8775                        //proposal.setPackageName(null);
8776                        proposal.setTypeName(VOID);
8777                        proposal.setName(token);
8778                        //proposal.setParameterPackageNames(null);
8779                        //proposal.setParameterTypeNames(null);
8780                        //proposal.setPackageName(null);
8781                        proposal.setCompletion(token);
8782                        proposal.setFlags(Flags.AccPublic);
8783                        proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
8784                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
8785                        this.requestor.accept(proposal);
8786                        if(DEBUG) {
8787                                this.printDebug(proposal);
8788                        }
8789                }
8790        }
8791        private boolean isForbidden(Binding binding) {
8792                for (int i = 0; i <= this.forbbidenBindingsPtr; i++) {
8793                        if(this.forbbidenBindings[i] == binding) {
8794                                return true;
8795                        }
8796                        if((this.forbbidenBindingsFilter & SUBTYPE) != 0) {
8797                                if (binding instanceof TypeBinding &&
8798                                                this.forbbidenBindings[i] instanceof TypeBinding &&
8799                                                ((TypeBinding)binding).isCompatibleWith((TypeBinding)this.forbbidenBindings[i])) {
8800                                        return true;
8801                                }
8802                        }
8803                }
8804                return false;
8805        }
8806        private boolean isValidParent(ASTNode parent, ASTNode node, Scope scope){
8807 
8808                if(parent instanceof ParameterizedSingleTypeReference) {
8809                        ParameterizedSingleTypeReference ref = (ParameterizedSingleTypeReference) parent;
8810                        TypeVariableBinding[] typeVariables = ((ReferenceBinding)ref.resolvedType).typeVariables();
8811                        int length = ref.typeArguments == null ? 0 : ref.typeArguments.length;
8812                        int nodeIndex = -1;
8813                        for(int i = length - 1 ; i > -1 ; i--) {
8814                                if(node == ref.typeArguments[i]) {
8815                                        nodeIndex = i;
8816                                        break;
8817                                }
8818                        }
8819                        if(nodeIndex > -1 && (typeVariables == null || typeVariables.length < nodeIndex + 1)) {
8820                                TypeBinding[] typeBindings = new TypeBinding[nodeIndex + 1];
8821                                for(int i = 0; i < nodeIndex; i++) {
8822                                        typeBindings[i] = ref.typeArguments[i].resolvedType;
8823                                }
8824                                typeBindings[nodeIndex] = scope.getJavaLangObject();
8825                                if(typeVariables == null || typeVariables.length == 0) {
8826                                        scope.problemReporter().nonGenericTypeCannotBeParameterized(ref, ref.resolvedType, typeBindings);
8827                                } else {
8828                                        scope.problemReporter().incorrectArityForParameterizedType(ref, ref.resolvedType, typeBindings);
8829                                }
8830                                return false;
8831                        }
8832                } else if(parent instanceof ParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference) {
8833                        ParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference ref = (ParameterizedQualifiedTypeReference) parent;
8834                        TypeVariableBinding[] typeVariables = ((ReferenceBinding)ref.resolvedType).typeVariables();
8835                        TypeReference[][] arguments = ref.typeArguments;
8836                        int iLength = arguments == null ? 0 : arguments.length;
8837                        for (int i = 0; i < iLength; i++) {
8838                                int jLength = arguments[i] == null ? 0 : arguments[i].length;
8839                                for (int j = 0; j < jLength; j++) {
8840                                        if(arguments[i][j] == node && (typeVariables == null || typeVariables.length <= j)) {
8841                                                TypeBinding[] typeBindings = new TypeBinding[j + 1];
8842                                                for(int k = 0; k < j; k++) {
8843                                                        typeBindings[k] = ref.typeArguments[i][k].resolvedType;
8844                                                }
8845                                                typeBindings[j] = scope.getJavaLangObject();
8846                                                if(typeVariables == null || typeVariables.length == 0) {
8847                                                        scope.problemReporter().nonGenericTypeCannotBeParameterized(ref, ref.resolvedType, typeBindings);
8848                                                } else {
8849                                                        scope.problemReporter().incorrectArityForParameterizedType(ref, ref.resolvedType, typeBindings);
8850                                                }
8851                                                return false;
8852                                        }
8853                                }
8854                        }
8855                }
8856                return true;
8857        }
8858 
8859        public static char[] createNonGenericTypeSignature(char[] qualifiedPackageName, char[] qualifiedTypeName) {
8860                return Signature.createCharArrayTypeSignature(
8861                                CharOperation.concat(
8862                                                qualifiedPackageName,
8863                                                CharOperation.replaceOnCopy(qualifiedTypeName, '.', '$'), '.'), true);
8864        }
8865        public static char[] createTypeSignature(char[] qualifiedPackageName, char[] qualifiedTypeName) {
8866                char[] name = new char[qualifiedTypeName.length];
8867                System.arraycopy(qualifiedTypeName, 0, name, 0, qualifiedTypeName.length);
8868 
8869                int depth = 0;
8870                int length = name.length;
8871                for (int i = length -1; i >= 0; i--) {
8872                        switch (name[i]) {
8873                                case '.':
8874                                        if (depth == 0 && name[i - 1] != '>') {
8875                                                name[i] = '$';
8876                                        }
8877                                        break;
8878                                case '<':
8879                                        depth--;
8880                                        break;
8881                                case '>':
8882                                        depth++;
8883                                        break;
8884                        }
8885                }
8886                return Signature.createCharArrayTypeSignature(
8887                                CharOperation.concat(
8888                                                qualifiedPackageName,
8889                                                name, '.'), true);
8890        }

8892        public static char[] createMethodSignature(char[][] parameterPackageNames, char[][] parameterTypeNames, char[] returnPackagename, char[] returnTypeName) {
8893                char[] returnTypeSignature =
8894                        returnTypeName == null || returnTypeName.length == 0
8895                        ? Signature.createCharArrayTypeSignature(VOID, true)
8896                        : Signature.createCharArrayTypeSignature(
8897                                        CharOperation.concat(
8898                                                        returnPackagename,
8899                                                        CharOperation.replaceOnCopy(returnTypeName, '.', '$'), '.'), true);
8900 
8901                return createMethodSignature(
8902                                parameterPackageNames,
8903                                parameterTypeNames,
8904                                returnTypeSignature);
8905        }

8907        public static char[] createMethodSignature(char[][] parameterPackageNames, char[][] parameterTypeNames, char[] returnTypeSignature) {

8909                for (int i = 0; i < parameterTypeSignature.length; i++) {

8911                                Signature.createCharArrayTypeSignature(
8912                                                CharOperation.concat(
8913                                                                parameterPackageNames[i],
8914                                                                CharOperation.replaceOnCopy(parameterTypeNames[i], '.', '$'), '.'), true);
8915                }
8916

8918                                parameterTypeSignature,
8919                                returnTypeSignature);

8929        /*
8930         * Create a completion proposal for a type.
8931         */
8932        private void createTypeProposal(char[] packageName, char[] typeName, int modifiers, int accessibility, char[] completionName, int relevance) {
8933 
8934                // Create standard type proposal
8935                if(!this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF) && (this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.ONLY_INLINE_TAG) == 0) {
8936                        CompletionProposal proposal = CompletionProposal.create(CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition - this.offset);
8937                        proposal.nameLookup = this.nameEnvironment.nameLookup;
8938                        proposal.completionEngine = this;
8939                        proposal.setDeclarationSignature(packageName);
8940                        proposal.setSignature(createNonGenericTypeSignature(packageName, typeName));
8941                        proposal.setPackageName(packageName);
8942                        proposal.setTypeName(typeName);
8943                        proposal.setCompletion(completionName);
8944                        proposal.setFlags(modifiers);
8945                        proposal.setReplaceRange(this.startPosition - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
8946                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance);
8947                        proposal.setAccessibility(accessibility);
8948                        this.requestor.accept(proposal);
8949                        if(DEBUG) {
8950                                this.printDebug(proposal);
8951                        }
8952                }
8953 
8954                // Create javadoc text proposal if necessary
8955                if ((this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.TEXT) != 0 && !this.requestor.isIgnored(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_TYPE_REF)) {
8956                        char[] javadocCompletion= inlineTagCompletion(completionName, JavadocTagConstants.TAG_LINK);
8957                        CompletionProposal proposal = CompletionProposal.create(CompletionProposal.JSDOC_TYPE_REF, this.actualCompletionPosition - this.offset);
8958                        proposal.nameLookup = this.nameEnvironment.nameLookup;
8959                        proposal.completionEngine = this;
8960                        proposal.setDeclarationSignature(packageName);
8961                        proposal.setSignature(createNonGenericTypeSignature(packageName, typeName));
8962                        proposal.setPackageName(packageName);
8963                        proposal.setTypeName(typeName);
8964                        proposal.setCompletion(javadocCompletion);
8965                        proposal.setFlags(modifiers);
8966                        int start = (this.assistNodeInJavadoc & CompletionOnJavadoc.REPLACE_TAG) != 0 ? this.javadocTagPosition : this.startPosition;
8967                        proposal.setReplaceRange(start - this.offset, this.endPosition - this.offset);
8968                        proposal.setRelevance(relevance+R_INLINE_TAG);
8969                        proposal.setAccessibility(accessibility);
8970                        this.requestor.accept(proposal);
8971                        if(DEBUG) {
8972                                this.printDebug(proposal);
8973                        }
8974                }
8975        }

9065        /**
9066         * Returns completion string inserted inside a specified inline tag.
9067         * @param completionName
9068         * @return char[] Completion text inclunding specified inline tag
9069         */
9070        private char[] inlineTagCompletion(char[] completionName, char[] inlineTag) {
9071                int tagLength= inlineTag.length;
9072                int completionLength = completionName.length;
9073                int inlineLength = 2+tagLength+1+completionLength+1;
9074                char[] inlineCompletion = new char[inlineLength];
9075                inlineCompletion[0] = '{';
9076                inlineCompletion[1] = '@';
9077                System.arraycopy(inlineTag, 0, inlineCompletion, 2, tagLength);
9078                inlineCompletion[tagLength+2] = ' ';
9079                System.arraycopy(completionName, 0, inlineCompletion, tagLength+3, completionLength);
9080                // do not add space at end of inline tag (see bug https://bugs.eclipse.org/bugs/show_bug.cgi?id=121026)
9081                //inlineCompletion[inlineLength-2] = ' ';
9082                inlineCompletion[inlineLength-1] = '}';
9083                return inlineCompletion;
9084        }

9133                        case CompletionProposal.TYPE_REF :
9134                                buffer.append("TYPE_REF"); //$NON-NLS-1$
9135                                break;
9136                        case CompletionProposal.VARIABLE_DECLARATION :
9137                                buffer.append("VARIABLE_DECLARATION"); //$NON-NLS-1$
9138                                break;
9139                        case CompletionProposal.POTENTIAL_METHOD_DECLARATION :
9140                                buffer.append("POTENTIAL_METHOD_DECLARATION"); //$NON-NLS-1$

9190                }
9191 
9192                printDebugTab(tab, buffer);
9193                buffer.append("\tCompletionLocation[").append(proposal.getCompletionLocation()).append("]\n"); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$
9194                int start = proposal.getReplaceStart();
9195                int end = proposal.getReplaceEnd();
9196                printDebugTab(tab, buffer);
9197                buffer.append("\tReplaceStart[").append(start).append("]"); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$
9198                buffer.append("-ReplaceEnd[").append(end).append("]\n"); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$
9199                if (this.source != null) {
9200                        printDebugTab(tab, buffer);
9201                        buffer.append("\tReplacedText[").append(this.source, start, end-start).append("]\n"); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$
9202                }
9203                printDebugTab(tab, buffer);
9204                buffer.append("\tTokenStart[").append(proposal.getTokenStart()).append("]"); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$
9205                buffer.append("-TokenEnd[").append(proposal.getTokenEnd()).append("]\n"); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$
9206                printDebugTab(tab, buffer);
9207                buffer.append("\tRelevance[").append(proposal.getRelevance()).append("]\n"); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$
9208 
9209                printDebugTab(tab, buffer);
9210                buffer.append("}\n");//$NON-NLS-1$
9211        }

9213        private char[][] substituteMethodTypeParameterNames(TypeVariableBinding[] typeVariables, char[][] excludedNames) {
9214                char[][] substituedParameterNames = new char[typeVariables.length][];
9215 
9216                for (int i = 0; i < substituedParameterNames.length; i++) {
9217                        substituedParameterNames[i] = typeVariables[i].sourceName;
9218                }
9219 
9220                boolean foundConflicts = false;
9221 
9222                nextTypeParameter : for (int i = 0; i < typeVariables.length; i++) {
9223                        TypeVariableBinding typeVariableBinding = typeVariables[i];
9224                        char[] methodParameterName = typeVariableBinding.sourceName;
9225 
9226                        for (int j = 0; j < excludedNames.length; j++) {
9227                                char[] typeParameterName = excludedNames[j];
9228                                if(CharOperation.equals(typeParameterName, methodParameterName, false)) {
9229                                        char[] substitution;
9230                                        if(methodParameterName.length == 1) {
9231                                                if(ScannerHelper.isUpperCase(methodParameterName[0])) {
9232                                                        substitution = substituteMethodTypeParameterName(methodParameterName[0], 'A', 'Z', excludedNames, substituedParameterNames);
9233                                                } else {
9234                                                        substitution = substituteMethodTypeParameterName(methodParameterName[0], 'a', 'z', excludedNames, substituedParameterNames);
9235                                                }
9236                                        } else {
9237                                                substitution = substituteMethodTypeParameterName(methodParameterName, excludedNames, substituedParameterNames);
9238                                        }
9239                                        substituedParameterNames[i] = substitution;
9240 
9241                                        foundConflicts = true;
9242                                        continue nextTypeParameter;
9243                                }
9244                        }
9245                }
9246 
9247                if(foundConflicts) return substituedParameterNames;
9248                return null;
9249        }

9251        private char[] substituteMethodTypeParameterName(char firstName, char startChar, char endChar, char[][] excludedNames, char[][] otherParameterNames) {
9252                char name = firstName;
9253                next : while (true) {
9254                        for (int i = 0 ; i < excludedNames.length ; i++){
9255                                if(excludedNames[i].length == 1 && ScannerHelper.toLowerCase(excludedNames[i][0]) == ScannerHelper.toLowerCase(name)) {
9256                                        name++;
9257                                        if(name > endChar)
9258                                                name = startChar;
9259                                        if(name == firstName)
9260                                                return substituteMethodTypeParameterName(new char[]{firstName}, excludedNames, otherParameterNames);
9261                                        continue next;
9262                                }
9263                        }
9264 
9265                        for (int i = 0; i < otherParameterNames.length; i++) {
9266                                if(otherParameterNames[i].length == 1 && ScannerHelper.toLowerCase(otherParameterNames[i][0]) == ScannerHelper.toLowerCase(name)) {
9267                                        name++;
9268                                        if(name > endChar)
9269                                                name = startChar;
9270                                        if(name == firstName)
9271                                                return substituteMethodTypeParameterName(new char[]{firstName}, excludedNames, otherParameterNames);
9272                                        continue next;
9273                                }
9274                        }
9275                        break next;
9276                }
9277                return new char[]{name};
9278        }

9280        private char[] substituteMethodTypeParameterName(char[] firstName, char[][] excludedNames, char[][] otherParameterNames) {
9281                char[] name = firstName;
9282                int count = 2;
9283                next : while(true) {
9284                        for(int k = 0 ; k < excludedNames.length ; k++){
9285                                if(CharOperation.equals(name, excludedNames[k], false)) {
9286                                        name = CharOperation.concat(firstName, String.valueOf(count++).toCharArray());
9287                                        continue next;
9288                                }
9289                        }
9290                        for (int i = 0; i < otherParameterNames.length; i++) {
9291                                if(CharOperation.equals(name, otherParameterNames[i], false)) {
9292                                        name = CharOperation.concat(firstName, String.valueOf(count++).toCharArray());
9293                                        continue next;
9294                                }
9295                        }
9296                        break next;
9297                }
9298                return name;
9299        }
